{"118408":{"value":{"Media":{"characters":{"edges":[{"id":222364,"node":{"age":"24","dateOfBirth":{"day":21,"month":12},"description":"__Height:__ 185cm","gender":"Male","id":169633,"image":{"large":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/character/large/b169633-IJHSVt0x5Lmg.png"},"isFavourite":false,"name":{"full":"Derrick Eckhart","native":"데릭 에카르트"},"siteUrl":"https://anilist.co/character/169633"},"role":"MAIN"},{"id":222365,"node":{"dateOfBirth":{},"gender":"Male","id":169634,"image":{"large":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/character/large/b169634-dfbhwApFGfYm.png"},"isFavourite":false,"name":{"alternative":["Vinter Berdandi"],"full":"Winter Berdandi","native":"뷘터 베르단디"},"siteUrl":"https://anilist.co/character/169634"},"role":"MAIN"},{"id":222366,"node":{"age":"17-","dateOfBirth":{},"description":"Penelope is the adoptive daughter of the Eckhart family.\n\nThe protagonist, Siyeon Cha, transmigrates into Penelope's body after struggling with the Hard Mode of the game Daughter of the Duke - Love Project! and falling asleep. After years of abuse, the protagonist has become a cold-hearted and independent person. She can also be very sarcastic.","gender":"Female","id":169632,"image":{"large":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/character/large/b169632-YCq6ateRLXbM.png"},"isFavourite":false,"name":{"full":"Penelope Eckhart","native":"페넬로페 에카르트"},"siteUrl":"https://anilist.co/character/169632"},"role":"MAIN"},{"id":222367,"node":{"dateOfBirth":{},"gender":"Male","id":169635,"image":{"large":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/character/large/b169635-58ouOLhO5dS4.png"},"isFavourite":false,"name":{"full":"Reynold Eckhart","native":"레널드 에카르트"},"siteUrl":"https://anilist.co/character/169635"},"role":"MAIN"},{"id":222368,"node":{"age":"20","dateOfBirth":{"day":1,"month":8},"description":"__Height:__ 188cm\n\nThe crown prince of the Empire of Eorka, Callisto Regulus is a cruel tyrant who treats humans like dirt. It is hinted that there may be an ill-fated reason for his disposition.","gender":"Male","id":169636,"image":{"large":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/character/large/b169636-SpY8Kw9K5sjx.png"},"isFavourite":false,"name":{"alternative":["Kallisto Regulus"],"full":"Callisto Regulus","native":"칼리스토 레굴루스"},"siteUrl":"https://anilist.co/character/169636"},"role":"MAIN"},{"id":230559,"node":{"dateOfBirth":{},"gender":"Male","id":177033,"image":{"large":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/character/large/b177033-RDugl70Qv7ez.png"},"isFavourite":false,"name":{"alternative":["Eclipse","Iklies","Eclise"],"full":"Eckles","native":"이클리스"},"siteUrl":"https://anilist.co/character/177033"},"role":"MAIN"},{"id":380592,"node":{"dateOfBirth":{},"gender":"Male","id":283427,"image":{"large":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/character/large/b283427-BQVzVdIIVYeJ.jpg"},"isFavourite":false,"name":{"full":"Pennel"},"siteUrl":"https://anilist.co/character/283427"},"role":"SUPPORTING"},{"id":424958,"node":{"age":"18","dateOfBirth":{},"description":"Ivonne Eckhart is the true, biological daughter of Duke Eckhart, and younger sister of Derrick Eckhart and Reynold Eckhart. She is the heroine of the otome game Daughter of the Duke - Love Project! in Normal Mode.\n~!After being possessed by the goddess, she is the main antagonist of the series.!~","gender":"Female","id":304404,"image":{"large":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/character/large/b304404-BimTcwtHOcju.png"},"isFavourite":false,"name":{"full":"Ivonne Eckhart","native":"이본 에카르트"},"siteUrl":"https://anilist.co/character/304404"},"role":"SUPPORTING"},{"id":282224,"node":{"dateOfBirth":{},"gender":"Female","id":209742,"image":{"large":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/character/large/b209742-SfwRlrv4Vl8X.png"},"isFavourite":false,"name":{"full":"Emily"},"siteUrl":"https://anilist.co/character/209742"},"role":"SUPPORTING"},{"id":380591,"node":{"dateOfBirth":{},"gender":"Male","id":283425,"image":{"large":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/character/large/b283425-FVeBUnohGku4.jpg"},"isFavourite":false,"name":{"full":"Duke Eckhart"},"siteUrl":"https://anilist.co/character/283425"},"role":"SUPPORTING"}]},"genres":["Drama","Fantasy","Psychological","Romance"],"id":118408,"rankings":[{"allTime":true,"context":"highest rated all time","format":"MANGA","rank":108,"type":"RATED"},{"allTime":true,"context":"most popular all time","format":"MANGA","rank":166,"type":"POPULAR"},{"allTime":false,"context":"highest rated","format":"MANGA","rank":8,"type":"RATED","year":2020},{"allTime":false,"context":"most popular","format":"MANGA","rank":12,"type":"POPULAR","year":2020}],"recommendations":{"edges":[{"node":{"mediaRecommendation":{"bannerImage":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/manga/banner/116382-o3f55yOakBaD.jpg","chapters":125,"countryOfOrigin":"KR","coverImage":{"color":"#e4a15d","extraLarge":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/manga/cover/large/bx116382-EPyB5KDY9UEo.png","large":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/manga/cover/medium/bx116382-EPyB5KDY9UEo.png","medium":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/manga/cover/small/bx116382-EPyB5KDY9UEo.png"},"description":"Aria Roscent mercilessly bullied her stepsister Mielle and paid the ultimate price for her misdeeds—but not before Mielle revealed that she’d manipulated Aria into harassing Mielle in the first place! Instead of dying, Aria is sent back in time and gifted a strange hourglass with mysterious powers. Now, Aria’s just got one goal: to embrace her role of villainess and utterly destroy Mielle’s life!\n\u003cbr\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\n(Source: Yen Press)","endDate":{"day":4,"month":11,"year":2022},"format":"MANGA","id":116382,"idMal":147207,"isAdult":false,"meanScore":78,"siteUrl":"https://anilist.co/manga/116382","startDate":{"day":1,"month":3,"year":2020},"status":"FINISHED","synonyms":["The Villainess Reverses the Hourglass","La villana retrocede el reloj de arena","反派女主的时间沙漏","悪女は砂時計をひっくり返す","时光沙漏·逆转命运的少女","ย้อนเวลากลับมาร้าย","惡女翻轉時光沙漏","Aria \u0026 Die goldene Sanduhr der Zeit"],"title":{"english":"The Villainess Turns the Hourglass","native":"악녀는 모래시계를 되돌린다","romaji":"Agnyeoneun Molaesigyeleul Doedollinda","userPreferred":"Agnyeoneun Molaesigyeleul Doedollinda"},"type":"MANGA"}}},{"node":{"mediaRecommendation":{"bannerImage":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/manga/banner/129210-EWwjla5kQTeT.jpg","countryOfOrigin":"KR","coverImage":{"color":"#e43550","extraLarge":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/manga/cover/large/bx129210-3QmLApie5gYJ.jpg","large":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/manga/cover/medium/bx129210-3QmLApie5gYJ.jpg","medium":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/manga/cover/small/bx129210-3QmLApie5gYJ.jpg"},"description":"Kidnapping, murder, and risqué relationships! Within the scandalous pages of The Abysmal Flower, the downfall of Roxana Agrece's criminal family is already foretold. So when Cassis Pedelian, the heroine's older brother, is kidnapped by Roxana's father, she can either wait for the heroine's revenge... or take matters into her own hands, since Cassis is the key to her survival. But with deceitful characters on all sides, can Roxana and Cassis trust each other enough to bring down the brutal Agreces?\u003cbr\u003e\n\u003cbr\u003e\n(Source: Tapas)","endDate":{},"format":"MANGA","id":129210,"idMal":147454,"isAdult":false,"meanScore":81,"siteUrl":"https://anilist.co/manga/129210","startDate":{"day":31,"month":1,"year":2021},"status":"HIATUS","synonyms":["How to Protect the Heroine’s Older Brother","The Way to Protect the Female Lead's Older Brother","Как защитить старшего брата главной героини","保护女主角哥哥的方法","ロクサナ〜悪女がヒロインの兄を守る方法〜","ฉันขอปกป้องพี่ชายนางเอก"],"title":{"english":"Roxana","native":"여주인공의 오빠를 지키는 방법","romaji":"Yeojuingongui Oppareul Jikineun Bangbeop","userPreferred":"Yeojuingongui Oppareul Jikineun Bangbeop"},"type":"MANGA"}}},{"node":{"mediaRecommendation":{"bannerImage":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/manga/banner/114542-4jysXXJd2vim.jpg","countryOfOrigin":"KR","coverImage":{"color":"#e4505d","extraLarge":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/manga/cover/large/bx114542-3fUNOX8DqS5e.jpg","large":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/manga/cover/medium/bx114542-3fUNOX8DqS5e.jpg","medium":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/manga/cover/small/bx114542-3fUNOX8DqS5e.jpg"},"description":"Tensions are brewing under the seemingly calm surface of the Vasilios Empire, a kingdom ruled by the Imperial Family and the Temple. Lady Medea Solon has lost her place next to Crown Prince Eros, but resolves to do whatever it will take to win back what's rightfully hers. Will she reclaim her throne?\n\u003cbr\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\n(Source: WEBTOON)","endDate":{},"format":"MANGA","id":114542,"idMal":130832,"isAdult":false,"meanScore":78,"siteUrl":"https://anilist.co/manga/114542","startDate":{"day":6,"month":1,"year":2020},"status":"HIATUS","synonyms":["I Want to Be You, Just for a Day","I Wanna Be U","La duchesse déchue","Tu trono","Dein Thron","惡女的變身","以你之名","君の全てを奪いたい","ชิงชีวิตพลิกลิขิตชะตา"],"title":{"english":"Your Throne","native":"하루만 네가 되고 싶어","romaji":"Haruman Nega Doego Sipeo","userPreferred":"Haruman Nega Doego Sipeo"},"type":"MANGA"}}},{"node":{"mediaRecommendation":{"bannerImage":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/manga/banner/117540-qBoIxW9tNXqt.jpg","countryOfOrigin":"KR","coverImage":{"color":"#e4ae5d","extraLarge":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/manga/cover/large/bx117540-RRDXqQJbhWTv.jpg","large":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/manga/cover/medium/bx117540-RRDXqQJbhWTv.jpg","medium":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/manga/cover/small/bx117540-RRDXqQJbhWTv.jpg"},"description":"Sit back and take in this romantic tale of an angelic heroine and her devoted suitors as they vie for the depths of her love... or not. This story’s about to go through some edits! After an accident, a modern-day college student awakens as the story’s villainess, Melissa Foddebrat. She’s far from anyone’s favorite, but she IS the daughter of the duke. Determined to live it up, this new Melissa is doing things her way — antiquated society, be damned! All idiots, prepare to step aside or perish!\n\u003cbr\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\n(Source: Tapas)","endDate":{},"format":"MANGA","id":117540,"idMal":146912,"isAdult":false,"meanScore":77,"siteUrl":"https://anilist.co/manga/117540","startDate":{"day":13,"month":4,"year":2020},"status":"RELEASING","synonyms":["Gare à la vilaine!","その悪女に気をつけてください","小心那个恶女！","恶毒女配今天不营业","ระวังไว้ ยัยตัวร้ายกำลังมา","惡女出沒請小心"],"title":{"english":"Beware the Villainess!","native":"그 악녀를 조심하세요!","romaji":"Geu Angnyeoreul Josimhaseyo!","userPreferred":"Geu Angnyeoreul Josimhaseyo!"},"type":"MANGA"}}},{"node":{"mediaRecommendation":{"chapters":102,"countryOfOrigin":"KR","coverImage":{"color":"#d61a1a","extraLarge":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/manga/cover/large/bx132165-vbmIhwI4JjeZ.jpg","large":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/manga/cover/medium/bx132165-vbmIhwI4JjeZ.jpg","medium":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/manga/cover/small/bx132165-vbmIhwI4JjeZ.jpg"},"description":"Eris Miserian just wants to die. Being overworked and underappreciated in the real world wasn’t great, but living as the villainess in a romance novel is even worse. If Eris can die in the novel, she might be able to return to reality, but the story won’t let her. Desperate to escape a life as the protagonist’s tormentor, she sets off on a journey with the help of a witch, a knight, and a high priest. Can she find her way back to her friends and family, or is Eris doomed to a fictional future?\n\u003cbr\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\n(Source: Tapas)\u003cbr\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\n\u003ci\u003eNote: Includes six extra chapters.\u003c/i\u003e","endDate":{"day":1,"month":1,"year":2024},"format":"MANGA","id":132165,"idMal":148410,"isAdult":false,"meanScore":79,"siteUrl":"https://anilist.co/manga/132165","startDate":{"day":2,"month":4,"year":2021},"status":"FINISHED","synonyms":["Lady Eris – Nur der Tod kann mich erlösen","Matar a la Villana","Töte die Teufelin!","悪女を殺して","殺死惡女","นางร้ายต้องสังหาร","Comment Tuer la Vilaine","Pela Morte da Vilã"],"title":{"english":"Kill the Villainess","native":"악녀를 죽여 줘","romaji":"Angnyeoreul Jugyeo Jwo","userPreferred":"Angnyeoreul Jugyeo Jwo"},"type":"MANGA","volumes":7}}},{"node":{"mediaRecommendation":{"bannerImage":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/manga/banner/104973-TzptXjVKOXqo.jpg","chapters":158,"countryOfOrigin":"KR","coverImage":{"color":"#e4935d","extraLarge":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/manga/cover/large/bx104973-5KZSV2FK9BMt.jpg","large":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/manga/cover/medium/bx104973-5KZSV2FK9BMt.jpg","medium":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/manga/cover/small/bx104973-5KZSV2FK9BMt.jpg"},"description":"Eunha Park was just a regular girl desperate to get into college, but when she finally does, her elation is cut short as she's pushed off a roof—only to wake up as Raeliana McMillan, a character from a novel whose death serves as the catalyst for the story's events. But Raeliana refuses to die a second time and is determined to change her fate, no matter what!\u003cbr\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\n(Source: Yen Press)","endDate":{"day":22,"month":3,"year":2021},"format":"MANGA","id":104973,"idMal":118646,"isAdult":false,"meanScore":81,"siteUrl":"https://anilist.co/manga/104973","startDate":{"day":3,"month":9,"year":2017},"status":"FINISHED","synonyms":["Why Raeliana Ended Up at the Duke's Mansion","Cómo Raeliana acabó en la mansión del Duque","Raeliana – Warum sie die Verlobte des Dukes wurde","Comment j'ai survécu au Manoir Wynknight","彼女が公爵邸に行った理由","Kanojo ga Koushaku Yashiki ni itta Riyuu","公爵的契约未婚妻","Vị Hôn Thê Khế Ước Của Công Tước","彼女が公爵邸に行った理由","พระเอกของฉันเป็นท่านดยุค","Реліана: Наречена герцога за контрактом","Tunangan Kontrak Duke","Okoliczności, które sprawiły, że Raeliana trafiła do posiadłości diuka"],"title":{"english":"The Reason Why Raeliana Ended Up at the Duke's Mansion","native":"그녀가 공작저로 가야 했던 사정","romaji":"Geunyeoga Gongjakjeoro Gaya Haetdeon Sajeong","userPreferred":"Geunyeoga Gongjakjeoro Gaya Haetdeon Sajeong"},"type":"MANGA","volumes":9}}},{"node":{"mediaRecommendation":{"bannerImage":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/manga/banner/119523-ZUzP5PjSYjWk.jpg","chapters":230,"countryOfOrigin":"KR","coverImage":{"color":"#4393f1","extraLarge":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/manga/cover/large/bx119523-5OBKEF4D4Zfj.jpg","large":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/manga/cover/medium/bx119523-5OBKEF4D4Zfj.jpg","medium":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/manga/cover/small/bx119523-5OBKEF4D4Zfj.jpg"},"description":"From childhood, Artezia Rosan's happiness was dependent on ensuring the success of her brother. As a master manipulator and schemer, she became his most valuable ally in seizing the empire’s throne. That’s exactly why her brother's betrayal cut so deeply when Artezia was imprisoned as punishment for all of her crimes. Soon after being rescued by Grand Duke Cedric Ebron, she vows to help him overthrow the cruel new emperor by sacrificing her own life with forbidden magic. Now waking up several years earlier back in time, she will forsake her own family to help Cedric at all costs. They say that blood is thicker than water, but can Artezia destroy her brother while her own romance blossoms amidst the chaos? \n\u003cbr\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\n(Source: Tappytoon)","endDate":{"day":6,"month":1,"year":2025},"format":"MANGA","id":119523,"idMal":147205,"isAdult":false,"meanScore":72,"siteUrl":"https://anilist.co/manga/119523","startDate":{"day":3,"month":6,"year":2020},"status":"FINISHED","synonyms":["The Villainess Lives Twice","ชีวิตที่สองของนางร้าย","惡女重生"],"title":{"english":"The Villainess Lives Again","native":"악녀는 두 번 산다","romaji":"Agnyeoneun du Beon Sanda","userPreferred":"Agnyeoneun du Beon Sanda"},"type":"MANGA"}}},{"node":{"mediaRecommendation":{"countryOfOrigin":"KR","coverImage":{"color":"#782843","extraLarge":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/manga/cover/large/bx124458-F95rVuirXEmZ.jpg","large":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/manga/cover/medium/bx124458-F95rVuirXEmZ.jpg","medium":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/manga/cover/small/bx124458-F95rVuirXEmZ.jpg"},"description":"I woke up in a strange bed, with not just one, but two lovers beside me! In this game of love, affection, and deception, I’m Elvia, the Imperial Princess, with a gaggle of men vying for my favor. Sounds great, right? Except this means I'm also stuck as the villainess while the main character is my manipulative maid, Arielle! She’s out to bring me down, and she’s got plans for my harem of men. But I know all her secrets, because I can see her player notifications. Can I beat her at her own game?\n\u003cbr\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\n(Source: Tapas)","endDate":{},"format":"MANGA","id":124458,"idMal":147741,"isAdult":false,"meanScore":70,"siteUrl":"https://anilist.co/manga/124458","startDate":{"day":4,"month":9,"year":2020},"status":"HIATUS","synonyms":["It Looks Like I've Fallen Into the World of a Reverse Harem Game","It Looks Like It Fell Into a Reverse Harem Game  "],"title":{"english":"I Fell into a Reverse Harem Game!","native":"역하렘 게임 속으로 떨어진 모양입니다","romaji":"Yeok Harem Game Sogeuro Tteoreojin Moyangimnida","userPreferred":"Yeok Harem Game Sogeuro Tteoreojin Moyangimnida"},"type":"MANGA"}}}]},"relations":{},"siteUrl":"https://anilist.co/manga/118408"}},"updated_at":"2026-03-07T00:47:35.339792+03:00"},"120980":{"value":{"Media":{"characters":{"edges":[{"id":360012,"node":{"age":"15-","dateOfBirth":{},"description":"He was a member of the Cheon Family and was the son of a female servant who worked at the Lord’s chamber and was not from the Six Clans. Although considered as an illegitimate son of the Lord due to a servant mother, he was still part of the Cheon family and he had the right to the throne but had an extremely low chance without support. \n\nHe doesn't learn any martial arts in his early 15 years due to his oath with the Lord's wives from Six Clans. After entering the Demonic Academy, only then did he learn Martial Arts and have an unimaginable growth rate due to Nano Machine'a support.","gender":"Male","id":267544,"image":{"large":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/character/large/b267544-Rij5JmLpbnQa.png"},"isFavourite":false,"name":{"alternative":["Seventh Prince"],"full":"Yeo-Un Cheon","native":"천여운"},"siteUrl":"https://anilist.co/character/267544"},"role":"MAIN"},{"id":380891,"node":{"dateOfBirth":{},"description":"Won-Ryeo Cheon was the Sound Clan candidate for the throne.\n~!She was the first heir candidate to be eliminated.!~","gender":"Female","id":283641,"image":{"large":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/character/large/b283641-jSI5Hc91WQpO.png"},"isFavourite":false,"name":{"full":"Won-Ryeo Cheon","native":"천원려"},"siteUrl":"https://anilist.co/character/283641"},"role":"SUPPORTING"},{"id":458654,"node":{"dateOfBirth":{},"description":"Coming from the Gentle Kick Clan, he is one of the most trusted followers of Cheon Yeo-Woon.","gender":"Male","id":319324,"image":{"large":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/character/large/b319324-8ZLpwvLlmPmv.jpg"},"isFavourite":false,"name":{"full":"Baek-Gi","native":"백기"},"siteUrl":"https://anilist.co/character/319324"},"role":"SUPPORTING"},{"id":380884,"node":{"dateOfBirth":{},"description":"The Right Guardian of the Demonic Cult. His nickname is Crazy Blade, due to his drunkard-like and unpredictable blade skills. He is the first Teacher Yeo-Woon Cheon had in his martial arts journey.","gender":"Male","id":283634,"image":{"large":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/character/large/b283634-GFxiXQYu6GmZ.png"},"isFavourite":false,"name":{"alternative":["Meng Seob","Crazy Blade"],"full":"Maeng Seop","native":"섭맹"},"siteUrl":"https://anilist.co/character/283634"},"role":"SUPPORTING"},{"id":380892,"node":{"dateOfBirth":{},"description":"Jong-Seom Cheon was the Poison Clan candidate for the throne.","gender":"Male","id":283642,"image":{"large":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/character/large/b283642-28MVTHCel2ti.png"},"isFavourite":false,"name":{"full":"Jong-Seom Cheon","native":"천종섬"},"siteUrl":"https://anilist.co/character/283642"},"role":"SUPPORTING"},{"id":495114,"node":{"dateOfBirth":{},"description":"She is the daughter of Wang Jeon, one of the Five Greatest Martial Artists.","gender":"Female","id":340677,"image":{"large":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/character/large/b340677-04Wk6uF5xvYZ.jpg"},"isFavourite":false,"name":{"full":"Yeo-Gun Wang","native":"왕여군"},"siteUrl":"https://anilist.co/character/340677"},"role":"SUPPORTING"},{"id":380885,"node":{"dateOfBirth":{},"description":"Ga-Gyeong Jang was the parental figure of Yeo-Woon Cheon's early life and served Lady Hwa until she died. He went to crown Yeo-Woon as the Lord of the Demonic Cult during his Coronation Ceremony.","gender":"Male","id":283635,"image":{"large":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/character/large/b283635-6XXmYALszyIN.png"},"isFavourite":false,"name":{"alternative":["Guard Jang"],"full":"Ga-Gyeong Jang","native":"장가경"},"siteUrl":"https://anilist.co/character/283635"},"role":"SUPPORTING"},{"id":380893,"node":{"dateOfBirth":{},"description":"~!Lady Baek is the one who asked the Poison Clan to poison Lady Hwa, Yeo-Woon's mother.!~","gender":"Female","id":283643,"image":{"large":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/character/large/b283643-z0fPrhw6Y0Vx.png"},"isFavourite":false,"name":{"alternative":["Lady Baek"],"full":"Baek"},"siteUrl":"https://anilist.co/character/283643"},"role":"SUPPORTING"},{"id":495115,"node":{"dateOfBirth":{},"description":"She was one of the twelve expert martial artists from the Demonic Cult that were tasked to protect the Kirin blood.","gender":"Female","id":340678,"image":{"large":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/character/large/b340678-V870jL6x2BFt.jpg"},"isFavourite":false,"name":{"full":"Ran-Yeong Mun","native":"문란영"},"siteUrl":"https://anilist.co/character/340678"},"role":"SUPPORTING"},{"id":380886,"node":{"dateOfBirth":{},"description":"Gyu Mun is the female protagonist of Nano Machine. She is the granddaughter of Yun Mun, one of the elders of the Demonic Cult. She is a part of Yeo-Woon Cheon's team during their stay in the Demonic Academy. ~!She is Yeo-Woon's future first wife.!~","gender":"Female","id":283636,"image":{"large":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/character/large/b283636-Z1R6el5KD4id.png"},"isFavourite":false,"name":{"alternative":["Cadet 408"],"full":"Mun-Gyu","native":"문규"},"siteUrl":"https://anilist.co/character/283636"},"role":"SUPPORTING"},{"id":380894,"node":{"dateOfBirth":{},"description":"Mu-Hwa Yeon is the 2nd Council Elder of the Demonic Cult (Formerly 10th) as well as the only female elder aside from Soyu Hang. ~!Later, she was acknowledged as the true successor of the Sword Demon lineage.!~","gender":"Female","id":283644,"image":{"large":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/character/large/b283644-iP1pnjVnsIWE.png"},"isFavourite":false,"name":{"full":"Mu-Hwa Yeon","native":"연무화"},"siteUrl":"https://anilist.co/character/283644"},"role":"SUPPORTING"},{"id":527040,"node":{"dateOfBirth":{},"description":"He is Cheon Yeo-Un's first subordinate.","gender":"Male","id":361210,"image":{"large":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/character/large/b361210-28BY8nt1WOpy.png"},"isFavourite":false,"name":{"full":"Heo-Bong","native":"허봉"},"siteUrl":"https://anilist.co/character/361210"},"role":"SUPPORTING"},{"id":380887,"node":{"dateOfBirth":{},"description":"Lady Hwa (Yeon Hwa) was Yeo-Woon Cheon's Mother and the Seventh wife of Cheon-Yu Jong. She was poisoned and died when Yeo-Woon was little. ~!Later on, it was revealed by Jong-Seom Cheon that the one who poisoned her was Lady Mu.!~","gender":"Female","id":283637,"image":{"large":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/character/large/b283637-SryWfSsFpdDA.png"},"isFavourite":false,"name":{"alternative":["Lady Hwa"],"full":"Yeon Hwa","native":"화연"},"siteUrl":"https://anilist.co/character/283637"},"role":"SUPPORTING"},{"id":380895,"node":{"dateOfBirth":{},"description":"She is the head of the Sound Clan and the 5th Council Elder but was later demoted to the 11th Elder of the Demonic Cult.","gender":"Female","id":283645,"image":{"large":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/character/large/b283645-mfELhPO7oqH6.png"},"isFavourite":false,"name":{"full":"Soyu Hang","native":"항소유"},"siteUrl":"https://anilist.co/character/283645"},"role":"SUPPORTING"},{"id":527041,"node":{"dateOfBirth":{},"description":"He is the head of the Demonic Academy.","gender":"Male","id":361211,"image":{"large":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/character/large/b361211-6o8WstQbRZ8i.jpg"},"isFavourite":false,"name":{"alternative":["Left Guardian","Fire King"],"full":"Hwa-Myeong Lee"},"siteUrl":"https://anilist.co/character/361211"},"role":"SUPPORTING"},{"id":380888,"node":{"dateOfBirth":{},"description":"Mu-Yeon Cheon is the son of Lord Yu-Jong Cheon from the Dark Clan and had been deemed the most likely to succeed the throne during the start of Demonic Academy.","gender":"Male","id":283638,"image":{"large":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/character/large/b283638-BBRbjHwt1TKZ.png"},"isFavourite":false,"name":{"full":"Mu-Yeon Cheon","native":"천무연"},"siteUrl":"https://anilist.co/character/283638"},"role":"SUPPORTING"},{"id":380896,"node":{"dateOfBirth":{},"description":"She is the first female warrior who joined Yeo-Woon Cheon in the Demonic Academy and one of his Six Swords. She joined him because of his strength and his character as a leader.","gender":"Female","id":283646,"image":{"large":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/character/large/b283646-gwOCpLOSvczk.png"},"isFavourite":false,"name":{"full":"Sang-Hwa Ho","native":"호상화"},"siteUrl":"https://anilist.co/character/283646"},"role":"SUPPORTING"},{"id":527042,"node":{"dateOfBirth":{},"gender":"Male","id":361212,"image":{"large":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/character/large/b361212-fZuqD3uTSXkH.jpg"},"isFavourite":false,"name":{"alternative":["Grand Guardian","Great Guardian"],"full":"Hobeopga","native":"호법가"},"siteUrl":"https://anilist.co/character/361212"},"role":"SUPPORTING"},{"id":380889,"node":{"dateOfBirth":{},"description":"Gyeong-Un Cheon is the heir candidate from the Sword Clan and one of the Top 3 candidates that were most likely to succeed the throne.","gender":"Male","id":283639,"image":{"large":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/character/large/b283639-AqQbtHh45ia8.png"},"isFavourite":false,"name":{"full":"Gyeong-Un Cheon","native":"천경운"},"siteUrl":"https://anilist.co/character/283639"},"role":"SUPPORTING"},{"id":380897,"node":{"dateOfBirth":{},"description":"~!Blade God is the main antagonist. He is from a future timeline and is the originator of the Extreme Art of the Blade God in the current timeline. He is the founder of the Blade God Six Martial Clan.!~","gender":"Male","id":283647,"image":{"large":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/character/large/b283647-1RPeIPYRAehu.png"},"isFavourite":false,"name":{"alternative":["Blade God"],"full":"Geukdosin","native":"극도신"},"siteUrl":"https://anilist.co/character/283647"},"role":"SUPPORTING"},{"id":527043,"node":{"dateOfBirth":{},"description":"He is from the upper sect of the Magic Sword Sect and is a master of martial arts. He is the first of the six swords.\n\n~!In a relationship with Ho Sang-Hwa!~","gender":"Male","id":361213,"image":{"large":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/character/large/b361213-Kv2IewJ3OZJd.png"},"isFavourite":false,"name":{"full":"Wang-Heul Go","native":"고왕흘"},"siteUrl":"https://anilist.co/character/361213"},"role":"SUPPORTING"},{"id":380890,"node":{"dateOfBirth":{},"description":"Mu-Geum Cheon is the Spring Clan candidate for the throne.","gender":"Male","id":283640,"image":{"large":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/character/large/b283640-lhcgnm4ztYvT.png"},"isFavourite":false,"name":{"full":"Mu-Geum Cheon","native":"천무금"},"siteUrl":"https://anilist.co/character/283640"},"role":"SUPPORTING"},{"id":380898,"node":{"dateOfBirth":{},"description":"Yu-Jong Cheon is the Lord of the Demonic Cult and the Father of Yeo-Woon Cheon. He was one of the Top Five Strongest Masters in the entire Murim and succeeded in the title 'Southern Demon Lord' after Inji Cheon.","gender":"Male","id":283648,"image":{"large":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/character/large/b283648-RSJhMKX1fipf.png"},"isFavourite":false,"name":{"alternative":["South Demon Lord"],"full":"Yu-Jong Cheon","native":"천유종"},"siteUrl":"https://anilist.co/character/283648"},"role":"SUPPORTING"},{"id":548138,"node":{"dateOfBirth":{},"gender":"Male","id":379605,"image":{"large":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/character/large/b379605-Nkvko3KqaROf.jpg"},"isFavourite":false,"name":{"full":"Agui","native":"악의"},"siteUrl":"https://anilist.co/character/379605"},"role":"SUPPORTING"}]},"genres":["Action","Adventure","Fantasy","Sci-Fi"],"id":120980,"rankings":[{"allTime":true,"context":"highest rated all time","format":"MANGA","rank":262,"type":"RATED"},{"allTime":true,"context":"most popular all time","format":"MANGA","rank":134,"type":"POPULAR"},{"allTime":false,"context":"highest rated","format":"MANGA","rank":14,"type":"RATED","year":2020},{"allTime":false,"context":"most popular","format":"MANGA","rank":10,"type":"POPULAR","year":2020}],"recommendations":{"edges":[{"node":{"mediaRecommendation":{"bannerImage":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/manga/banner/132144-tITrsibdFo3n.jpg","countryOfOrigin":"KR","coverImage":{"color":"#e45078","extraLarge":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/manga/cover/large/bx132144-i5B4VnG9sRgh.png","large":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/manga/cover/medium/bx132144-i5B4VnG9sRgh.png","medium":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/manga/cover/small/bx132144-i5B4VnG9sRgh.png"},"description":"When Cheong-Myeong of the Mount Hua Sect awakens a hundred years in the future, his last memories are of a bloody battle against the Leader of the Demonic Cult, the evil Cheon-Ma. The battle almost saw the end of the Ten Great Sects of ancient China, when Cheong-Myeong ended the hard-fought struggle by striking down Cheon-Ma. Soon after, he succumbed to his wounds, filled with regret at their pyrrhic victory. All is not lost, however, as he awakens to his second chance at life. Shocked to find his beloved Mount Hua Sect reduced to a mere shadow of itself in the present day, Cheong-Myeong embarks on a journey to restore Mount Hua to its former glory.\u003cbr\u003e\n\u003cbr\u003e\n(Source: WEBTOON, edited)","endDate":{},"format":"MANGA","id":132144,"idMal":146878,"isAdult":false,"meanScore":84,"siteUrl":"https://anilist.co/manga/132144","startDate":{"day":23,"month":3,"year":2021},"status":"HIATUS","synonyms":["Return of The Mount Hua Sect","Return of the Flowery Mountain Sect","Le retour du clan Hwasan","El retorno del Monte Hua","劍尊歸來","หวนคืนสู่ฮวาซาน","剑尊归来"],"title":{"english":"Return of the Blossoming Blade","native":"화산귀환","romaji":"Hwasangwihwan","userPreferred":"Hwasangwihwan"},"type":"MANGA"}}},{"node":{"mediaRecommendation":{"bannerImage":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/manga/banner/105398-4UrEhdqZukrg.jpg","chapters":201,"countryOfOrigin":"KR","coverImage":{"extraLarge":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/manga/cover/large/bx105398-b673Vt5ZSuz3.jpg","large":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/manga/cover/medium/bx105398-b673Vt5ZSuz3.jpg","medium":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/manga/cover/small/bx105398-b673Vt5ZSuz3.jpg"},"description":"In a world where awakened beings called “Hunters” must battle deadly monsters to protect humanity, Seong Jin-U, nicknamed “the weakest hunter of all mankind,” finds himself in a constant struggle for survival. One day, after a brutal encounter in an overpowered dungeon wipes out his party and threatens to end his life, a mysterious System chooses him as its sole player: Jin-U has been granted the rare opportunity to level up his abilities, possibly beyond any known limits. Follow Jin-U’s journey as he takes on ever-stronger enemies, both human and monster, to discover the secrets deep within the dungeons and the ultimate extent of his powers.\n\u003cbr\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\n(Source: Tappytoon)\n\u003cbr\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\n\u003ci\u003eNote: Includes 22 extra chapters.\u003c/i\u003e","endDate":{"day":31,"month":5,"year":2023},"format":"MANGA","id":105398,"idMal":121496,"isAdult":false,"meanScore":84,"siteUrl":"https://anilist.co/manga/105398","startDate":{"day":4,"month":3,"year":2018},"status":"FINISHED","synonyms":["I Level Up Alone","Only I Level Up","俺だけレベルアップな件","我獨自升級","Ore dake Level Up na Ken","Поднятие уровня в одиночку","Тільки я візьму новий рівень"],"title":{"english":"Solo Leveling","native":"나 혼자만 레벨업","romaji":"Na Honjaman Level Up","userPreferred":"Na Honjaman Level Up"},"type":"MANGA","volumes":15}}},{"node":{"mediaRecommendation":{"bannerImage":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/manga/banner/107518-s3Ob9xlcAobb.jpg","chapters":252,"countryOfOrigin":"KR","coverImage":{"color":"#f1505d","extraLarge":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/manga/cover/large/bx107518-mIYnC1TQIe4P.png","large":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/manga/cover/medium/bx107518-mIYnC1TQIe4P.png","medium":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/manga/cover/small/bx107518-mIYnC1TQIe4P.png"},"description":"In an ancient world where martial artists reign supreme, Un-Seong can only watch as his master is brutally beaten to death after a false accusation of practicing forbidden demonic arts. Even after a valiant fight, he fails to kill those responsible and faces his own end. But fate has other plans… Instead of taking his last breath, he awakens as a child, training to be an elite soldier of a demonic sect. Now Un-Seong must embrace the demonic arts and harness power in his ultimate quest for revenge.\n\u003cbr\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\n(Source: Tapas)\u003cbr\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\n\u003ci\u003eNote: Includes six extra chapters.\u003c/i\u003e","endDate":{"day":8,"month":1,"year":2025},"format":"MANGA","id":107518,"idMal":147572,"isAdult":false,"meanScore":77,"siteUrl":"https://anilist.co/manga/107518","startDate":{"day":14,"month":8,"year":2018},"status":"FINISHED","synonyms":["Chronicles of Heavenly Demon"],"title":{"english":"Heavenly Demon Reborn!","native":"신마경천기","romaji":"Shinma Gyeongcheongi","userPreferred":"Shinma Gyeongcheongi"},"type":"MANGA"}}},{"node":{"mediaRecommendation":{"countryOfOrigin":"KR","coverImage":{"color":"#7843e4","extraLarge":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/manga/cover/large/bx120385-4JYGuOR6cn72.jpg","large":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/manga/cover/medium/bx120385-4JYGuOR6cn72.jpg","medium":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/manga/cover/small/bx120385-4JYGuOR6cn72.jpg"},"description":"When an interdimensional portal appeared and released countless monsters across the world, humanity didn’t take the threat lying down. Mankind fought back, defeating the monsters' Demon King and creating a new way of life as \"hunters.\" But when Taekyung Jin, a struggling, low-ranked hunter, accidentally logs into a game on a beat-up VR console, he finds himself trapped in an all-new world, unable to log out.\n\u003cbr\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\n(Source: Tapas)","endDate":{},"format":"MANGA","id":120385,"idMal":147389,"isAdult":false,"meanScore":80,"siteUrl":"https://anilist.co/manga/120385","startDate":{"day":1,"month":5,"year":2020},"status":"HIATUS","synonyms":["Murim Login","ログイン武林","登录武林系统"],"title":{"english":"Log-in Murim","native":"로그인 무림","romaji":"Login Murim","userPreferred":"Login Murim"},"type":"MANGA"}}},{"node":{"mediaRecommendation":{"bannerImage":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/manga/banner/119521-CPhjvDuMReVg.jpg","chapters":202,"countryOfOrigin":"KR","coverImage":{"extraLarge":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/manga/cover/large/bx119521-qYqxFvn0NnXo.png","large":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/manga/cover/medium/bx119521-qYqxFvn0NnXo.png","medium":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/manga/cover/small/bx119521-qYqxFvn0NnXo.png"},"description":"For decades, the brave warriors of the Northern Heavenly Sect fought to keep the world safe from the evil Silent Night. But when the fourth generation leader is accused of colluding with the enemy, he is forced to disband the sect and commit suicide to protect his son, Moo-Won. With no family and allies left, Moo-Won leads a dreary life under close surveillance... until a surprise attack from the Silent Night gives him a chance to escape to the mountains. There, the young warrior trains to master the fighting techniques of his predecessors, before the mysterious disappearance of a loved one brings him back to the mainland. Follow Moo-Won as he embarks on a journey to avenge his father’s death and take down the villains who threaten to plunge the world into darkness! \u003cbr\u003e\n\u003cbr\u003e\n(Source: Tappytoon)\n","endDate":{"day":19,"month":11,"year":2024},"format":"MANGA","id":119521,"idMal":134744,"isAdult":false,"meanScore":85,"siteUrl":"https://anilist.co/manga/119521","startDate":{"day":31,"month":12,"year":2019},"status":"FINISHED","synonyms":["北剑江湖"],"title":{"english":"The Legend of the Northern Blade","native":"북검전기","romaji":"Bukgeom Jeongi","userPreferred":"Bukgeom Jeongi"},"type":"MANGA"}}},{"node":{"mediaRecommendation":{"countryOfOrigin":"KR","coverImage":{"color":"#936b1a","extraLarge":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/manga/cover/medium/b120907-K1LMQMdOqaDC.png","large":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/manga/cover/medium/b120907-K1LMQMdOqaDC.png","medium":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/manga/cover/small/b120907-K1LMQMdOqaDC.png"},"description":"The son of a lowly innkeeper, U-Mun Song always dreamed of being a martial arts master, a dream that would never become a reality thanks to his frail body. Then one night, a mysterious guest leaves behind a painting as payment that enthralls U-Mun for reasons he can’t explain. It soon becomes clear that it’s no ordinary painting when U-Mun starts showing prowess in the martial arts he’s never had before. Thus begins the path for a scatterbrained kid to change his destiny and become truly undefeatable!\n\u003cbr\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\n(Source: Tapas, edited)","endDate":{},"format":"MANGA","id":120907,"idMal":184976,"isAdult":false,"meanScore":72,"siteUrl":"https://anilist.co/manga/120907","startDate":{"day":30,"month":6,"year":2020},"status":"RELEASING","title":{"english":"The Undefeatable Swordsman","native":"불패검선","romaji":"Bulpaegeomseon","userPreferred":"Bulpaegeomseon"},"type":"MANGA"}}},{"node":{"mediaRecommendation":{"countryOfOrigin":"KR","coverImage":{"color":"#a13528","extraLarge":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/manga/cover/medium/b134635-iybRMnRnktOQ.jpg","large":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/manga/cover/medium/b134635-iybRMnRnktOQ.jpg","medium":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/manga/cover/small/b134635-iybRMnRnktOQ.jpg"},"description":"Killed on the battlefield without glory to his name, Yuseong Dan receives an opportunity to grow stronger with a strange quest and level system. But each quest he’s forced to fight only seems to be getting harder and harder. Can he level up enough to avoid the same miserable ending and become the powerful hero he wishes to be? \n\u003cbr\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\n(Source: WEBTOON)","endDate":{},"format":"MANGA","id":134635,"idMal":184860,"isAdult":false,"meanScore":77,"siteUrl":"https://anilist.co/manga/134635","startDate":{"day":21,"month":4,"year":2020},"status":"RELEASING","synonyms":["Infinite Level up in Murim","Unlimited Level-ups in Murim"],"title":{"english":"Infinite Leveling: Murim","native":"무한 레벨업 in 무림","romaji":"Muhan Level Up in Murim","userPreferred":"Muhan Level Up in Murim"},"type":"MANGA"}}},{"node":{"mediaRecommendation":{"bannerImage":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/manga/banner/151460-zE0YRolZcxEq.jpg","countryOfOrigin":"KR","coverImage":{"color":"#d6ae6b","extraLarge":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/manga/cover/large/bx151460-Cb2CXwN2ZElE.jpg","large":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/manga/cover/medium/bx151460-Cb2CXwN2ZElE.jpg","medium":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/manga/cover/small/bx151460-Cb2CXwN2ZElE.jpg"},"description":"For as long as he can remember, Woonhwi So has been the black sheep of his family and clan. Because his spirit core has been destroyed, he has no choice but to serve as a third-rate spy for the Blood Cult. One day, during his mission to find the legendary Blade Scroll, he is killed and sent 10 years into the past. When Woonhwi regains consciousness, he realizes that he has been sent back to the day he was kidnapped by the Blood Cult, and that he has gained a mysterious ability to hear the voice of a dagger.\n\u003cbr\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\n(Source: WEBTOON)","endDate":{},"format":"MANGA","id":151460,"idMal":149880,"isAdult":false,"meanScore":77,"siteUrl":"https://anilist.co/manga/151460","startDate":{"day":19,"month":6,"year":2022},"status":"RELEASING","synonyms":["Perfect Sword Sense","Le Sens de l'épée","绝对剑感","เซียนสัมผัสดาบ"],"title":{"english":"Absolute Sword Sense","native":"절대검감","romaji":"Jeoldaegeomgam","userPreferred":"Jeoldaegeomgam"},"type":"MANGA"}}}]},"relations":{"edges":[{"node":{"countryOfOrigin":"KR","coverImage":{"color":"#ffe435","extraLarge":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/manga/cover/large/bx175946-rx6eIfakvWYV.jpg","large":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/manga/cover/medium/bx175946-rx6eIfakvWYV.jpg","medium":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/manga/cover/small/bx175946-rx6eIfakvWYV.jpg"},"description":"All Jeong wants is a second chance – for revenge! His grandfather’s gruesome death has transformed him into the bloodthirsty and ruthless Scythe Demon. He will stop at nothing until he has killed the man responsible. Yet rage and determination alone are not enough. He must train in martial arts if he ever wants to stand a chance against such a formidable foe. Will he succeed in his revenge on the murderer of his grandfather?\n\u003cbr\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\n(Source: WEBTOON)","endDate":{},"format":"MANGA","genres":["Action","Fantasy"],"id":175946,"idMal":168980,"isAdult":false,"meanScore":83,"siteUrl":"https://anilist.co/manga/175946","startDate":{"day":4,"month":3,"year":2024},"status":"RELEASING","synonyms":["The Chaotic God of Extraordinary Strength","怪力 亂神","ลับลางลวง"],"title":{"english":"Myst, Might, Mayhem","native":"괴력 난신","romaji":"Goeryeok Nansin","userPreferred":"Goeryeok Nansin"},"type":"MANGA"},"relationType":"OTHER"}]},"siteUrl":"https://anilist.co/manga/120980"}},"updated_at":"2026-03-10T19:51:17.043955+03:00"},"124090":{"value":{"Media":{"characters":{"edges":[{"id":274059,"node":{"id":204937,"isFavourite":false,"gender":"Male","dateOfBirth":{},"name":{"full":"Seung-Ho","native":"승호"},"image":{"large":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/character/large/b204937-JDjokegYPuoc.jpg"},"description":"An ordinary young man who is living with his first love, [Min-Ha](https://anilist.co/character/204939).","siteUrl":"https://anilist.co/character/204937"},"role":"MAIN"},{"id":274060,"node":{"id":204938,"isFavourite":false,"gender":"Female","dateOfBirth":{},"name":{"full":"Jae-Eun","native":"재은"},"image":{"large":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/character/large/b204938-jTn6wb7WK5b1.jpg"},"description":"[Seung-Ho](https://anilist.co/character/204937)'s boss who joined the company at an early age.","siteUrl":"https://anilist.co/character/204938"},"role":"MAIN"},{"id":274061,"node":{"id":204939,"isFavourite":false,"gender":"Female","dateOfBirth":{},"name":{"full":"Min-Ha","native":"민하"},"image":{"large":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/character/large/b204939-jZqxxNCREdgj.jpg"},"description":"[Seung-Ho](https://anilist.co/character/204937)'s girlfriend. She's sexy and lovely, but she's immature.","siteUrl":"https://anilist.co/character/204939"},"role":"MAIN"},{"id":274062,"node":{"id":204940,"isFavourite":false,"gender":"Female","dateOfBirth":{},"name":{"full":"Yu-Seon","native":"유선"},"image":{"large":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/character/large/b204940-U6MHbYRAP3b4.jpg"},"description":"[Seung-Ho](https://anilist.co/character/204937)'s co-worker.","siteUrl":"https://anilist.co/character/204940"},"role":"SUPPORTING"}]},"genres":["Drama","Hentai","Romance","Slice of Life"],"id":124090,"recommendations":{"edges":[{"node":{"mediaRecommendation":{"bannerImage":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/manga/banner/131769-yFZ4WVK1hF75.jpg","chapters":216,"countryOfOrigin":"KR","coverImage":{"color":"#f1bbae","extraLarge":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/manga/cover/large/bx131769-3YLy2cLklJ68.jpg","large":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/manga/cover/medium/bx131769-3YLy2cLklJ68.jpg","medium":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/manga/cover/small/bx131769-3YLy2cLklJ68.jpg"},"description":"This college's drama club puts on huge productions. And the audiences they draw rival Broadway. But I don't know if these guys are showing up for the plays. It might be for the big-titted goddesses putting them on...\u003cbr\u003e\u003cbr\u003e(Source: TOPTOON+)\u003cbr\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\n\u003ci\u003eNote: Includes one extra chapter.\u003c/i\u003e","endDate":{"day":19,"month":5,"year":2025},"format":"MANGA","id":131769,"isAdult":true,"meanScore":82,"siteUrl":"https://anilist.co/manga/131769","startDate":{"day":30,"month":11,"year":2020},"status":"FINISHED","synonyms":["Circles","社團學姊"],"title":{"english":"Drama Queens","native":"동아리","romaji":"Dongari","userPreferred":"Dongari"},"type":"MANGA"}}},{"node":{"mediaRecommendation":{"bannerImage":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/manga/banner/166581-BPwxR2TogKeS.jpg","countryOfOrigin":"KR","coverImage":{"color":"#e4935d","extraLarge":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/manga/cover/large/bx166581-3t6eAWLE5waV.jpg","large":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/manga/cover/medium/bx166581-3t6eAWLE5waV.jpg","medium":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/manga/cover/small/bx166581-3t6eAWLE5waV.jpg"},"description":"Tae-Yang runs away to the other world after getting caught sleeping with a married woman... The best married woman in this world, and a bed? Can Tae-Yang complete his harem in this other world successfully?\u003cbr\u003e\u003cbr\u003e(Source: DAYcomics)","endDate":{},"format":"MANGA","id":166581,"isAdult":true,"meanScore":78,"siteUrl":"https://anilist.co/manga/166581","startDate":{"day":27,"month":6,"year":2023},"status":"RELEASING","synonyms":["Milf Hunting in Another World","Cazador de milfs de otro mundo","異世界☆人妻ハンター","人妻獵人"],"title":{"english":"MILF Hunter in Another World","native":"이세계 밀프 헌터","romaji":"Isegye Milf Hunter","userPreferred":"Isegye Milf Hunter"},"type":"MANGA"}}},{"node":{"mediaRecommendation":{"bannerImage":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/manga/banner/143608-qIf7FC9sd4IC.jpg","chapters":93,"countryOfOrigin":"KR","coverImage":{"color":"#e46b5d","extraLarge":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/manga/cover/medium/b143608-OTwHdiZF5HEl.jpg","large":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/manga/cover/medium/b143608-OTwHdiZF5HEl.jpg","medium":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/manga/cover/small/b143608-OTwHdiZF5HEl.jpg"},"description":"Da-Hyeon and Da-Sol are sisters, and they suddenly look more stunning than I remember. What's going on now?\u003cbr\u003e\u003cbr\u003e(Source: Toomics, edited)","endDate":{"day":9,"month":3,"year":2023},"format":"MANGA","id":143608,"isAdult":true,"meanScore":75,"siteUrl":"https://anilist.co/manga/143608","startDate":{"day":22,"month":7,"year":2021},"status":"FINISHED","synonyms":["Dorm Room Sisters","พี่สาวครับ...เรามารักกันไหม?"],"title":{"english":"The Late-Bloomers","native":"자취방 누나들","romaji":"Jachwibang Nunadeul","userPreferred":"Jachwibang Nunadeul"},"type":"MANGA"}}},{"node":{"mediaRecommendation":{"chapters":43,"countryOfOrigin":"KR","coverImage":{"color":"#e4aebb","extraLarge":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/manga/cover/large/bx136052-CKmu3CS8grpR.jpg","large":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/manga/cover/medium/bx136052-CKmu3CS8grpR.jpg","medium":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/manga/cover/small/bx136052-CKmu3CS8grpR.jpg"},"description":"A single father raising twins wants nothing but the best for them, but he didn't expect that he'd need breast milk! A beautiful married woman offers to sell them, and things start to get real steamy...\u003cbr\u003e\n\u003cbr\u003e\n(Source: TOPTOON+, edited)","endDate":{"day":30,"month":8,"year":2020},"format":"MANGA","id":136052,"isAdult":true,"meanScore":64,"siteUrl":"https://anilist.co/manga/136052","startDate":{"day":15,"month":12,"year":2019},"status":"FINISHED","synonyms":["A Baby’s Nest"],"title":{"english":"Breastfeeding","native":"젖동냥","romaji":"Jeotdongnyang","userPreferred":"Jeotdongnyang"},"type":"MANGA"}}},{"node":{"mediaRecommendation":{"bannerImage":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/manga/banner/117892-EdtBTzrmqE5S.jpg","chapters":70,"countryOfOrigin":"KR","coverImage":{"color":"#e4ae86","extraLarge":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/manga/cover/medium/b117892-FpzTv3V3gdBN.png","large":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/manga/cover/medium/b117892-FpzTv3V3gdBN.png","medium":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/manga/cover/small/b117892-FpzTv3V3gdBN.png"},"description":"Those girls aren't family! They're gold diggers! I'm not gonna let them mess with me.\n\u003cbr\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\n(Source: Toomics)","endDate":{"day":18,"month":1,"year":2021},"format":"MANGA","id":117892,"isAdult":true,"meanScore":63,"siteUrl":"https://anilist.co/manga/117892","startDate":{"day":4,"month":11,"year":2019},"status":"FINISHED","synonyms":["危機四伏的家庭生活","甘いトラップ","La Coloc de Rêve","(Fast) wie eine Familie"],"title":{"english":"The Perfect Roommates","native":"꽃뱀 길들이기","romaji":"Kkotbaem Gildeurigi","userPreferred":"Kkotbaem Gildeurigi"},"type":"MANGA"}}},{"node":{"mediaRecommendation":{"bannerImage":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/manga/banner/110873-JCSTdNGCbaMV.jpg","chapters":30,"countryOfOrigin":"KR","coverImage":{"color":"#78c9d6","extraLarge":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/manga/cover/large/bx110873-2drJ0HPDdWyF.jpg","large":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/manga/cover/medium/bx110873-2drJ0HPDdWyF.jpg","medium":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/manga/cover/small/bx110873-2drJ0HPDdWyF.jpg"},"description":"After losing all hope of finding love, Ha-eun doesn't see the point of carrying on...until one day, a mysterious being saves her life and promises to make her irresistible to any man. Its method is unorthodox to say the least, but it sure makes her feel good. 2nd Lezhin Comics Big Comic Contest Prize Winner.\u003cbr\u003e\u003cbr\u003e(Source: Lezhin US)","endDate":{"day":16,"month":11,"year":2018},"format":"MANGA","id":110873,"idMal":154809,"isAdult":true,"meanScore":62,"siteUrl":"https://anilist.co/manga/110873","startDate":{"day":18,"month":5,"year":2018},"status":"FINISHED","synonyms":["やわらかな彼","Mon Chéri Tout Mou","Mi amada criatura"],"title":{"english":"My Special Squishy Someone","native":"말랑한 그이","romaji":"Mallanghan Geui","userPreferred":"Mallanghan Geui"},"type":"MANGA"}}},{"node":{"mediaRecommendation":{"bannerImage":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/manga/banner/181155-svl7QAciEaTa.jpg","chapters":54,"countryOfOrigin":"KR","coverImage":{"color":"#e4a15d","extraLarge":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/manga/cover/large/bx181155-JkZjjGIeiWMQ.jpg","large":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/manga/cover/medium/bx181155-JkZjjGIeiWMQ.jpg","medium":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/manga/cover/small/bx181155-JkZjjGIeiWMQ.jpg"},"description":"Orange cats have a reputation for chaos, but not Big Cheese! This clever feline has a mission: play matchmaker and help two clueless souls find love.\u003cbr\u003e\u003cbr\u003e(Source: Toomics)","endDate":{"day":1,"month":8,"year":2025},"format":"MANGA","id":181155,"isAdult":true,"meanScore":70,"siteUrl":"https://anilist.co/manga/181155","startDate":{"day":13,"month":9,"year":2024},"status":"FINISHED","synonyms":["The General is Here!"],"title":{"english":"The Love Meowtchmaker","native":"장군님 나가신다","romaji":"Janggunnim Nagasinda","userPreferred":"Janggunnim Nagasinda"},"type":"MANGA"}}},{"node":{"mediaRecommendation":{"chapters":79,"countryOfOrigin":"KR","coverImage":{"color":"#f1f1bb","extraLarge":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/manga/cover/medium/b112191-Phd9CGDL4Js7.jpg","large":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/manga/cover/medium/b112191-Phd9CGDL4Js7.jpg","medium":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/manga/cover/small/b112191-Phd9CGDL4Js7.jpg"},"description":"He met a beauty on the beach and had a passionate night with her. But it turns out that she was actually his friend's mom! A tale of deception, mystery, and shocking truth. What is really going on? Is anyone who they actually claim to be?\u003cbr\u003e\u003cbr\u003e(Source: DAYcomics)","endDate":{"day":30,"month":5,"year":2019},"format":"MANGA","id":112191,"isAdult":true,"meanScore":70,"siteUrl":"https://anilist.co/manga/112191","startDate":{"day":23,"month":11,"year":2017},"status":"FINISHED","synonyms":["She's The Girl","She～秘密のカノジョ","She：我的魅惑女友"],"title":{"english"