ilistcdn/media/manga/cover/medium/bx111748-Bgn026tOq9Kp.jpg","medium":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/manga/cover/small/bx111748-Bgn026tOq9Kp.jpg"},"description":"We often follow stories of a man at the very top, surrounded by his harem. But what happens when we follow the man behind him, scheming to take it all out from under him? A drama of Machiavellian proportions, what's his is mine now.\u003cbr\u003e\u003cbr\u003e(Source: TOPTOON+)","endDate":{"day":9,"month":2,"year":2022},"format":"MANGA","id":111748,"isAdult":true,"meanScore":75,"siteUrl":"https://anilist.co/manga/111748","startDate":{"day":24,"month":8,"year":2018},"status":"FINISHED","synonyms":["Silent War","生残賭博","衝突"],"title":{"english":"My Kingdom","native":"작은 전쟁","romaji":"Jageun Jeonjaeng","userPreferred":"Jageun Jeonjaeng"},"type":"MANGA"}}},{"node":{"mediaRecommendation":{"bannerImage":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/manga/banner/121476-DmEWCCF7B851.jpg","chapters":73,"countryOfOrigin":"KR","coverImage":{"color":"#e45d5d","extraLarge":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/manga/cover/large/bx121476-PjGqJJSTYzSw.jpg","large":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/manga/cover/medium/bx121476-PjGqJJSTYzSw.jpg","medium":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/manga/cover/small/bx121476-PjGqJJSTYzSw.jpg"},"description":"The most important exam of his life… and Jeong-Seok blew it. Dumped by his girlfriend and rejected by his college of choice, the future looks bleak. But instead of moping, Jeong-Seok checks himself into a boarding cram school for a year. Sealed off from the outside world with nothing but a bunch of stressed-out, horny students for company, things start getting steamy in no time. How distracting! Perhaps some one-on-one lessons with the gorgeous, busty Ms. Kang will help him focus? Study hard, Jeong-Seok. Nice and hard…\u003cbr\u003e\u003cbr\u003e(Source: Lezhin US, edited)\n\u003cbr\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\n\u003ci\u003eNote: Includes two extra chapters.\u003c/i\u003e","endDate":{"day":23,"month":10,"year":2020},"format":"MANGA","id":121476,"idMal":147641,"isAdult":true,"meanScore":76,"siteUrl":"https://anilist.co/manga/121476","startDate":{"day":15,"month":2,"year":2019},"status":"FINISHED","synonyms":["浪人ヘブン〜滑る門には福来る〜"],"title":{"english":"Lucky Guy","native":"재수 좋은 남자","romaji":"Jaesu Joeun Namja","userPreferred":"Jaesu Joeun Namja"},"type":"MANGA"}}},{"node":{"mediaRecommendation":{"bannerImage":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/manga/banner/139257-46vOx44VYMpY.jpg","chapters":140,"countryOfOrigin":"KR","coverImage":{"color":"#e4ae50","extraLarge":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/manga/cover/medium/b139257-xFIGBu0gy9WF.jpg","large":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/manga/cover/medium/b139257-xFIGBu0gy9WF.jpg","medium":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/manga/cover/small/b139257-xFIGBu0gy9WF.jpg"},"description":"Yu-Chan, who's shy when it comes to girls, has to tutor a curious little girl. Little does he know that he'll be teaching her some other things too.\u003cbr\u003e\u003cbr\u003e(Source: Toomics, edited)","endDate":{"day":16,"month":2,"year":2024},"format":"MANGA","id":139257,"isAdult":true,"meanScore":71,"siteUrl":"https://anilist.co/manga/139257","startDate":{"day":7,"month":8,"year":2021},"status":"FINISHED","synonyms":["Private Tutoring in These Trying Times","Private Tutoring in These Difficult Times","Cours et Pandémie","Lektionen im Lockdown","Lecciones mortales durante la pandemia","このご時世に家庭教師","疫情下的家教生活","疫情期间的家教生活"],"title":{"english":"Fatal Lessons in this Pandemic","native":"이 시국에 개인교습","romaji":"I Siguge Gaeingyoseup","userPreferred":"I Siguge Gaeingyoseup"},"type":"MANGA"}}},{"node":{"mediaRecommendation":{"chapters":62,"countryOfOrigin":"KR","coverImage":{"extraLarge":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/manga/cover/medium/b138393-01kRyZfexQr8.png","large":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/manga/cover/medium/b138393-01kRyZfexQr8.png","medium":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/manga/cover/small/b138393-01kRyZfexQr8.png"},"description":"Three girls born between my best friend and my first love. The eldest, she looks just like my first love. The second, she loves to flirt. And the third, young and innocent. My life will never be the same. \u003cbr\u003e\u003cbr\u003e(Source: TOPTOON)","endDate":{"day":18,"month":10,"year":2018},"format":"MANGA","id":138393,"isAdult":true,"meanScore":55,"siteUrl":"https://anilist.co/manga/138393","startDate":{"day":8,"month":5,"year":2017},"status":"FINISHED","synonyms":["Three Sisters","三姐妹","三姉妹"],"title":{"english":"Mamitas","native":"세자매","romaji":"Sejamae","userPreferred":"Sejamae"},"type":"MANGA"}}},{"node":{"mediaRecommendation":{"bannerImage":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/manga/banner/143618-mzaBvr2xHvHu.jpg","chapters":74,"countryOfOrigin":"KR","coverImage":{"color":"#e4aea1","extraLarge":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/manga/cover/large/bx143618-FAQXOmWXWhEl.png","large":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/manga/cover/medium/bx143618-FAQXOmWXWhEl.png","medium":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/manga/cover/small/bx143618-FAQXOmWXWhEl.png"},"description":"Jihoon’s always working. He needs to--there’s rent to pay, tuition to take care of, and hospital bills that need to be sorted out. His money problems don’t end when he gets into university, but he soon finds a way to pull himself up by his bootstraps. His part-time job at the girl’s dorm introduces him to a bunch of rich, spoiled, and sexy girls…all of whom want to have their way with him. Why would he say no? It’s his chance to climb up the social ladder, as well as sleeping with the most alluring girls in the school!\u003cbr\u003e\u003cbr\u003e(Source: Lezhin X)","endDate":{"day":13,"month":3,"year":2022},"format":"MANGA","id":143618,"idMal":160038,"isAdult":true,"meanScore":64,"siteUrl":"https://anilist.co/manga/143618","startDate":