/b122161-TiVVDGIyebvZ.jpg"},"description":"Being hated at work is one thing. Getting falsely accused of peeping is another. Driven to the edge, one man has finally decided to stand up for himself, and get revenge on his female coworkers. They'll all fall eventually. \u003cbr\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\u2028(Source: TOPTOON+)","endDate":{"day":18,"month":11,"year":2024},"format":"MANGA","id":122161,"isAdult":true,"meanScore":77,"siteUrl":"https://anilist.co/manga/122161","startDate":{"day":23,"month":3,"year":2019},"status":"FINISHED","synonyms":["A Wonderful New World","すばらしき新世界","美麗新世界"],"title":{"english":"Brave New World","native":"멋진 신세계","romaji":"Meotjin Sinsegye","userPreferred":"Meotjin Sinsegye"},"type":"MANGA"}}},{"node":{"mediaRecommendation":{"countryOfOrigin":"KR","coverImage":{"color":"#e46b50","extraLarge":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/manga/cover/large/bx176592-iJrPUFotO3LA.jpg","large":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/manga/cover/medium/bx176592-iJrPUFotO3LA.jpg","medium":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/manga/cover/small/bx176592-iJrPUFotO3LA.jpg"},"description":"\u003ci\u003e\"You look like you'd be fun to mess with.\"\u003c/i\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\nThese senior girls treated me like a pet, humiliating me every chance they got. But the tables have turned, and now they find themselves completely submitting to their junior.\u003cbr\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\n\u003ci\u003e\"I'm going to turn this whole relationship upside down. Get on your knees.\"\u003c/i\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\u003cbr\u003e(Source: DAYcomics)","endDate":{},"format":"MANGA","id":176592,"isAdult":true,"meanScore":77,"siteUrl":"https://anilist.co/manga/176592","startDate":{"day":1,"month":4,"year":2024},"status":"RELEASING","synonyms":["Relationship Reversal","Turning It Around","逆転大学性活","玩轉學姊"],"title":{"english":"Power Play","native":"관계역전","romaji":"Gwangyeyeokjeon","userPreferred":"Gwangyeyeokjeon"},"type":"MANGA"}}},{"node":{"mediaRecommendation