 the name of Kuroda-sensei is given a job as the new coach/adviser of the girls lacrosse club in an all female school called Felinus Academy for Girls but... it turns out to be a bumpy ride as he encounters sex fiends among the squad, and his adventures begins as he attempts to gain their respect as adviser.\u003cbr\u003e\n\u003cbr\u003e\n1-6. \u003cb\u003eChapter #1 - #6\u003c/b\u003e (第1話 - 第6話); Comic X-Eros #01, #02, #06, #08, #10, #12\u003cbr\u003e\n* 7. \u003cb\u003e2nd Season!?\u003c/b\u003e (2nd Season!?); Wanimagazine Comics Special \"Anekomori\" kakioroshi\u003cbr\u003e\n* 8. \u003cb\u003eOmake Manga Kumiko-hen\u003c/b\u003e (おまけ漫画久美子編); Joshi Luck! Toranoana Kounyuu Tokuten Shousasshi\u003cbr\u003e\n9. \u003cb\u003eBangai-hen\u003c/b\u003e (番外編); Comic X-Eros #13\u003cbr\u003e\n* 10. \u003cb\u003eAkagi Aya Massage-hen\u003c/b\u003e (赤城綾 マッサージ編); Comic Kairakuten 2014-05\u003cbr\u003e\n* 11-12. \u003cb\u003eAfter School\u003c/b\u003e (After School); Comic X-Eros #19, #21\u003cbr\u003e\n\u003cbr\u003e\n\u003ci\u003eNote: (*) Chapters included in the new edition published on 2018/11/24.\u003c/i\u003e","endDate":{"day":30,"month":5,"year":2015},"format":"MANGA","id":84505,"idMal":54505,"isAdult":true,"meanScore":76,"siteUrl":"https://anilist.co/manga/84505","startDate":{"day":26,"month":11,"year":2012},"status":"FINISHED","synonyms":["Jyoshi Luck!","Joshi Lac!","Girls Lacrosse Club"],"title":{"native":"じょしラク！","romaji":"Joshi Luck!","userPreferred":"Joshi Luck!"},"type":"MANGA","volumes":1}}},{"node":{"mediaRecommendation":{"bannerImage":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/manga/banner/51419-XtFxfr6wmFG7.jpg","chapters":117,"countryOfOrigin":"JP","coverImage":{"color":"#e46b50","extraLarge":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/manga/cover/large/bx51419-MbntyvO82kdm.png","large":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/manga/cover/medium/bx51419-MbntyvO82kdm.png","medium":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/manga/cover/small/bx51419-MbntyvO82kdm.png"},"description":"Tatsuhiko Kido, a vocational/technical school student who's staying in his school's dorms, one day discovers a hole in the wall of his apartment room. He peeks through the hole, but when he does so, he sees his neighbor, Ikuno Emiru, masturbating and he's caught peeking! However, when he goes over to inform her of the hole in the wall, she shuts the door in his face. Luckily for him, he's able to stop the door from closing and pursues after her, but, in his haste, he trips and lands right on top of her. As luck would have it, she takes a picture of them in a compromising position and tries to blackmail him into getting naked?!","endDate":{"day":1,"month":2,"year":2013},"format":"MANGA","id":51419,"idMal":21419,"isAdult":true,"meanScore":74,"siteUrl":"https://anilist.co/manga/51419","startDate":{"day":23,"month":1,"year":2009},"status":"FINISHED","synonyms":["A Peephole","Podejrzane sekrety","Nozoki Ana","Heimliche Blicke","Nozokiana"],"title":{"native":"ノ・ゾ・キ・ア・ナ","romaji":"No Zo Ki A Na","userPreferred":"No Zo Ki A Na"},"type":"MANGA","volumes":13}}},{"node":{"mediaRecommendation":{"bannerImage":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/manga/banner/79697-Beae1xND5lnv.jpg","chapters":11,"countryOfOrigin":"JP","coverImage":{"color":"#f12886","extraLarge":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/manga/cover/large/bx79697-8JU0mqjWcheP.jpg","large":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/manga/cover/medium/bx79697-8JU0mqjWcheP.jpg","medium":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/manga/cover/small/bx79697-8JU0mqjWcheP.jpg"},"description":"1. \u003cb\u003eKyuuketsuki no Hors d'oeuvre\u003c/b\u003e (吸血鬼のオードブル, First Course for Vampire); kakioroshi\u003cbr\u003e\n2. \u003cb\u003eKyuuketsuki no Gochisou\u003c/b\u003e (吸血鬼のご馳走, Dinner for a Vampire); Comic Unreal 2011-06\u003cbr\u003e\n3. \u003cb\u003eKyuuketsuki no Full Course\u003c/b\u003e (吸血鬼のフルコース, Full Course Dinner for Vampire); Comic Unreal 2012-04\u003cbr\u003e\