725"}},"updated_at":"2026-02-26T23:05:25.042747+03:00"},"136052":{"value":{"Media":{"characters":{"edges":[{"id":314174,"node":{"id":233865,"isFavourite":false,"gender":"Female","dateOfBirth":{},"name":{"alternative":["Woo-Hee"],"full":"U-Hui","native":"우희"},"image":{"large":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/character/large/default.jpg"},"siteUrl":"https://anilist.co/character/233865"},"role":"MAIN"},{"id":314175,"node":{"id":233864,"isFavourite":false,"gender":"Male","dateOfBirth":{},"name":{"full":"Wang-Gu","native":"왕구"},"image":{"large":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/character/large/default.jpg"},"siteUrl":"https://anilist.co/character/233864"},"role":"MAIN"}]},"genres":["Comedy","Drama","Hentai","Romance"],"id":136052,"recommendations":{"edges":[{"node":{"mediaRecommendation":{"bannerImage":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/manga/banner/124090-a7jheNA3vF9f.jpg","chapters":113,"countryOfOrigin":"KR","coverImage":{"color":"#e4506b","extraLarge":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/manga/cover/medium/b124090-ALya6arDXJsN.jpg","large":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/manga/cover/medium/b124090-ALya6arDXJsN.jpg","medium":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/manga/cover/small/b124090-ALya6arDXJsN.jpg"},"description":"Seung-Ho is dating a sweetheart, Min-Ha but he’s getting tired of her childish behavior. After getting a job followed by a long hiatus, he meets an attractive and talented young boss. He starts to struggle in between his boss and her girlfriend.\u003cbr\u003e\u003cbr\u003e(Source: TOPTOON+)","endDate":{"day":30,"month":12,"year":2021},"format":"MANGA","id":124090,"isAdult":true,"meanScore":76,"siteUrl":"https://anilist.co/manga/124090","startDate":{"day":5,"month":12,"year":2019},"status":"FINISHED","synonyms":["はらはら恋々"],"title":{"english":"Young Boss","native":"어린 상사","romaji":"Eorin Sangsa","userPreferred":"Eorin Sangsa"},"type":"MANGA"}}}]},"relations":{},"siteUrl":"https://anilist.co/manga/136052"}},"updated_at":"2026-03-15T06:34:56.057659+03:00"},"140475":{"value":{"Media":{"characters":{"edges":[{"id":360989,"node":{"age":"16","dateOfBirth":{"day":22,"month":7},"description":"__Height:__ 148 cm\n\nAn ace student at Kikyo Private Academy. Kaoruko is incredibly intelligent and kind, but often acts airheaded as well. She greatly enjoys eating sweets, meeting [Rintaro](https://anilist.co/character/268677/Rintarou-Tsumugi) in his family's cake shop and quickly befriending him. Despite later learning that he attends Chidori High—a school at bitter odds with her own—she continues to be close with him.\n\n~!Later, Rintaro confesses to Kaoruko and shortly after she returns his feelings, revealing that she has had feelings for him for much longer than what Rintaro remembers as their initial meeting.!~","gender":"Female","id":268676,"image":{"large":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/character/large/b268676-aQmqvqj0DNoJ.png"},"isFavourite":false,"name":{"full":"Kaoruko Waguri","native":"和栗薫子"},"siteUrl":"https://anilist.co/character/268676"},"role":"MAIN"},{"id":360990,"node":{"age":"16","dateOfBirth":{"day":28,"month":1},"description":"__Height:__ 190 cm\n\nA student at Chidori High. Rintarou is a very kind and calm person, but his blonde hair and piercings—adopted due to struggles with self-expression in his childhood—have led to many writing him off as a delinquent. The exceptions to this are his close friends at Chidori High, as well as [Kaoruko](https://anilist.co/character/268676), a girl from an opposing school known as Kikyo Private Academy. After first meeting Kaoruko in his family's cake shop, Rintarou gradually begins to spend more time with her.\n\n~!Later, Rintarou falls for Kaoruko and confesses his feelings to her. While this causes some awkwardness between the two at first, she eventually returns his feelings and they begin dating.!~","gender":"Male","id":268677,"image":{"large":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/character/large/b268677-oTCZrGWtenMv.png"},"isFavourite":false,"name":{"full":"Rintarou Tsumugi","native":"紬凛太郎"},"siteUrl":"https://anilist.co/character/268677"},"role":"MAIN"},{"id":414215,"node":{"age":"47","dateOfBirth":{"day":18,"month":4},"description":"[Rintaro](https://anilist.co/character/268677/Rintarou-Tsumugi)'s father. He runs the Tsumugi Family Bakery alongside his wife [Kyouko](https://anilist.co/character/286245/Kyouko-Tsumugi). He is dedicated to his work as a baker, spending nearly every day in the kitchen perfecting his technique.","gender":"Male","id":299398,"image":{"large":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/character/large/b299398-Xs4z2ZR8lywB.png"},"isFavourite":false,"name":{"full":"Keichiro Tsumugi","native":"紬圭一郎"},"siteUrl":"https://anilist.co/character/299398"},"role":"SUPPORTING"},{"id":484872,"node":{"age":"20","dateOfBirth":{},"description":"[Rintarou](https://anilist.co/character/268677/Rintarou-Tsumugi)'s older brother. He moved out of his family's house and works as a beautician.","gender":"Male","id":334758,"image":{"large":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/character/large/b334758-Ip6MDjXutI7s.png"},"isFavourite":false,"name":{"full":"Soutarou Tsumugi","native":"紬宗太郎"},"siteUrl":"https://anilist.co/character/334758"},"role":"SUPPORTING"},{"id":442435,"node":{"age":"17","dateOfBirth":{"day":11,"month":6},"description":"A good friend of [Kaoruko](https://anilist.co/character/268676/Kaoruko-Waguri)'s that attends Kikyo Private Academy. Extremely friendly and outgoing, and unlike her fellow classmates at Kikyo, harbors no animosity or negative feelings towards the students at Chidori High.","gender":"Female","id":312197,"image":{"large":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/character/large/b312197-fVxaGSxid7oF.png"},"isFavourite":false,"name":{"full":"Madoka Yuzuhara","native":"柚原まどか"},"siteUrl":"https://anilist.co/character/312197"},"role":"SUPPORTING"},{"id":507820,"node":{"dateOfBirth":{},"description":"Classmate of [Tsumugi Rintaro](https://anilist.co/character/268677/Rintarou-Tsumugi) from middle school. She was initially scared of him but gradually learnt about his gentle nature. She dyes her hair blonde after being inspired by Tsumugi to change.","gender":"Female","id":348803,"image":{"large":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/character/large/b348803-FXiJF920Qnan.png"},"isFavourite":false,"name":{"full":"Satsuki Nabata","native":"菜畑皐月"},"siteUrl":"https://anilist.co/character/348803"},"role":"SUPPORTING"},{"id":362996,"node":{"age":"16","dateOfBirth":{"day":19,"month":11},"description":"[Kaoruko](https://anilist.co/character/268676/Kaoruko-Waguri)'s closest friend since middle school. Subaru is noted to be exceptionally pretty by her peers but has a somewhat withdrawn personality, particularly having trouble whilst talking to boys. She's also very protective of Kaoruko, initially disapproving of her relationship with [Rintaro](https://anilist.co/character/268677/Rintarou-Tsumugi) and the others before discovering how kindhearted the boys are.\n\n~!Despite becoming friendly with the Chidori High boys, Subaru feels as though she doesn't fit in with the group despite wanting to be close with them. However, with Kaoruko and the boys' help she reaffirms her friendship with them, even becoming comfortable enough to casually tease [Saku](https://anilist.co/character/272241/Saku-Natsusawa) and bring him presents for his birthday.!~","gender":"Female","id":270095,"image":{"large":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/character/large/b270095-Z5KpvacVXp1S.jpg"},"isFavourite":false,"name":{"full":"Subaru Hoshina","native":"保科昴"},"siteUrl":"https://anilist.co/character/270095"},"role":"SUPPORTING"},{"id":442436,"node":{"age":"13","dateOfBirth":{"day":23,"month":4},"description":"[Kaoruko](https://anilist.co/character/268676/Kaoruko-Waguri)'s brother.","gender":"Male","id":312201,"image":{"large":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/character/large/b312201-A2vZqjtjfnLa.png"},"isFavourite":false,"name":{"full":"Kousuke Waguri","native":"和栗洸介"},"siteUrl":"https://anilist.co/character/312201"},"role":"SUPPORTING"},{"id":539426,"node":{"dateOfBirth":{},"description":"Reo was a friend and study partner to [Saku Natsusawa](https://anilist.co/character/272241/Saku-Natsusawa), before they got into a disagreement and parted ways.","gender":"Male","id":371378,"image":{"large":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/character/large/b371378-cbEm2t5xiUzf.jpg"},"isFavourite":false,"name":{"full":"Reo Hidaka","native":"飛鷹怜央"},"siteUrl":"https://anilist.co/character/371378"},"role":"SUPPORTING"},{"id":365637,"node":{"age":"17","dateOfBirth":{"day":27,"month":5},"description":"A student at Chidori High and a close friend of [Rintaro](https://anilist.co/character/268677/Rintarou-Tsumugi)'s, alongside [Ayato](https://anilist.co/character/272243/Ayato-Yorita) and [Saku](https://anilist.co/character/272241/Saku-Natsusawa). Shohei is extremely outgoing, being the most talkative member of Rintaro's friend group. He also holds no hostility towards Kikyo's students despite the opposing school's vitriol towards each other.","gender":"Male","id":272240,"image":{"large":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/character/large/b272240-1okw3miy0dPX.png"},"isFavourite":false,"name":{"full":"Shohei Usami","native":"宇佐美翔平"},"siteUrl":"https://anilist.co/character/272240"},"role":"SUPPORTING"},{"id":442437,"node":{"age":"46","dateOfBirth":{"day":22,"month":11},"description":"[Kaoruko](https://anilist.co/character/268676/Kaoruko-Waguri)'s mother.","gender":"Female","id":312202,"image":{"large":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/character/large/b312202-SB2XNOtOEvIw.png"},"isFavourite":false,"name":{"full":"Fuuko Waguri","native":"和栗楓子"},"siteUrl":"https://anilist.co/character/312202"},"role":"SUPPORTING"},{"id":545166,"node":{"dateOfBirth":{},"description":"Teacher \u0026 student guidance counselor at Kikyo Private Academy. Homeroom teacher for [Kaoruko](https://anilist.co/character/268676/Kaoruko-Waguri)’s class; extremely strict and holds bias against Chidori students.","gender":"Female","id":376746,"image":{"large":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/character/large/b376746-ksE9CoC7AfRj.jpg"},"isFavourite":false,"name":{"full":"Ayame Toki","native":"土岐菖蒲"},"siteUrl":"https://anilist.co/character/376746"},"role":"SUPPORTING"},{"id":365638,"node":{"age":"16","dateOfBirth":{"day":21,"month":8},"description":"A student at Chidori High and a close friend of [Rintaro](https://anilist.co/character/268677/Rintarou-Tsumugi)'s, alongside [Shouhei](https://anilist.co/character/272240/Shohei-Usami) and [Ayato](https://anilist.co/character/272243/Ayato-Yorita).\n\nDespite his attractive features he always appears gloomy, making him appear hard to talk to. But while he is more withdrawn than his friends he cares deeply about them and is naturally kind despite his cynical exterior. He is also incredibly intelligent, being the smartest student at Chidori High and even outdoing Kikyo's students, as noted by [Subaru](https://anilist.co/character/270095/Subaru-Hoshina) who begins to study with him.\n\n~!Due to his standing as a genius he became isolated from his peers in middle school, resulting in his current introverted personality.!~","gender":"Male","id":272241,"image":{"large":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/character/large/b272241-6NHTwQDIUXQk.png"},"isFavourite":false,"name":{"full":"Saku Natsusawa","native":"夏沢朔"},"siteUrl":"https://anilist.co/character/272241"},"role":"SUPPORTING"},{"id":442438,"node":{"age":"14","dateOfBirth":{"day":11,"month":2},"description":"[Saku](https://anilist.co/character/272241/Saku-Natsusawa)'s younger sister.","gender":"Female","id":312203,"image":{"large":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/character/large/b312203-n0UsKHCgeU4t.png"},"isFavourite":false,"name":{"full":"Mio Natsusawa","native":"夏沢澪"},"siteUrl":"https://anilist.co/character/312203"},"role":"SUPPORTING"},{"id":365639,"node":{"age":"16","dateOfBirth":{"day":16,"month":3},"description":"A student at Chidori High and a close friend of [Rintarou](https://anilist.co/character/268677/Rintarou-Tsumugi)'s, along with [Saku](https://anilist.co/character/272241/Saku-Natsusawa) and [Shohei](https://anilist.co/character/272240/Shohei-Usami). Ayato is rather friendly, and while he prefers to avoid situations involving violence, he is highly capable of defending himself and will readily fight should his friends be threatened.","gender":"Male","id":272243,"image":{"large":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/character/large/b272243-i9xYmuUQaI3q.png"},"isFavourite":false,"name":{"full":"Ayato Yorita","native":"依田絢斗"},"siteUrl":"https://anilist.co/character/272243"},"role":"SUPPORTING"},{"id":442533,"node":{"age":"16","dateOfBirth":{"day":25,"month":3},"description":"A good friend and classmate of [Kaoruko](https://anilist.co/character/268676/Kaoruko-Waguri)'s, and a student at Kikyo Private Academy. Raised in a strict and accomplished family, she grew to rely on the negative rumors about the students at Chidori Public High School to protect her self-esteem.\n\n~!Later, with Kaoruko's help, she overcomes her self esteem issues and becomes friends with the Chidori High boys, letting go of her previous preconceptions of them.!~","gender":"Female","id":312259,"image":{"large":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/character/large/b312259-lVFZJJ0cjLTA.png"},"isFavourite":false,"name":{"full":"Ayumi Sawatari","native":"沢渡亜由美"},"siteUrl":"https://anilist.co/character/312259"},"role":"SUPPORTING"},{"id":387019,"node":{"age":"45","dateOfBirth":{"day":5,"month":12},"description":"[Rintaro](https://anilist.co/character/268677/Rintarou-Tsumugi)'s mother. She runs the Tsumugi Family Bakery alongside her husband [Keichiro](https://anilist.co/character/299398/Keichiro-Tsumugi).","gender":"Female","id":286245,"image":{"large":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/character/large/b286245-iZhNiS29Mw2B.jpg"},"isFavourite":false,"name":{"alternative":["Rintaro's Mother"],"full":"Kyouko Tsumugi","native":"紬杏子"},"siteUrl":"https://anilist.co/character/286245"},"role":"SUPPORTING"},{"id":442534,"node":{"age":"16","dateOfBirth":{"day":14,"month":1},"description":"[Kaoruko's](https://anilist.co/character/268676/Kaoruko-Waguri) friend and classmate at Kikyo Private Academy.","gender":"Female","id":312258,"image":{"large":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/character/large/b312258-JI5qducsifMY.jpg"},"isFavourite":false,"name":{"full":"Chisa Minamoto","native":"源千紗"},"siteUrl":"https://anilist.co/character/312258"},"role":"SUPPORTING"},{"id":387020,"node":{"dateOfBirth":{},"description":"The homeroom teacher for Rintaro and his friends at Chidori High.","gender":"Male","id":286246,"image":{"large":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/character/large/b286246-AC7LfzvbhWl3.png"},"isFavourite":false,"name":{"alternative":["Tsuka-chan"],"full":"Shin Tsukada","native":"塚田慎"},"siteUrl":"https://anilist.co/character/286246"},"role":"SUPPORTING"},{"id":442535,"node":{"age":"17","dateOfBirth":{"day":25,"month":6},"description":"A friend of [Kaoruko](https://anilist.co/character/268676/Kaoruko-Waguri)'s, and a student at Kikyo Private Academy.","gender":"Female","id":312260,"image":{"large":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/character/large/b312260-4YsLvZoIhitx.png"},"isFavourite":false,"name":{"full":"Suzuka Asakura","native":"浅倉すずか"},"siteUrl":"https://anilist.co/character/312260"},"role":"SUPPORTING"}]},"genres":["Comedy","Drama","Romance"],"id":140475,"rankings":[{"allTime":true,"context":"highest rated all time","format":"MANGA","rank":29,"type":"RATED"},{"allTime":true,"context":"most popular all time","format":"MANGA","rank":54,"type":"POPULAR"},{"allTime":false,"context":"highest rated","format":"MANGA","rank":2,"type":"RATED","year":2021},{"allTime":false,"context":"most popular","format":"MANGA","rank":2,"type":"POPULAR","year":2021}],"recommendations":{"edges":[{"node":{"mediaRecommendation":{"bannerImage":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/manga/banner/42451-shG1Ksjxm3pw.jpg","chapters":152,"countryOfOrigin":"JP","coverImage":{"color":"#e45d93","extraLarge":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/manga/cover/large/bx72451-vVXtRwyttjGG.png","large":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/manga/cover/medium/bx72451-vVXtRwyttjGG.png","medium":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/manga/cover/small/bx72451-vVXtRwyttjGG.png"},"description":"At school, Kyouko Hori is known for being smart, attractive, and popular. On the other hand, her classmate, the boring, gloomy Izumi Miyamura tends to get painted as a \"loser fanboy.\" But when a liberally pierced and tattooed (not to mention downright gorgeous) Miyamura appears unexpectedly on the doorstep of secretly plain-Jane homebody Hori, these two similarly dissimilar teenagers discover that there are multiple sides to every story...and person!\n\u003cbr\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\n(Source: Yen Press)\n\u003cbr\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\n\u003ci\u003eNotes:\u003cbr\u003e\n- Includes 20 extra chapters.\u003cbr\u003e\n- The 17th volume was released on July 18, 2023, two years after the series' original ending. This new volume included 10 additional chapters.\n\u003c/i\u003e","endDate":{"day":18,"month":7,"year":2023},"format":"MANGA","id":72451,"idMal":42451,"isAdult":false,"meanScore":82,"siteUrl":"https://anilist.co/manga/72451","startDate":{"day":18,"month":10,"year":2011},"status":"FINISHED","synonyms":["โฮริมิยะ สาวมั่นกับนายมืดมน","Horimiya - Hori and Miyamura","Хорімія","호리미야"],"title":{"english":"Horimiya","native":"ホリミヤ","romaji":"Horimiya","userPreferred":"Horimiya"},"type":"MANGA","volumes":17}}},{"node":{"mediaRecommendation":{"bannerImage":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/manga/banner/132182-1jdVSMx8ShXd.jpg","countryOfOrigin":"JP","coverImage":{"color":"#e47843","extraLarge":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/manga/cover/large/bx132182-maXh2QzYPrqR.jpg","large":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/manga/cover/medium/bx132182-maXh2QzYPrqR.jpg","medium":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/manga/cover/small/bx132182-maXh2QzYPrqR.jpg"},"description":"Taiki Inomata is on the boys' badminton team at sports powerhouse Eimei Junior and Senior High. He's in love with basketball player Chinatsu Kano, the older girl he trains alongside every morning in the gym. One Spring day, their relationship takes a sharp turn ... And thus begins this brand-new series of love, sports and youth!\u003cbr\u003e\u003cbr\u003e(Source: MANGA Plus)","endDate":{},"format":"MANGA","id":132182,"idMal":135545,"isAdult":false,"meanScore":81,"siteUrl":"https://anilist.co/manga/132182","startDate":{"day":12,"month":4,"year":2021},"status":"RELEASING","synonyms":["青色之箱","กล่องรักวัยใส","Niebieskie pudełko","La caja azul","青春之箱","蓝箱"],"title":{"english":"Blue Box","native":"アオのハコ","romaji":"Ao no Hako","userPreferred":"Ao no Hako"},"type":"MANGA"}}},{"node":{"mediaRecommendation":{"bannerImage":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/manga/banner/86279-hGX7R26ZCUw3.jpg","chapters":121,"countryOfOrigin":"JP","coverImage":{"color":"#e45d78","extraLarge":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/manga/cover/large/nx86279-UF065BhrwVHW.jpg","large":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/manga/cover/medium/nx86279-UF065BhrwVHW.jpg","medium":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/manga/cover/small/nx86279-UF065BhrwVHW.jpg"},"description":"At Dahlia Academy, a prestigious boarding school attended by students of two feuding countries—the eastern Nation of Touwa, and the Principality of West—Romio Inuzuka, leader of the dorms’ Touwa first-years, wishes for a romance that can never be. For his ladylove is none other than his arch-enemy, Juliet Persia, leader of the dorms’ West first-years! Is Inuzuka ready to risk it all to confess his feelings? And even if Persia somehow agrees to go out with them, how long can they keep a forbidden relationship under wraps?!\n\u003cbr\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\n(Source: Kodansha USA)\n\u003cbr\u003e\n\u003cbr\u003e\n\u003ci\u003eNote: Includes an epilogue and bonus act.\u003c/i\u003e","endDate":{"day":4,"month":9,"year":2019},"format":"MANGA","id":86279,"idMal":91514,"isAdult":false,"meanScore":81,"siteUrl":"https://anilist.co/manga/86279","startDate":{"day":9,"month":7,"year":2015},"status":"FINISHED","synonyms":["Kushuku Gakkou no Alice","寄宿学校的朱丽叶","รักลับๆ ข้ามหอของนายหมากับน้องแมว","Romio vs Juliet","寄宿學校的茱麗葉"],"title":{"english":"Boarding School Juliet","native":"寄宿学校のジュリエット","romaji":"Kishuku Gakkou no Juliet","userPreferred":"Kishuku Gakkou no Juliet"},"type":"MANGA","volumes":16}}},{"node":{"mediaRecommendation":{"bannerImage":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/manga/banner/109285-ZJPAgX6vCwen.jpg","countryOfOrigin":"JP","coverImage":{"extraLarge":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/manga/cover/large/bx109285-HmBZpzsO2zxd.jpg","large":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/manga/cover/medium/bx109285-HmBZpzsO2zxd.jpg","medium":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/manga/cover/small/bx109285-HmBZpzsO2zxd.jpg"},"description":"Excellent student Iwakura Mitsumi has always dreamt about leaving her small town, going to a prestigious university, and making positive change in the world. But she’s so focused on reaching her goals that she’s not prepared for the very different (and overwhelming) city life that awaits her in a Tokyo high school. Luckily, she makes fast friends with Shima Sousuke, a handsome classmate who’s as laid-back as she is over-prepared. Can this naive country girl make it big in Tokyo with Sousuke by her side? \n\u003cbr\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\n(Source: Seven Seas Entertainment)\u003cbr\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\n\u003ci\u003eNotes:\u003cbr\u003e\n- Nominated for the 2020 Manga Taisho Award.\u003cbr\u003e\n- Winner of the 47th Kodansha Manga Award in the Best General Manga category in 2023.\u003c/i\u003e","endDate":{},"format":"MANGA","id":109285,"idMal":118289,"isAdult":false,"meanScore":86,"siteUrl":"https://anilist.co/manga/109285","startDate":{"day":25,"month":8,"year":2018},"status":"RELEASING","synonyms":["Skip and Loafer - Nhịp Bước Tuổi Xanh","Skip y Loafer","スキロー","스킵과 로퍼"],"title":{"english":"Skip and Loafer","native":"スキップとローファー","romaji":"Skip to Loafer","userPreferred":"Skip to Loafer"},"type":"MANGA"}}},{"node":{"mediaRecommendation":{"bannerImage":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/manga/banner/85135-BPNyMuWVvZjh.jpg","chapters":64,"countryOfOrigin":"JP","coverImage":{"color":"#e49343","extraLarge":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/manga/cover/large/bx85135-11OOnyaqV71k.png","large":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/manga/cover/medium/bx85135-11OOnyaqV71k.png","medium":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/manga/cover/small/bx85135-11OOnyaqV71k.png"},"description":"\u003ci\u003eBased on a one-shot that won the 80th Weekly Shounen Magazine Newbie Best Mangaka Award.\u003c/i\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\nShouya is a bully. When Shouko, a girl who can't hear, enters his elementary school class, she becomes their favorite target, and Shouya and his friends goad each other into devising new tortures for her. But the children's cruelty goes too far. Shouko is forced to leave the school, and Shouya ends up shouldering all the blame. Six years later, the two meet again. Can Shouya make up for his past mistakes, or is it too late?\u003cbr\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\n(Source: Kodansha USA)\u003cbr\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\n\u003ci\u003eNote: Includes two extra chapters.\u003c/i\u003e","endDate":{"day":19,"month":11,"year":2014},"format":"MANGA","id":85135,"idMal":56805,"isAdult":false,"meanScore":87,"siteUrl":"https://anilist.co/manga/85135","startDate":{"day":7,"month":8,"year":2013},"status":"FINISHED","synonyms":["The Shape of Voice","A Voz do Silêncio","A Forma da Voz","Kształt twojego głosu","Sessizliğin Sesi","声之形","Форма голоса","Němý hlas","รักไร้เสียง","Oblik glasa","목소리의 형태","Форма голосу","Silhuett av en stemme"],"title":{"english":"A Silent Voice","native":"聲の形","romaji":"Koe no Katachi","userPreferred":"Koe no Katachi"},"type":"MANGA","volumes":7}}},{"node":{"mediaRecommendation":{"bannerImage":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/manga/banner/66933-7JrONjV73S6B.jpg","chapters":56,"countryOfOrigin":"JP","coverImage":{"color":"#f15dae","extraLarge":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/manga/cover/large/bx66933-mMQbhh7WTCEs.png","large":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/manga/cover/medium/bx66933-mMQbhh7WTCEs.png","medium":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/manga/cover/small/bx66933-mMQbhh7WTCEs.png"},"description":"Takeo Goda is a GIANT guy with a GIANT heart.\n\u003cbr\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\nToo bad the girls don’t want him! (They want his good-looking best friend, Sunakawa.)\n\u003cbr\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\nUsed to being on the sidelines, Takeo simply stands tall and accepts his fate. But one day when he saves a girl named Yamato from a harasser on the train, his (love!) life suddenly takes an incredible turn!\n\u003cbr\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\nTakeo can hardly believe it when he crosses paths with Yamato again, and he finds himself falling in love with her… But with handsome Sunakawa around, does Takeo even stand a chance?\n\u003cbr\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\n(Source: VIZ Media)\n\u003cbr\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\n\u003ci\u003eNote: Shueisha released its 14th volume on April 24th, 2024. This volume contains an extra chapter and the 2 chapter sequel \"Ore Monogatari!! Yukiyama Mystery!? no Maki\".\u003c/i\u003e","endDate":{"day":24,"month":4,"year":2024},"format":"MANGA","id":66933,"idMal":36933,"isAdult":false,"meanScore":80,"siteUrl":"https://anilist.co/manga/66933","startDate":{"day":1,"month":11,"year":2011},"status":"FINISHED","synonyms":["Ore Monogatari","Câu chuyện tình tôi","Mon histoire"],"title":{"english":"My Love Story!!","native":"俺物語!!","romaji":"Ore Monogatari!!","userPreferred":"Ore Monogatari!!"},"type":"MANGA","volumes":14}}},{"node":{"mediaRecommendation":{"bannerImage":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/manga/banner/33378-9RtoYIQMFGq0.jpg","chapters":127,"countryOfOrigin":"JP","coverImage":{"color":"#e4a15d","extraLarge":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/manga/cover/large/bx33378-G9sHqsJryoP2.jpg","large":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/manga/cover/medium/bx33378-G9sHqsJryoP2.jpg","medium":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/manga/cover/small/bx33378-G9sHqsJryoP2.jpg"},"description":"Sawako Kuronuma is the perfect heroine...for a horror movie. With striking similarities to a haunting movie character--jet-black hair, sinister smile and silent demeanor--she's mistakenly called Sadako by those around her. But behind her scary façade is a very misunderstood teenager. Too shy to fit in, all she wants to do is make some friends. But when the most popular boy in class befriends her, she's sure to make more than just that--she's about to make some enemies too!\n\u003cbr\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\n(Source: VIZ Media)\n\u003cbr\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\n\u003ci\u003eNotes: The chapter count includes four extra chapters.\u003c/i\u003e","endDate":{"day":13,"month":11,"year":2017},"format":"MANGA","id":33378,"idMal":3378,"isAdult":false,"meanScore":83,"siteUrl":"https://anilist.co/manga/33378","startDate":{"day":25,"month":5,"year":2006},"status":"FINISHED","synonyms":["Reaching You","Llegando a Ti","Que Chegue a Você","Sawako","Nguyện ước yêu thương"],"title":{"english":"Kimi ni Todoke: From Me to You","native":"君に届け","romaji":"Kimi ni Todoke","userPreferred":"Kimi ni Todoke"},"type":"MANGA","volumes":30}}},{"node":{"mediaRecommendation":{"bannerImage":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/manga/banner/136943-9xrYRwstZOxC.jpg","countryOfOrigin":"JP","coverImage":{"extraLarge":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/manga/cover/large/bx136943-X9vwb5Nc7Bq8.jpg","large":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/manga/cover/medium/bx136943-X9vwb5Nc7Bq8.jpg","medium":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/manga/cover/small/bx136943-X9vwb5Nc7Bq8.jpg"},"description":"Spare eraser? Check. Extra folding umbrella? Check. First aid kit? Check. Cool and collected high school student Risa Amakawa has something in her heavy bag for every situation, and the last thing she needs—or knows how to ask for—is anyone's help. When she saves a beat-up delinquent in the park one rainy evening, she refuses any sort of repayment. But it turns out that saving the notorious Zen Ohira buys her the attention of some unsavory characters. As Zen keeps swooping in to help her out of one pickle after another, her feelings about relying on anyone but herself—and her feelings toward Zen—slowly begin to change...\n\u003cbr\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\n(Source: Kodansha USA)","endDate":{},"format":"MANGA","id":136943,"idMal":139104,"isAdult":false,"meanScore":81,"siteUrl":"https://anilist.co/manga/136943","startDate":{"day":26,"month":7,"year":2021},"status":"RELEASING","synonyms":["To Say The Least, This Is Love","Más allá del amor","Definitely Love","C'est de L'amour, Crois-Moi!","委婉地說，這是愛"],"title":{"english":"Love, That's an Understatement","native":"ひかえめに言っても、これは愛","romaji":"Hikaeme ni Itte mo, Kore wa Ai","userPreferred":"Hikaeme ni Itte mo, Kore wa Ai"},"type":"MANGA"}}}]},"relations":{"edges":[{"node":{"bannerImage":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/banner/181444-SBhwJNPxjHrr.jpg","countryOfOrigin":"JP","coverImage":{"color":"#a1d6f1","extraLarge":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/cover/large/bx181444-Ut9DDUZdfHwg.jpg","large":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/cover/medium/bx181444-Ut9DDUZdfHwg.jpg","medium":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/cover/small/bx181444-Ut9DDUZdfHwg.jpg"},"description":"Chidori High is a boys’ school that takes in the dregs of society with the lowest grades. Next door stands Kikyo Girls’ High, where the wealthy, high-class families send their precious daughters. Chidori second-year Rintarou, who has a fierce face but a gentle heart, is helping at his family’s patisserie when he meets a girl named Kaoruko. The two hit it off right away…but this blissful peace is quickly disturbed when Rintarou discovers that Kaoruko is actually a student at Kikyo. Worse, she doesn’t seem to realize what a huge problem this really is! Will these two be able to forge a path for themselves, and sidestep the traps (metaphorical and literal) laid by their classmates?\n\u003cbr\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\n(Source: Kodansha USA)","endDate":{"day":28,"month":9,"year":2025},"format":"TV","genres":["Comedy","Drama","Romance"],"id":181444,"idMal":59845,"isAdult":false,"meanScore":85,"season":"SUMMER","siteUrl":"https://anilist.co/anime/181444","startDate":{"day":6,"month":7,"year":2025},"status":"FINISHED","synonyms":["Kaoru i Rin: Rozkwitając z tobą","BLOOM","Благоухающий цветок расцветает с достоинством","La nobleza de las flores","Kaoru und Rin"],"title":{"english":"The Fragrant Flower Blooms With Dignity","native":"薫る花は凛と咲く","romaji":"Kaoru Hana wa Rin to Saku","userPreferred":"Kaoru Hana wa Rin to Saku"},"type":"ANIME"},"relationType":"ADAPTATION"}]},"siteUrl":"https://anilist.co/manga/140475"}},"updated_at":"2026-02-26T18:07:35.819059+03:00"},"149332":{"value":{"Media":{"characters":{"edges":[{"id":381008,"node":{"id":283698,"isFavourite":false,"gender":"Male","dateOfBirth":{"day":9,"month":11,"year":1779},"name":{"full":"Jin Runcandel","native":"진 룬칸델"},"image":{"large":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/character/large/b283698-9deKCyrCnSsy.jpg"},"description":"The youngest son of Runcandel family.","siteUrl":"https://anilist.co/character/283698"},"role":"MAIN"},{"id":551484,"node":{"id":382333,"isFavourite":false,"dateOfBirth":{},"name":{"full":"Shuri Runkandel","native":"슈리 룬칸델"},"image":{"large":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/character/large/default.jpg"},"description":"Originally witch Heluram's pet cat. Later made a pact with Jin, becoming Jin's cat.","siteUrl":"https://anilist.co/character/382333"},"role":"SUPPORTING"},{"id":552830,"node":{"id":382913,"isFavourite":false,"gender":"Female","dateOfBirth":{},"name":{"alternative":["Aria Owlheart (아리아 아울하트)"],"full":"Valeria Heaster","native":"발레리아 히스터"},"image":{"large":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/character/large/b382913-c37hi0KwzHH8.jpg"},"description":"Jin's magic mentor in his previous life. She is the sole survivor of the Heaster family, which was annihilated by Zipple.","siteUrl":"https://anilist.co/character/382913"},"role":"SUPPORTING"},{"id":556237,"node":{"id":386283,"isFavourite":false,"gender":"Female","dateOfBirth":{},"name":{"full":"Yona Runcandel","native":"요나 룬칸델"},"image":{"large":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/character/large/default.jpg"},"description":"The sixth daughter of Chiron Runcandel. She currently resides with the Nameless Assassin group.","siteUrl":"https://anilist.co/character/386283"},"role":"SUPPORTING"},{"id":556322,"node":{"id":386410,"isFavourite":false,"gender":"Female","dateOfBirth":{},"name":{"full":"Octavia Zipple","native":"옥타비아 지플"},"image":{"large":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/character/large/b386410-dsROAhuQXiEp.jpg"},"description":"Kelliak Zipple's younger sister and the true second-in-command of the Zipple family. While she is generally considered to have retired at 7-star, she was actually the leader of the Shadow Squad, a secret special forces unit comprised of 9-star and 10-star Zipple mages.","siteUrl":"https://anilist.co/character/386410"},"role":"SUPPORTING"},{"id":559262,"node":{"id":388164,"isFavourite":false,"gender":"Male","dateOfBirth":{},"name":{"full":"Casimir Alfrion","native":"카시미르 알프리온"},"image":{"large":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/character/large/b388164-OOY6ymwiSVu2.jpg"},"description":"The leader of the Free City of Tikan and the intelligence organization Seven-Colored Bird. He was a prince of the Viment Empire, but was expelled from the imperial court. Since then, he has been known to the world as a warrior of immense skill, nicknamed the Demon Sword.","siteUrl":"https://anilist.co/character/388164"},"role":"SUPPORTING"},{"id":560866,"node":{"id":389100,"isFavourite":false,"gender":"Male","dateOfBirth":{},"name":{"full":"Tess","native":"테스"},"image":{"large":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/character/large/b389100-8tsfsJXcyWSR.jpg"},"description":"The Phoenix that made a contract with Jin.","siteUrl":"https://anilist.co/character/389100"},"role":"SUPPORTING"},{"id":416004,"node":{"id":300024,"isFavourite":false,"gender":"Male","dateOfBirth":{},"name":{"alternative":["Ciaron"],"full":"Chiron Runcandel","native":"시론 룬칸델"},"image":{"large":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/character/large/b300024-UHUBLjwT6Z2l.jpg"},"description":"Jin's father and the current head of Runcandel. He is the only true knight of the present age, the strongest knight, and the undisputed strongest human","siteUrl":"https://anilist.co/character/300024"},"role":"SUPPORTING"},{"id":551485,"node":{"id":382334,"isFavourite":false,"gender":"Male","dateOfBirth":{},"name":{"full":"Garmund","native":"가르문드"},"image":{"large":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/character/large/b382334-MH56uC7uRoqs.jpg"},"siteUrl":"https://anilist.co/character/382334"},"role":"SUPPORTING"},{"id":553102,"node":{"id":383129,"isFavourite":false,"gender":"Male","dateOfBirth":{},"name":{"full":"Tuyan","native":"투얀"},"image":{"large":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/character/large/b383129-iG7Ioowspoci.jpg"},"description":"Water dragon. One of the guardian dragons of Veradin Zipple.","siteUrl":"https://anilist.co/character/383129"},"role":"SUPPORTING"},{"id":556238,"node":{"id":386285,"isFavourite":false,"gender":"Male","dateOfBirth":{},"name":{"full":"Daytona Runcandel","native":"데이토나 룬칸델"},"image":{"large":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/character/large/b386285-he4GPd0zwNln.jpg"},"description":"The fifth son of Chiron Runcandel and the 10th flagbearer of Runcandel. He is two years older than Jin and is an identical twin to Heytona.","siteUrl":"https://anilist.co/character/386285"},"role":"SUPPORTING"},{"id":556517,"node":{"id":386506,"isFavourite":false,"gender":"Female","dateOfBirth":{},"name":{"full":"Talaris Endorma","native":"탈라리스 엔도르마"},"image":{"large":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/character/large/default.jpg"},"description":"The 51st master of the Ice Palace. She's a 10-star knight and is one of the world's most powerful warriors. She's friends with [Chiron](https://anilist.co/character/300024).","siteUrl":"https://anilist.co/character/386506"},"role":"SUPPORTING"},{"id":559263,"node":{"id":388162,"isFavourite":false,"gender":"Female","dateOfBirth":{},"name":{"full":"Alyssa Badger","native":"알리사 뱃저"},"image":{"large":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/character/large/b388162-UpNfJhQyILiU.jpg"},"description":"Former Vice-Captain of the 2nd Division of the Viment Special Forces and wife of the demon sword Casimir. Currently, she serves as the captain of the defense of the free city of Tikan.","siteUrl":"https://anilist.co/character/388162"},"role":"SUPPORTING"},{"id":560867,"node":{"id":389099,"isFavourite":false,"gender":"Male","dateOfBirth":{},"name":{"full":"Buretta","native":"뷰렛타"},"image":{"large":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/character/large/b389099-KnSrUzHInVyB.jpg"},"description":"Wind Dragon. The dragon that protects Andrei Zipple.","siteUrl":"https://anilist.co/character/389099"},"role":"SUPPORTING"},{"id":416054,"node":{"id":300072,"isFavourite":false,"gender":"Female","dateOfBirth":{},"name":{"full":"Rosa Runcandel","native":"로사 룬칸델"},"image":{"large":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/character/large/b300072-DiKc3gLZ8Kf5.jpg"},"description":"She is the lady of the Runcandel family..","siteUrl":"https://anilist.co/character/300072"},"role":"SUPPORTING"},{"id":551486,"node":{"id":382335,"isFavourite":false,"gender":"Male","dateOfBirth":{},"name":{"full":"Veradin Zipple","native":"베라딘 지플"},"image":{"large":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/character/large/b382335-FtOGmuPhsUuV.png"},"description":"The youngest son of Kelliak Zipple and a powerful next-generation head of the family.","siteUrl":"https://anilist.co/character/382335"},"role":"SUPPORTING"},{"id":553103,"node":{"id":383131,"isFavourite":false,"gender":"Female","dateOfBirth":{},"name":{"alternative":["Cuicantelle"],"full":"Quicantel","native":"퀴칸텔"},"image":{"large":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/character/large/b383131-3PdoAchdbMhy.jpg"},"description":"The Silver Dragon of Time.The guardian dragon of the Olta Contractor. She and Murakan were lovers for approximately 500 years, 1000 years ago.","siteUrl":"https://anilist.co/character/383131"},"role":"SUPPORTING"},{"id":556239,"node":{"id":386286,"isFavourite":false,"gender":"Male","dateOfBirth":{},"name":{"full":"Heytona Runcandel","native":"헤이토나 룬칸델"},"image":{"large":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/character/large/b386286-aGJgriXex6Ry.jpg"},"description":"The sixth son of Chiron Runcandel and the 11th flagbearer of Runcandel. He is two years older than Jin and is Daytona's identical twin.","siteUrl":"https://anilist.co/character/386286"},"role":"SUPPORTING"},{"id":556518,"node":{"id":386509,"isFavourite":false,"gender":"Female","dateOfBirth":{},"name":{"full":"Mesa Milkano","native":"메사 밀카노"},"image":{"large":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/character/large/b386509-SNaWwvkDQPns.jpg"},"siteUrl":"https://anilist.co/character/386509"},"role":"SUPPORTING"},{"id":559264,"node":{"id":388163,"isFavourite":false,"gender":"Male","dateOfBirth":{},"name":{"full":"Jet","native":"제트"},"image":{"large":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/character/large/b388163-YIDcPtwbSKUj.jpg"},"description":"An innkeeper and an informant.","siteUrl":"https://anilist.co/character/388163"},"role":"SUPPORTING"},{"id":560868,"node":{"id":389101,"isFavourite":false,"gender":"Male","dateOfBirth":{},"name":{"alternative":["Pirate King (해적왕)"],"full":"Cosmos","native":"코스모스"},"image":{"large":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/character/large/b389101-FlUq6WyQiVXI.jpg"},"description":"A famous pirate nicknamed the Pirate King. He holds the world's dirtiest martial arts tournament, the Cosmos Arena, every year.","siteUrl":"https://anilist.co/character/389101"},"role":"SUPPORTING"},{"id":416055,"node":{"id":300073,"isFavourite":false,"gender":"Female","dateOfBirth":{},"name":{"full":"Luna Runcandel","native":"루나 룬칸델"},"image":{"large":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/character/large/b300073-JzJzit3dNetj.jpg"},"description":"She's the 1st flagbearer of Runcandel also known as the White Whale. Despite being the strongest of all the Runcandel siblings, she has no interest in becoming the patriarch and has stepped away from the \"Succession War\".","siteUrl":"https://anilist.co/character/300073"},"role":"SUPPORTING"},{"id":551917,"node":{"id":382485,"isFavourite":false,"gender":"Female","dateOfBirth":{},"name":{"full":"Misha","native":"미샤"},"image":{"large":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/character/large/b382485-rxza58PBvXHk.jpg"},"description":"Murakan's older sister.","siteUrl":"https://anilist.co/character/382485"},"role":"SUPPORTING"},{"id":553104,"node":{"id":383130,"isFavourite":false,"gender":"Female","dateOfBirth":{},"name":{"full":"Phinia","native":"피니아"},"image":{"large":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/character/large/b383130-JGWS6f0NlgR9.jpg"},"description":"Earth Dragon. One of the guardian dragons of Veradin Zipple.","siteUrl":"https://anilist.co/character/383130"},"role":"SUPPORTING"},{"id":556240,"node":{"id":386284,"isFavourite":false,"gender":"Female","dateOfBirth":{},"name":{"full":"Mary Runcandel","native":"메리 룬칸델"},"image":{"large":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/character/large/b386284-Vur9a6w8jiHm.jpg"},"description":"Chiron Runcandel's third daughter and the 7th flagbearer of Runcandel.","siteUrl":"https://anilist.co/character/386284"},"role":"SUPPORTING"}]},"genres":["Action","Adventure","Fantasy"],"id":149332,"rankings":[{"allTime":true,"context":"most popular all time","format":"MANGA","rank":161,"type":"POPULAR"},{"allTime":false,"context":"highest rated","format":"MANGA","rank":21,"type":"RATED","year":2022},{"allTime":false,"context":"most popular","format":"MANGA","rank":5,"type":"POPULAR","year":2022}],"recommendations":{"edges":[{"node":{"mediaRecommendation":{"countryOfOrigin":"KR","coverImage":{"color":"#5078e4","extraLarge":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/manga/cover/large/bx163824-KiablxybJD6i.jpg","large":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/manga/cover/medium/bx163824-KiablxybJD6i.jpg","medium":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/manga/cover/small/bx163824-KiablxybJD6i.jpg"},"description":"Raised to kill like a pack of loyal hounds, the Baskerville children took countless lives as a band of fearsome assassins. Despite being the shunned illegitimate son of the brood, Vikir served his family faithfully, only to meet his untimely demise at his father’s hands. But when he is inexplicably reborn with a second chance at life, Vikir, armed with the memories and knowledge of his past, swears to rise above the pack and take his revenge. This time, he's ready to bite the hand that feeds.\n\u003cbr\u003e\u003cbr\u003e(Source: Tapas)","endDate":{},"format":"MANGA","id":163824,"idMal":157888,"isAdult":false,"meanScore":80,"siteUrl":"https://anilist.co/manga/163824","startDate":{"day":14,"month":4,"year":2023},"status":"RELEASING","synonyms":["Revenge of the Iron-Blooded Sword Hound","Revenge of the Sword Clan's Hound","Die Rückkehr des Jagdhundes aus Eisen und Blut","回帰した鉄血の猟犬","铁血剑家猎犬的回归"],"title":{"english":"Revenge of the Baskerville Bloodhound","native":"철혈검가 사냥개의 회귀","romaji":"Cheolhyeolgeomga Sanyanggaeui Hoegwi","userPreferred":"Cheolhyeolgeomga Sanyanggaeui Hoegwi"},"type":"MANGA"}}},{"node":{"mediaRecommendation":{"bannerImage":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/manga/banner/151512-EPskkVDBQvtC.jpg","countryOfOrigin":"KR","coverImage":{"color":"#5dc9e4","extraLarge":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/manga/cover/large/bx151512-q0Xddr1JNKNq.png","large":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/manga/cover/medium/bx151512-q0Xddr1JNKNq.png","medium":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/manga/cover/small/bx151512-q0Xddr1JNKNq.png"},"description":"When the warrior Hamel sacrifices himself to protect his rival Bermut Lionhart, he makes Bermut vow to vanquish the last of the demon kings. Reincarnated with his memories 300 years later, he is shocked to find that not only are the demon kings still alive, but that he has been reborn as Eugene Lionhart, a member of his former rival’s bloodline! Now, as Eugene comes of age, he must train to prove himself as a Lionhart and eliminate the remaining demon kings once and for all. \n\u003cbr\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\n(Source: Tapas)","endDate":{},"format":"MANGA","id":151512,"idMal":149438,"isAdult":false,"meanScore":78,"siteUrl":"https://anilist.co/manga/151512","startDate":{"day":22,"month":6,"year":2022},"status":"HIATUS","synonyms":["Damn Reincarnation"],"title":{"english":"My Blasted Reincarnated Life","native":"빌어먹을 환생","romaji":"Bireomeogeul Hwansaeng","userPreferred":"Bireomeogeul Hwansaeng"},"type":"MANGA"}}},{"node":{"mediaRecommendation":{"bannerImage":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/manga/banner/105398-4UrEhdqZukrg.jpg","chapters":201,"countryOfOrigin":"KR","coverImage":{"extraLarge":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/manga/cover/large/bx105398-b673Vt5ZSuz3.jpg","large":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/manga/cover/medium/bx105398-b673Vt5ZSuz3.jpg","medium":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/manga/cover/small/bx105398-b673Vt5ZSuz3.jpg"},"description":"In a world where awakened beings called “Hunters” must battle deadly monsters to protect humanity, Seong Jin-U, nicknamed “the weakest hunter of all mankind,” finds himself in a constant struggle for survival. One day, after a brutal encounter in an overpowered dungeon wipes out his party and threatens to end his life, a mysterious System chooses him as its sole player: Jin-U has been granted the rare opportunity to level up his abilities, possibly beyond any known limits. Follow Jin-U’s journey as he takes on ever-stronger enemies, both human and monster, to discover the secrets deep within the dungeons and the ultimate extent of his powers.\n\u003cbr\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\n(Source: Tappytoon)\n\u003cbr\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\n\u003ci\u003eNote: Includes 22 extra chapters.\u003c/i\u003e","endDate":{"day":31,"month":5,"year":2023},"format":"MANGA","id":105398,"idMal":121496,"isAdult":false,"meanScore":84,"siteUrl":"https://anilist.co/manga/105398","startDate":{"day":4,"month":3,"year":2018},"status":"FINISHED","synonyms":["I Level Up Alone","Only I Level Up","俺だけレベルアップな件","我獨自升級","Ore dake Level Up na Ken","Поднятие уровня в одиночку","Тільки я візьму новий рівень"],"title":{"english":"Solo Leveling","native":"나 혼자만 레벨업","romaji":"Na Honjaman Level Up","userPreferred":"Na Honjaman Level Up"},"type":"MANGA","volumes":15}}},{"node":{"mediaRecommendation":{"bannerImage":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/manga/banner/146712-PXsVphjLRcvV.jpg","countryOfOrigin":"KR","coverImage":{"color":"#50aee4","extraLarge":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/manga/cover/large/bx146712-mxMLu7boE3W3.png","large":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/manga/cover/medium/bx146712-mxMLu7boE3W3.png","medium":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/manga/cover/small/bx146712-mxMLu7boE3W3.png"},"description":"After getting revenge on the Thulcaan Empire, Jack Valantier took his last breath. But just when he thinks it's all over, he finds himself transported back to when he was 14! From his negligent and wicked family to his loyal servant and caring sister, it's all just as he had remembered. But this time, Jack is armed to the teeth with decades of experience from his previous life! He's ready to give them hell, and those that have wronged him will pay dearly. Because this time, he's invincible.\n\u003cbr\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\n(Source: Tapas)","endDate":{},"format":"MANGA","id":146712,"idMal":150724,"isAdult":false,"meanScore":70,"siteUrl":"https://anilist.co/manga/146712","startDate":{"day":12,"month":3,"year":2022},"status":"RELEASING","synonyms":["Legendary Youngest Son of the Marquis House","The Margravial Household's Phenomenal Youngest Son","The Marquess's Youngest Son","The Youngest Son of a Marquis"],"title":{"english":"Jack Be Invincible","native":"후작가의 역대급 막내아들","romaji":"Hujakgaui Yeokdaegeup Mangnaeadeul","userPreferred":"Hujakgaui Yeokdaegeup Mangnaeadeul"},"type":"MANGA"}}},{"node":{"mediaRecommendation":{"countryOfOrigin":"KR","coverImage":{"color":"#e4a11a","extraLarge":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/manga/cover/large/bx135325-YAhEGWro8zFK.jpg","large":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/manga/cover/medium/bx135325-YAhEGWro8zFK.jpg","medium":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/manga/cover/small/bx135325-YAhEGWro8zFK.jpg"},"description":"After witnessing the shocking death of his mother, young Airen Farreira uses sleep to escape his painful reality, earning him the nickname, “the lazy lord”. Yet, in spite of others’ jeers and whispers, Airen has no intention of changing his ways. But when he awakens one day from a dream about a mysterious swordsman, his life’s trajectory takes a complete turn...\n\u003cbr\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\n(Source: WEBTOON)","endDate":{},"format":"MANGA","id":135325,"idMal":146827,"isAdult":false,"meanScore":78,"siteUrl":"https://anilist.co/manga/135325","startDate":{"day":21,"month":5,"year":2021},"status":"HIATUS","synonyms":["The Lazy Prince Becomes a Genius   ","Reformation of the Deadbeat Noble","Der faule Lord meistert die Schwertkunst","懶惰公子成長記"],"title":{"english":"The Lazy Lord Masters the Sword","native":"나태 공자, 노력 천재 되다","romaji":"Natae Gongja, Nolyeog Cheonjae Doeda","userPreferred":"Natae Gongja, Nolyeog Cheonjae Doeda"},"type":"MANGA"}}},{"node":{"mediaRecommendation":{"countryOfOrigin":"KR","coverImage":{"color":"#f1a150","extraLarge":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/manga/cover/large/bx168823-ehslkXrDOGu8.png","large":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/manga/cover/medium/bx168823-ehslkXrDOGu8.png","medium":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/manga/cover/small/bx168823-ehslkXrDOGu8.png"},"description":"Raon was once a loyal assassin for House Robert until Derus killed him. Not willing to give up, Raon prayed for vengeance and woke as a member of House Sieghart, the most powerful noble house. He’ll need all of their near-infinite resources to get revenge. Though he carried over knowledge of a powerful Flame Link technique, he also carries the Curse of Bitter Frost, something that’s slowly killing him. As if that weren’t enough, the demonic embodiment of Wrath is trying to take over his body.\u003cbr\u003e\u003cbr\u003e(Source: Tapas)","endDate":{},"format":"MANGA","id":168823,"idMal":162380,"isAdult":false,"meanScore":71,"siteUrl":"https://anilist.co/manga/168823","startDate":{"day":31,"month":8,"year":2023},"status":"RELEASING","synonyms":["The Reincarnated Assassin Is a Genius Swordsman"],"title":{"english":"The Reincarnated Assassin Is a Swordmaster","native":"환생한 암살자는 검술 천재","romaji":"Hwansaenghan Amsaljaneun Geomsul Cheonjae","userPreferred":"Hwansaenghan Amsaljaneun Geomsul Cheonjae"},"type":"MANGA"}}},{"node":{"mediaRecommendation":{"countryOfOrigin":"KR","coverImage":{"color":"#5d93e4","extraLarge":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/manga/cover/large/bx183855-BbnSsUPiOVrM.jpg","large":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/manga/cover/medium/bx183855-BbnSsUPiOVrM.jpg","medium":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/manga/cover/small/bx183855-BbnSsUPiOVrM.jpg"},"description":"Theo Ragnar, the 31st son of the mighty Grand Duke of Ragnar, was born without the legendary Ragnar Gift—a fatal flaw in a family where might is right. Labeled the “Ragnar Defect,” he and his mother were betrayed, meeting a brutal end at the hands of those they trusted. But death was only the beginning. Reborn at 17, Theo awakens not only with the Ragnar Gift, but with powers far beyond imagination. Fueled by vengeance and a second chance, he sets out to claim the glory he was once denied.\u003cbr\u003e\u003cbr\u003e(Source: Tapas)","endDate":{},"format":"MANGA","id":183855,"idMal":175209,"isAdult":false,"meanScore":75,"siteUrl":"https://anilist.co/manga/183855","startDate":{"day":8,"month":10,"year":2024},"status":"RELEASING","synonyms":["Regressing as the Reincarnated Bastard of the Sword Clan","ラグナール～回帰の剣士～"],"title":{"english":"The Bastard of Swordborne","native":"회귀검가의 서자가 사는 법","romaji":"Hoegwigeomgaui Seojaga Saneun Beop","userPreferred":"Hoegwigeomgaui Seojaga Saneun Beop"},"type":"MANGA"}}},{"node":{"mediaRecommendation":{"chapters":131,"countryOfOrigin":"JP","coverImage":{"color":"#e4785d","extraLarge":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/manga/cover/large/bx143025-YL8hzpkVFR5J.jpg","large":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/manga/cover/medium/bx143025-YL8hzpkVFR5J.jpg","medium":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/manga/cover/small/bx143025-YL8hzpkVFR5J.jpg"},"description":"After 10 grueling years as a monster hunter in the Devil’s Army, Raven Balt was given his final mission: guard Allen Pendragon, heir of a formerly glorious dragon-taming family. But when Raven and Allen are both killed as part of a conspiracy, Raven wakes up seven years in the past inside Allen’s body. To solve the mystery behind his death, Raven must find the legendary White Dragon to restore the power of House Pendragon. But does this mere hunter have what it takes to become a dragon master?\u003cbr\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\n(Source: Tapas)","endDate":{"day":12,"month":4,"year":2025},"format":"MANGA","id":143025,"isAdult":false,"meanScore":74,"siteUrl":"https://anilist.co/manga/143025","startDate":{"day":22,"month":12,"year":2021},"status":"FINISHED","synonyms":["백룡공작 팬드래건","Duke Pendragon","White Dragon Duke: Pendragon","白龙公爵佩德·莱欧"],"title":{"english":"Duke Pendragon: Master of the White Dragon","native":"白龍公爵ペンドラゴン","romaji":"Hakuryuu Koushaku Pendragon","userPreferred":"Hakuryuu Koushaku Pendragon"},"type":"MANGA"}}}]},"relations":{},"siteUrl":"https://anilist.co/manga/149332"}},"updated_at":"2026-03-15T07:10:13.695728+03:00"},"170400":{"value":{"Media":{"characters":{"edges":[{"id":546644,"node":{"id":378004,"isFavourite":false,"gender":"Male","dateOfBirth":{},"name":{"full":"Vlad","native":"블라드"},"image":{"large":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/character/large/b378004-wS3tTLJnFEYD.png"},"description":"An orphan living in Schoarra's slums. Despite his lowly birth, his appearance bears resemblance to nobility.","siteUrl":"https://anilist.co/character/378004"},"role":"MAIN"},{"id":546689,"node":{"id":378065,"isFavourite":false,"gender":"Male","dateOfBirth":{},"name":{"alternative":["Harven"],"full":"Haven","native":"하벤"},"image":{"large":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/character/large/b378065-XGmF3aY0NntK.png"},"description":"A clerk working for Captain Hoover. He's a close childhood friend of Vlad and Jemina.","siteUrl":"https://anilist.co/character/378065"},"role":"SUPPORTING"},{"id":546759,"node":{"id":378134,"isFavourite":false,"gender":"Female","dateOfBirth":{},"name":{"full":"Anna","native":"안나"},"image":{"large":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/character/large/b378134-KDciSaDWVVIo.png"},"description":"A prostitute at the Smiling Rose. She's a close acquaintance of Vlad's, who helps her after she is abused by a customer.\n\n~!She is later killed after being trafficked by Black Bear.!~","siteUrl":"https://anilist.co/character/378134"},"role":"SUPPORTING"},{"id":546855,"node":{"id":378194,"isFavourite":false,"gender":"Male","dateOfBirth":{},"name":{"full":"Ramund","native":"라문드"},"image":{"large":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/character/large/b378194-R52oxU8jgot0.png"},"description":"An old knight, and one of the most powerful of his era.","siteUrl":"https://anilist.co/character/378194"},"role":"SUPPORTING"},{"id":546871,"node":{"id":378229,"isFavourite":false,"gender":"Male","dateOfBirth":{},"name":{"full":"Ragmus","native":"라그무스"},"image":{"large":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/character/large/b378229-GzvN7iJ05J8a.jpg"},"description":"Count Vayezid's advisor.","siteUrl":"https://anilist.co/character/378229"},"role":"SUPPORTING"},{"id":546954,"node":{"id":378284,"isFavourite":false,"gender":"Male","dateOfBirth":{},"name":{"full":"Portley Cannor","native":"포틀리 칸노르"},"image":{"large":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/character/large/b378284-qDbQXigyPRMY.jpg"},"description":"A squire and a friend of Vlad.","siteUrl":"https://anilist.co/character/378284"},"role":"SUPPORTING"},{"id":546645,"node":{"id":378001,"isFavourite":false,"gender":"Male","dateOfBirth":{},"name":{"full":"Zayar","native":"자야르"},"image":{"large":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/character/large/b378001-RR67jGCK5zup.jpg"},"description":"Josef's knight. He is one of the strongest knights in the north, and becomes Vlad's mentor when he comes under Josef's wing.","siteUrl":"https://anilist.co/character/378001"},"role":"SUPPORTING"},{"id":546690,"node":{"id":378062,"isFavourite":false,"gender":"Male","dateOfBirth":{},"name":{"alternative":["The Whaler"],"full":"Captain Hoover","native":"캡틴 후버"},"image":{"large":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/character/large/b378062-XvLEh7nkOSvC.png"},"description":"One of the five bosses who rule over the slums of Schoarra.","siteUrl":"https://anilist.co/character/378062"},"role":"SUPPORTING"},{"id":546760,"node":{"id":378136,"isFavourite":false,"gender":"Male","dateOfBirth":{},"name":{"full":"Kade","native":"케이드"},"image":{"large":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/character/large/b378136-V1QGI4yV0b7G.png"},"description":"A knight serving Josef. He has excellent tracking abilities.","siteUrl":"https://anilist.co/character/378136"},"role":"SUPPORTING"},{"id":546856,"node":{"id":378196,"isFavourite":false,"gender":"Male","dateOfBirth":{},"name":{"full":"Gott","native":"고트"},"image":{"large":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/character/large/b378196-1GXfKqyirN00.png"},"description":"He has worked under Vlad during his days as a mercenary, later becoming a stable boy for the Vayezid family.","siteUrl":"https://anilist.co/character/378196"},"role":"SUPPORTING"},{"id":546874,"node":{"id":378234,"isFavourite":false,"gender":"Female","dateOfBirth":{},"name":{"alternative":["Justia"],"full":"Yustia","native":"유스티아"},"image":{"large":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/character/large/b378234-fqCc8GGNdXR0.jpg"},"description":"A powerful crusader of San Rosino.","siteUrl":"https://anilist.co/character/378234"},"role":"SUPPORTING"},{"id":546955,"node":{"id":378287,"isFavourite":false,"gender":"Male","dateOfBirth":{},"name":{"full":"Duncan","native":"던칸"},"image":{"large":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/character/large/b378287-vbGJ4l9oFbMX.png"},"description":"An elderly knight of house Hynal. Having served the family for many years, he is very loyal and close to the young baroness Alicia.","siteUrl":"https://anilist.co/character/378287"},"role":"SUPPORTING"},{"id":546646,"node":{"id":378002,"isFavourite":false,"gender":"Female","dateOfBirth":{},"name":{"full":"Jemina","native":"제미나"},"image":{"large":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/character/large/b378002-JbH5BcdWTsDz.png"},"description":"Vlad's childhood friend.","siteUrl":"https://anilist.co/character/378002"},"role":"SUPPORTING"},{"id":546691,"node":{"id":378063,"isFavourite":false,"gender":"Male","dateOfBirth":{},"name":{"alternative":["The Whoresguard"],"full":"Jorge","native":"호르헤"},"image":{"large":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/character/large/b378063-dHQgAqKyY94l.png"},"description":"One of the five bosses who rule over the slums of Schoarra. As a former knight, he is strong and kind, taking in an orphaned Vlad.\n\n~!He is later killed by Godin, his former squire.!~","siteUrl":"https://anilist.co/character/378063"},"role":"SUPPORTING"},{"id":546761,"node":{"id":378135,"isFavourite":false,"gender":"Male","dateOfBirth":{},"name":{"full":"Mirshea Dragulia","native":"미르셰아 드라굴리아"},"image":{"large":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/character/large/b378135-zGgjF1hEshIZ.png"},"description":"Sarnus Dragulia's heir, and the captain of the dragonslayers.","siteUrl":"https://anilist.co/character/378135"},"role":"SUPPORTING"},{"id":546865,"node":{"id":378231,"isFavourite":false,"gender":"Male","dateOfBirth":{},"name":{"full":"Andrea","native":"안드레아"},"image":{"large":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/character/large/b378231-h96Gj3k8erhS.jpg"},"description":"He created Vlad's identity card and served as guarantor.","siteUrl":"https://anilist.co/character/378231"},"role":"SUPPORTING"},{"id":546948,"node":{"id":378290,"isFavourite":false,"gender":"Male","dateOfBirth":{},"name":{"full":"Zuber","native":"주베르"},"image":{"large":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/character/large/b378290-A4yrOtS6nJF9.png"},"description":"A powerful knight and a representative of the Shazad family.","siteUrl":"https://anilist.co/character/378290"},"role":"SUPPORTING"},{"id":546956,"node":{"id":378286,"isFavourite":false,"gender":"Male","dateOfBirth":{},"name":{"full":"Istvan Gaithar","native":"이슈트반 가이다르"},"image":{"large":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/character/large/b378286-6pPpXS8MPK55.png"},"description":"The oldest son of Count Gaithar and the heir to the Gaithar family.","siteUrl":"https://anilist.co/character/378286"},"role":"SUPPORTING"},{"id":546647,"node":{"id":378003,"isFavourite":false,"gender":"Male","dateOfBirth":{},"name":{"full":"Josef Vayezid","native":"요제프 바예지드"},"image":{"large":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/character/large/b378003-zDXWHlEPku9t.jpg"},"description":"The second son of House Vayezid.","siteUrl":"https://anilist.co/character/378003"},"role":"SUPPORTING"},{"id":546692,"node":{"id":378064,"isFavourite":false,"gender":"Female","dateOfBirth":{},"name":{"alternative":["Madam"],"full":"Marcella","native":"마르셀라"},"image":{"large":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/character/large/b378064-kAkC7PK6WCOl.jpg"},"description":"The madam at the Smiling Rose. She's very close with Vlad, since the day he was first brought to her by Jorge as an orphan.","siteUrl":"https://anilist.co/character/378064"},"role":"SUPPORTING"},{"id":546850,"node":{"id":378186,"isFavourite":false,"gender":"Male","dateOfBirth":{},"name":{"full":"Rutger Vayezid","native":"루트거 바예지드"},"image":{"large":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/character/large/b378186-6IQUbUL2v0BY.jpg"},"description":"The eldest son of Count Vayezid and Josef's half-brother. He is known as one of the most powerful knights of the north.","siteUrl":"https://anilist.co/character/378186"},"role":"SUPPORTING"},{"id":546866,"node":{"id":378226,"isFavourite":false,"gender":"Male","dateOfBirth":{},"name":{"full":"Pablo","native":"파블로"},"image":{"large":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/character/large/b378226-8bqe0owm7BZt.jpg"},"description":"A knight and a representative of the Arnstein family.","siteUrl":"https://anilist.co/character/378226"},"role":"SUPPORTING"},{"id":546949,"node":{"id":378289,"isFavourite":false,"gender":"Male","dateOfBirth":{},"name":{"full":"Volkov Varanov","native":"볼코프 바라노프"},"image":{"large":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/character/large/b378289-Dewn3yKVlNBW.png"},"description":"The eldest son of Timur Varanov and the rightful heir to the Varanov family.","siteUrl":"https://anilist.co/character/378289"},"role":"SUPPORTING"},{"id":546957,"node":{"id":378285,"isFavourite":false,"gender":"Male","dateOfBirth":{},"name":{"full":"Sigmund Gaithar","native":"지그문드 가이다르"},"image":{"large":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/character/large/b378285-sU3yixHYAZub.png"},"description":"The head of the Gaithar family and the current champion of the west.","siteUrl":"https://anilist.co/character/378285"},"role":"SUPPORTING"},{"id":546648,"node":{"id":378005,"isFavourite":false,"gender":"Female","dateOfBirth":{},"name":{"full":"Alicia Hynal","native":"알리시아 하이날"},"image":{"large":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/character/large/b378005-cMZQkZtxLQId.png"},"description":"The heir to the Hynal family. She is calm and dignified despite her young age, though she shows a different side of herself to Vlad.","siteUrl":"https://anilist.co/character/378005"},"role":"SUPPORTING"}]},"genres":["Action","Adventure","Fantasy"],"id":170400,"rankings":[{"allTime":true,"context":"highest rated all time","format":"MANGA","rank":275,"type":"RATED"},{"allTime":true,"context":"most popular all time","format":"MANGA","rank":312,"type":"POPULAR"},{"allTime":false,"context":"highest rated","format":"MANGA","rank":6,"type":"RATED","year":2023},{"allTime":false,"context":"most popular","format":"MANGA","rank":6,"type":"POPULAR","year":2023}],"recommendations":{"edges":[{"node":{"mediaRecommendation":{"countryOfOrigin":"KR","coverImage":{"color":"#1a78f1","extraLarge":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/manga/cover/large/bx159930-qK1P4BNQL0zG.jpg","large":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/manga/cover/medium/bx159930-qK1P4BNQL0zG.jpg","medium":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/manga/cover/small/bx159930-qK1P4BNQL0zG.jpg"},"description":"After Sirone was abandoned in a stable, he was found by a family of hunters and raised in a loving home. Despite the hardships of the peasant life, he learned how to read from a young age and became obsessed with books, especially ones on the history of magic. One day, he has an unlikely encounter with a mage and learns how to enter the \"spirit zone,\" the first step to learning how to use magic. Although they say only nobles can be mages, will Sirone be able to prove his infinite potential?\n\u003cbr\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\n(Source: Tapas)","endDate":{},"format":"MANGA","id":159930,"idMal":154692,"isAdult":false,"meanScore":79,"siteUrl":"https://anilist.co/manga/159930","startDate":{"day":30,"month":12,"year":2022},"status":"RELEASING","synonyms":["Infinite Mage","無限の魔法使い"],"title":{"english":"The Infinite Mage","native":"무한의 마법사","romaji":"Muhanui Mabeopsa","userPreferred":"Muhanui Mabeopsa"},"type":"MANGA"}}},{"node":{"mediaRecommendation":{"countryOfOrigin":"KR","coverImage":{"color":"#e4a11a","extraLarge":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/manga/cover/large/bx135325-YAhEGWro8zFK.jpg","large":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/manga/cover/medium/bx135325-YAhEGWro8zFK.jpg","medium":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/manga/cover/small/bx135325-YAhEGWro8zFK.jpg"},"description":"After witnessing the shocking death of his mother, young Airen Farreira uses sleep to escape his painful reality, earning him the nickname, “the lazy lord”. Yet, in spite of others’ jeers and whispers, Airen has no intention of changing his ways. But when he awakens one day from a dream about a mysterious swordsman, his life’s trajectory takes a complete turn...\n\u003cbr\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\n(Source: WEBTOON)","endDate":{},"format":"MANGA","id":135325,"idMal":146827,"isAdult":false,"meanScore":78,"siteUrl":"https://anilist.co/manga/135325","startDate":{"day":21,"month":5,"year":2021},"status":"HIATUS","synonyms":["The Lazy Prince Becomes a Genius   ","Reformation of the Deadbeat Noble","Der faule Lord meistert die Schwertkunst","懶惰公子成長記"],"title":{"english":"The Lazy Lord Masters the Sword","native":"나태 공자, 노력 천재 되다","romaji":"Natae Gongja, Nolyeog Cheonjae Doeda","userPreferred":"Natae Gongja, Nolyeog Cheonjae Doeda"},"type":"MANGA"}}},{"node":{"mediaRecommendation":{"countryOfOrigin":"KR","coverImage":{"color":"#f1c935","extraLarge":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/manga/cover/large/bx182066-kqOV7WW1DAH4.jpg","large":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/manga/cover/medium/bx182066-kqOV7WW1DAH4.jpg","medium":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/manga/cover/small/bx182066-kqOV7WW1DAH4.jpg"},"description":"Cecil Perdium, the Mercenary King, was killed in battle before he could avenge his family. As he faces death, he learns that Duke Delphine, the man who caused the downfall of his family, didn't work alone. Suddenly waking up as his teenage self, Cecil must work to both overcome his poor reputation and build up his strength to save his family. With their soldiers and knights defecting due to the harsh conditions they must endure, he has his work cut out for him. Can Cecil become the mighty warrior he once was and avert his family's fate?\n\u003cbr\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\n(Source: WEBTOON)","endDate":{},"format":"MANGA","id":182066,"idMal":174559,"isAdult":false,"meanScore":80,"siteUrl":"https://anilist.co/manga/182066","startDate":{"day":23,"month":9,"year":2024},"status":"RELEASING","synonyms":["The Regressed Mercenary’s Machinations","El mercenario que regresó tiene un plan","逆行傭兵は全て計画済み","重生佣兵王的复仇","重生傭兵的完美計畫","แผนเปลี่ยนชะตาของทหารรับจ้าง"],"title":{"english":"The Regressed Mercenary Has a Plan","native":"회귀한 용병은 다 계획이 있다","romaji":"Hoegwihan Yongbyeongeun Da Gyehoegi Itda","userPreferred":"Hoegwihan Yongbyeongeun Da Gyehoegi Itda"},"type":"MANGA"}}},{"node":{"mediaRecommendation":{"countryOfOrigin":"KR","coverImage":{"color":"#5078e4","extraLarge":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/manga/cover/large/bx163824-KiablxybJD6i.jpg","large":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/manga/cover/medium/bx163824-KiablxybJD6i.jpg","medium":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/manga/cover/small/bx163824-KiablxybJD6i.jpg"},"description":"Raised to kill like a pack of loyal hounds, the Baskerville children took countless lives as a band of fearsome assassins. Despite being the shunned illegitimate son of the brood, Vikir served his family faithfully, only to meet his untimely demise at his father’s hands. But when he is inexplicably reborn with a second chance at life, Vikir, armed with the memories and knowledge of his past, swears to rise above the pack and take his revenge. This time, he's ready to bite the hand that feeds.\n\u003cbr\u003e\u003cbr\u003e(Source: Tapas)","endDate":{},"format":"MANGA","id":163824,"idMal":157888,"isAdult":false,"meanScore":80,"siteUrl":"https://anilist.co/manga/163824","startDate":{"day":14,"month":4,"year":2023},"status":"RELEASING","synonyms":["Revenge of the Iron-Blooded Sword Hound","Revenge of the Sword Clan's Hound","Die Rückkehr des Jagdhundes aus Eisen und Blut","回帰した鉄血の猟犬","铁血剑家猎犬的回归"],"title":{"english":"Revenge of the Baskerville Bloodhound","native":"철혈검가 사냥개의 회귀","romaji":"Cheolhyeolgeomga Sanyanggaeui Hoegwi","userPreferred":"Cheolhyeolgeomga Sanyanggaeui Hoegwi"},"type":"MANGA"}}},{"node":{"mediaRecommendation":{"countryOfOrigin":"KR","coverImage":{"extraLarge":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/manga/cover/large/bx149332-adkSyOFY3c5U.jpg","large":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/manga/cover/medium/bx149332-adkSyOFY3c5U.jpg","medium":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/manga/cover/small/bx149332-adkSyOFY3c5U.jpg"},"description":"Jin Runcandel was destined to become the head of his swordmaster clan. But despite his best efforts, he's banished for his shoddy swordsmanship. Though Jin eventually makes a contract with the god Solderet and is freed from the curse that hindered his abilities, he meets a rather unfortunate end. In the next moment, however, he awakens as a baby, long before his tragedy began. Armed with a second chance and some new powers, Jin swears to fulfill his destiny and become the ultimate swordmaster. \u003cbr\u003e\u003cbr\u003e(Source: Tapas)","endDate":{},"format":"MANGA","id":149332,"idMal":146949,"isAdult":false,"meanScore":79,"siteUrl":"https://anilist.co/manga/149332","startDate":{"day":30,"month":4,"year":2022},"status":"HIATUS","synonyms":["The Youngest Son of a Master Swordsman   ","Swordmaster's Youngest Son","Youngest Son of the Renowned Swordsmanship Clan","剣術名家の末息子","劍術名家的小兒子","剑术名门的小儿子"],"title":{"english":"The Swordmaster's Son","native":"검술명가 막내아들","romaji":"Geomsulmyeongga Mangnaeadeul","userPreferred":"Geomsulmyeongga Mangnaeadeul"},"type":"MANGA"}}},{"node":{"mediaRecommendation":{"countryOfOrigin":"KR","coverImage":{"color":"#3578f1","extraLarge":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/manga/cover/large/bx150508-xh4xwMVQB6Vf.jpg","large":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/manga/cover/medium/bx150508-xh4xwMVQB6Vf.jpg","medium":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/manga/cover/small/bx150508-xh4xwMVQB6Vf.jpg"},"description":"Though Leon has years' worth of training in swordsmanship, it's still not enough to defeat his rival at the royal academy, Lionel. That is until one day, the holy sword Elsyd appears and names Leon as his chosen hero and new pupil. The young swordmaster didn't expect the holy sword's instruction to be easy, but now Elsyd is even trying to teach him how to... see? If Leon can manage to endure this, will he finally be strong enough to beat the privileged Lionel and earn his place in the world?\n\u003cbr\u003e\u003cbr\u003e(Source: Tapas)","endDate":{},"format":"MANGA","id":150508,"idMal":148456,"isAdult":false,"meanScore":72,"siteUrl":"https://anilist.co/manga/150508","startDate":{"day":4,"month":6,"year":2022},"status":"HIATUS","synonyms":["Leveling Up With The Sword","Overpowered Sword","剣任せでレベルアップ"],"title":{"english":"Disciple of the Holy Sword","native":"검빨로 레벨업","romaji":"Geomppallo Level Up","userPreferred":"Geomppallo Level Up"},"type":"MANGA"}}},{"node":{"mediaRecommendation":{"countryOfOrigin":"KR","coverImage":{"color":"#f1d6a1","extraLarge":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/manga/cover/large/bx179963-BS0rA7MmNO31.jpg","large":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/manga/cover/medium/bx179963-BS0rA7MmNO31.jpg","medium":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/manga/cover/small/bx179963-BS0rA7MmNO31.jpg"},"description":"Betrayed and on the brink of death, Ian Verocian, a mage and the emperor of the Variel Empire, is sent a hundred years back in time by a forbidden spell. He wakes up as Ian Vratz, a margrave's illegitimate son, and soon learns he's about to be sent off to a desert tribe as part of a political treaty. Now, Ian must use his wits and powerful magic to gather allies and figure out the plots lurking around him. The question is... can this young mage change his fate before time runs out once more?\n\u003cbr\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\n(Source: Tapas)","endDate":{},"format":"MANGA","id":179963,"idMal":170725,"isAdult":false,"meanScore":67,"siteUrl":"https://anilist.co/manga/179963","startDate":{"day":31,"month":5,"year":2024},"status":"RELEASING","synonyms":["Margrave's Bastard Son Was the Emperor","The Margrave's Bastard Used to be the Emperor","辺境伯家の落ちこぼれは皇帝だった"],"title":{"english":"Ian the Illegitimate Son Was an Emperor","native":"변경백 서자는 황제였다","romaji":"Byeongyeongbaek Seojaneun Hwangjeyeotda","userPreferred":"Byeongyeongbaek Seojaneun Hwangjeyeotda"},"type":"MANGA"}}},{"node":{"mediaRecommendation":{"countryOfOrigin":"KR","coverImage":{"color":"#5d93e4","extraLarge":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/manga/cover/large/bx183855-BbnSsUPiOVrM.jpg","large":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/manga/cover/medium/bx183855-BbnSsUPiOVrM.jpg","medium":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/manga/cover/small/bx183855-BbnSsUPiOVrM.jpg"},"description":"Theo Ragnar, the 31st son of the mighty Grand Duke of Ragnar, was born without the legendary Ragnar Gift—a fatal flaw in a family where might is right. Labeled the “Ragnar Defect,” he and his mother were betrayed, meeting a brutal end at the hands of those they trusted. But death was only the beginning. Reborn at 17, Theo awakens not only with the Ragnar Gift, but with powers far beyond imagination. Fueled by vengeance and a second chance, he sets out to claim the glory he was once denied.\u003cbr\u003e\u003cbr\u003e(Source: Tapas)","endDate":{},"format":"MANGA","id":183855,"idMal":175209,"isAdult":false,"meanScore":75,"siteUrl":"https://anilist.co/manga/183855","startDate":{"day":8,"month":10,"year":2024},"status":"RELEASING","synonyms":["Regressing as the Reincarnated Bastard of the Sword Clan","ラグナール～回帰の剣士～"],"title":{"english":"The Bastard of Swordborne","native":"회귀검가의 서자가 사는 법","romaji":"Hoegwigeomgaui Seojaga Saneun Beop","userPreferred":"Hoegwigeomgaui Seojaga Saneun Beop"},"type":"MANGA"}}}]},"relations":{},"siteUrl":"https://anilist.co/manga/170400"}},"updated_at":"2026-03-15T07:10:02.964559+03:00"},"180890":{"value":{"Media":{"characters":{"edges":[{"id":519557,"node":{"dateOfBirth":{},"gender":"Male","id":354865,"image":{"large":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/character/large/b354865-pqRMiYbs0Tov.png"},"isFavourite":false,"name":{"full":"Yang-Cheon Ku","native":"구양천"},"siteUrl":"https://anilist.co/character/354865"},"role":"MAIN"}]},"genres":["Action","Adventure","Fantasy"],"id":180890,"rankings":[{"allTime":false,"context":"highest rated","format":"MANGA","rank":33,"type":"RATED","year":2024},{"allTime":false,"context":"most popular","format":"MANGA","rank":11,"type":"POPULAR","year":2024}],"recommendations":{"edges":[{"node":{"mediaRecommendation":{"bannerImage":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/manga/banner/132144-tITrsibdFo3n.jpg","countryOfOrigin":"KR","coverImage":{"color":"#e45078","extraLarge":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/manga/cover/large/bx132144-i5B4VnG9sRgh.png","large":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/manga/cover/medium/bx132144-i5B4VnG9sRgh.png","medium":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/manga/cover/small/bx132144-i5B4VnG9sRgh.png"},"description":"When Cheong-Myeong of the Mount Hua Sect awakens a hundred years in the future, his last memories are of a bloody battle against the Leader of the Demonic Cult, the evil Cheon-Ma. The battle almost saw the end of the Ten Great Sects of ancient China, when Cheong-Myeong ended the hard-fought struggle by striking down Cheon-Ma. Soon after, he succumbed to his wounds, filled with regret at their pyrrhic victory. All is not lost, however, as he awakens to his second chance at life. Shocked to find his beloved Mount Hua Sect reduced to a mere shadow of itself in the present day, Cheong-Myeong embarks on a journey to restore Mount Hua to its former glory.\u003cbr\u003e\n\u003cbr\u003e\n(Source: WEBTOON, edited)","endDate":{},"format":"MANGA","id":132144,"idMal":146878,"isAdult":false,"meanScore":84,"siteUrl":"https://anilist.co/manga/132144","startDate":{"day":23,"month":3,"year":2021},"status":"HIATUS","synonyms":["Return of The Mount Hua Sect","Return of the Flowery Mountain Sect","Le retour du clan Hwasan","El retorno del Monte Hua","劍尊歸來","หวนคืนสู่ฮวาซาน","剑尊归来"],"title":{"english":"Return of the Blossoming Blade","native":"화산귀환","romaji":"Hwasangwihwan","userPreferred":"Hwasangwihwan"},"type":"MANGA"}}},{"node":{"mediaRecommendation":{"countryOfOrigin":"KR","coverImage":{"color":"#a15de4","extraLarge":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/manga/cover/large/bx185816-DhnjJEpwiur1.jpg","large":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/manga/cover/medium/bx185816-DhnjJEpwiur1.jpg","medium":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/manga/cover/small/bx185816-DhnjJEpwiur1.jpg"},"description":"After a lifetime of bloodshed, the Heavenly Demon longs for peace. In his final moments, he uncovers the truth about his power and yearns for a different life. He wakes up in the body of Tae-San Byeok, the frail second son of a powerful merchant family, barely clinging to life. Using his knowledge from his life as the Heavenly Demon, Tae-San must navigate a world of temptation and corruption to survive. As his martial arts reputation grows, new enemies emerge to disrupt his quiet life. Yet, Tae-San is determined to live on his own terms, despite the chaos around him.\u003cbr\u003e\u003cbr\u003e(Source: WEBTOON)","endDate":{},"format":"MANGA","id":185816,"idMal":176735,"isAdult":false,"meanScore":72,"siteUrl":"https://anilist.co/manga/185816","startDate":{"day":26,"month":11,"year":2024},"status":"RELEASING","synonyms":["天魔只想苟着","天魔想低調過日子","ชาตินี้เทพมารขอชิล"],"title":{"english":"The Heavenly Demon Wants a Quiet Life","native":"천마는 조용히 살고싶다","romaji":"Cheonmaneun Joyonghi Salgosipda","userPreferred":"Cheonmaneun Joyonghi Salgosipda"},"type":"MANGA"}}},{"node":{"mediaRecommendation":{"countryOfOrigin":"KR","coverImage":{"color":"#bb5df1","extraLarge":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/manga/cover/large/bx147027-6vlUI1C4kK9Z.jpg","large":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/manga/cover/medium/bx147027-6vlUI1C4kK9Z.jpg","medium":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/manga/cover/small/bx147027-6vlUI1C4kK9Z.jpg"},"description":"An ordinary middle schooler, Lee Seong-Min, is summoned to a world called \"Eria\". He endures dozens of years with no skills or powers, and makes it through all kinds of hardships to survive, but dies miserably in the end.\u003cbr\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\n\nHowever, before he dies, he gets sent back to the past after obtaining the ‘Stone of the Past Life’ by chance, and gains the opportunity to start his life anew.\u003cbr\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\n\nYet, he still lives a life without any talents; nothing. Although he can’t approach the powerful people around him due to the \"wall\" surrounding them, he moves forward step by step with firm determination, never giving up.\u003cbr\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\n\n\u003cI\u003e\"No matter what, I’m going to live a better life than my previous one even if I have to struggle!\"\u003c/I\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\n\n(Source: KakaoPage, translated)","endDate":{},"format":"MANGA","id":147027,"idMal":152612,"isAdult":false,"meanScore":75,"siteUrl":"https://anilist.co/manga/147027","startDate":{"day":27,"month":3,"year":2022},"status":"HIATUS","synonyms":[" Possessing Nothing","Worthless Regression"],"title":{"english":"Returning With Absolutely Nothing","native":"쥐뿔도 없는 회귀","romaji":"Jwippuldo Eomneun Hoegwi","userPreferred":"Jwippuldo Eomneun Hoegwi"},"type":"MANGA"}}},{"node":{"mediaRecommendation":{"countryOfOrigin":"KR","coverImage":{"color":"#50a1e4","extraLarge":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/manga/cover/large/bx194523-cLAK6gTAKNkM.jpg","large":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/manga/cover/medium/bx194523-cLAK6gTAKNkM.jpg","medium":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/manga/cover/small/bx194523-cLAK6gTAKNkM.jpg"},"description":"Wuseong Dan, the man who ruled over the martial world with his fists alone. After unexpectedly losing a duel against two practitioners of the Demonic Way, he’s reborn into the body of the wild child heir apparent of the affluent Silver River Merchants. Not one to leave debts unpaid, be they to his benefit or detriment, Wuseong sets out on his path of revenge in the body of Jineon Lee. Using his knowledge of martial arts from his past life and the wealth of his current life, he only has one goal: get stronger and kill those who killed him.\u003cbr\u003e\u003cbr\u003e(Source: WEBTOON)","endDate":{},"format":"MANGA","id":194523,"idMal":182882,"isAdult":false,"meanScore":74,"siteUrl":"https://anilist.co/manga/194523","startDate":{"day":14,"month":6,"year":2025},"status":"RELEASING","synonyms":["拳王归来"],"title":{"english":"Reincarnation of the Fist King","native":"권왕환생","romaji":"Gwonwanghwansaeng","userPreferred":"Gwonwanghwansaeng"},"type":"MANGA"}}}]},"relations":{},"siteUrl":"https://anilist.co/manga/180890"}},"updated_at":"2026-02-26T18:08:32.916282+03:00"},"180891":{"value":{"Media":{"characters":{"edges":[{"id":505312,"node":{"dateOfBirth":{},"description":"He is the second son of [Wu-Jin Geom](https://anilist.co/character/346843/WooJin-Geom). He was an incompetent young master who could not properly compete with his older brother and was easily deprived of the position of successor. However, when he lost everything, from his father to everyone around him, he decided to use The Great Regression Technique. After many years, he gathered all the necessary materials for the regression technique and decided to return to the past to take revenge on Moogi Hwa.\n\nAfter being able to reach the past, his goal would be to kill the one who deserves to die and save those who should not die. Because he lost everything to Hwa Moogi, he has a vengeful side, but more than anything, after losing everything to Hwa Moogi, he looks back and says he has no good memories, and tries to get closer to his father by talking to him, for his own good.","gender":"Male","id":346842,"image":{"large":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/character/large/b346842-bgvgqU22gOKq.png"},"isFavourite":false,"name":{"alternative":["Second Young Master"],"full":"Mu-Geuk Geom","native":"검무극"},"siteUrl":"https://anilist.co/character/346842"},"role":"MAIN"},{"id":505313,"node":{"dateOfBirth":{},"description":"Woojin Geom, the Heavenly Demon, the Strongest of This Era, the Cult Lord of the Heavenly Demon Divine Cult.","gender":"Male","id":346843,"image":{"large":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/character/large/b346843-89lzi1VL10tH.png"},"isFavourite":false,"name":{"alternative":["Heavenly Demon"],"full":"U-Jin Geom","native":"검우진"},"siteUrl":"https://anilist.co/character/346843"},"role":"SUPPORTING"},{"id":505314,"node":{"dateOfBirth":{},"description":"Lee-An is a Mu-Geuk's Bodyguard.","gender":"Female","id":346844,"image":{"large":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/character/large/b346844-ZhR6k3Nz7EVR.png"},"isFavourite":false,"name":{"full":"Lee-An","native":"이안"},"siteUrl":"https://anilist.co/character/346844"},"role":"SUPPORTING"},{"id":513602,"node":{"dateOfBirth":{},"description":"Cheon-Pa Gu, the Blood Heaven Blade Demon, is a One of the Eight Demon Supremes of the Heavenly Demon Divine Cult.","gender":"Male","id":352210,"image":{"large":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/character/large/b352210-9gt9gdlBuUmc.png"},"isFavourite":false,"name":{"alternative":["Blood Heaven Blade Demon"],"full":"Cheon-Pa Gu","native":"구천파"},"siteUrl":"https://anilist.co/character/352210"},"role":"SUPPORTING"},{"id":513603,"node":{"dateOfBirth":{},"description":"Dae-Ryong Seo is a a special investigation officer.","gender":"Male","id":352212,"image":{"large":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/character/large/b352212-DwGjqvKPGDX8.png"},"isFavourite":false,"name":{"full":"Dae-Ryong Seo","native":"서대룡"},"siteUrl":"https://anilist.co/character/352212"},"role":"SUPPORTING"},{"id":526220,"node":{"dateOfBirth":{},"description":"One of the Eight Demon Supremes of the Heavenly Demon Divine Cult.","gender":"Female","id":360252,"image":{"large":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/character/large/b360252-8CEothDEBMF9.jpg"},"isFavourite":false,"name":{"alternative":["일화검존","One Flower Sword Supreme"],"full":"Yeon-Rang So","native":"소연랑"},"siteUrl":"https://anilist.co/character/360252"},"role":"SUPPORTING"},{"id":556032,"node":{"dateOfBirth":{},"description":"A man who was bound by shackles.","gender":"Male","id":386101,"image":{"large":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/character/large/b386101-0azlfOBOTpEV.jpg"},"isFavourite":false,"name":{"full":"Go-Wol","native":"고월"},"siteUrl":"https://anilist.co/character/386101"},"role":"SUPPORTING"}]},"genres":["Action","Fantasy"],"id":180891,"rankings":[{"allTime":true,"context":"highest rated all time","format":"MANGA","rank":375,"type":"RATED"},{"allTime":false,"context":"highest rated","format":"MANGA","rank":5,"type":"RATED","year":2024},{"allTime":false,"context":"most popular","format":"MANGA","rank":9,"type":"POPULAR","year":2024}],"recommendations":{"edges":[{"node":{"mediaRecommendation":{"countryOfOrigin":"KR","coverImage":{"color":"#ffe435","extraLarge":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/manga/cover/large/bx175946-rx6eIfakvWYV.jpg","large":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/manga/cover/medium/bx175946-rx6eIfakvWYV.jpg","medium":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/manga/cover/small/bx175946-rx6eIfakvWYV.jpg"},"description":"All Jeong wants is a second chance – for revenge! His grandfather’s gruesome death has transformed him into the bloodthirsty and ruthless Scythe Demon. He will stop at nothing until he has killed the man responsible. Yet rage and determination alone are not enough. He must train in martial arts if he ever wants to stand a chance against such a formidable foe. Will he succeed in his revenge on the murderer of his grandfather?\n\u003cbr\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\n(Source: WEBTOON)","endDate":{},"format":"MANGA","id":175946,"idMal":168980,"isAdult":false,"meanScore":83,"siteUrl":"https://anilist.co/manga/175946","startDate":{"day":4,"month":3,"year":2024},"status":"RELEASING","synonyms":["The Chaotic God of Extraordinary Strength","怪力 亂神","ลับลางลวง"],"title":{"english":"Myst, Might, Mayhem","native":"괴력 난신","romaji":"Goeryeok Nansin","userPreferred":"Goeryeok Nansin"},"type":"MANGA"}}},{"node":{"mediaRecommendation":{"countryOfOrigin":"KR","coverImage":{"color":"#f1bb93","extraLarge":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/manga/cover/large/bx176790-qR0AhWd6xxWC.png","large":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/manga/cover/medium/bx176790-qR0AhWd6xxWC.png","medium":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/manga/cover/small/bx176790-qR0AhWd6xxWC.png"},"description":"Regret is the bane of old men. When aging Alliance Lord Hajin Cheon of the Grand Martial Alliance reflects on his immense legacy, he finds that he recalls little of his deeds or even the lives of his closest advisors. Stricken by a mysterious ailment, Hajin suddenly passes away only to wake up in the body of Ridan Byeok, heir to the Byeok Clan of swordsmen. The only problem is, Ridan is a well-known wastrel, the polar opposite of the virtuous and stern Hajin. Righting the wrongs of his predecessor, Hajin begins to uncover the truth behind his death…\u003cbr\u003e\u003cbr\u003e(Source: WEBTOON)","endDate":{},"format":"MANGA","id":176790,"idMal":168981,"isAdult":false,"meanScore":75,"siteUrl":"https://anilist.co/manga/176790","startDate":{"day":17,"month":3,"year":2024},"status":"RELEASING","synonyms":["Reborn as The Heavenly Demon","Reincarnation of the Heavenly Demon"],"title":{"english":"Reincarnated Murim Lord","native":"환생천마","romaji":"Hwansaengcheonma","userPreferred":"Hwansaengcheonma"},"type":"MANGA"}}},{"node":{"mediaRecommendation":{"bannerImage":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/manga/banner/137304-6aGcY98dBeUY.jpg","countryOfOrigin":"KR","coverImage":{"color":"#e4935d","extraLarge":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/manga/cover/large/bx137304-XZ91kOmUIMQo.png","large":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/manga/cover/medium/bx137304-XZ91kOmUIMQo.png","medium":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/manga/cover/small/bx137304-XZ91kOmUIMQo.png"},"description":"The Mad Demon, Ja-Ha Lee, dreams of becoming the God of Martial Arts. Unfortunately, his dreams are dashed after he falls off a cliff while running from the Demonic Cult for stealing the Jade of Heaven. Yet this is not the end for Ja-Ha -- he awakens from the fall to find himself back in his 20s. With his knowledge of the future and of martial arts, he now has a chance at revenge and at getting life right this time. Will he be able to fulfill his dream this time around, or is he doomed to face the same fate yet again?\n\u003cbr\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\n(Source: WEBTOON)","endDate":{},"format":"MANGA","id":137304,"idMal":147577,"isAdult":false,"meanScore":79,"siteUrl":"https://anilist.co/manga/137304","startDate":{"day":22,"month":7,"year":2021},"status":"HIATUS","synonyms":["The Return of the Crazy Demon","อสูรคลั่งผู้หวนคืน","狂魔重生記","狂魔重生"],"title":{"english":"Return of the Mad Demon","native":"광마회귀","romaji":"Gwangmahoegwi","userPreferred":"Gwangmahoegwi"},"type":"MANGA"}}},{"node":{"mediaRecommendation":{"bannerImage":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/manga/banner/132144-tITrsibdFo3n.jpg","countryOfOrigin":"KR","coverImage":{"color":"#e45078","extraLarge":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/manga/cover/large/bx132144-i5B4VnG9sRgh.png","large":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/manga/cover/medium/bx132144-i5B4VnG9sRgh.png","medium":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/manga/cover/small/bx132144-i5B4VnG9sRgh.png"},"description":"When Cheong-Myeong of the Mount Hua Sect awakens a hundred years in the future, his last memories are of a bloody battle against the Leader of the Demonic Cult, the evil Cheon-Ma. The battle almost saw the end of the Ten Great Sects of ancient China, when Cheong-Myeong ended the hard-fought struggle by striking down Cheon-Ma. Soon after, he succumbed to his wounds, filled with regret at their pyrrhic victory. All is not lost, however, as he awakens to his second chance at life. Shocked to find his beloved Mount Hua Sect reduced to a mere shadow of itself in the present day, Cheong-Myeong embarks on a journey to restore Mount Hua to its former glory.\u003cbr\u003e\n\u003cbr\u003e\n(Source: WEBTOON, edited)","endDate":{},"format":"MANGA","id":132144,"idMal":146878,"isAdult":false,"meanScore":84,"siteUrl":"https://anilist.co/manga/132144","startDate":{"day":23,"month":3,"year":2021},"status":"HIATUS","synonyms":["Return of The Mount Hua Sect","Return of the Flowery Mountain Sect","Le retour du clan Hwasan","El retorno del Monte Hua","劍尊歸來","หวนคืนสู่ฮวาซาน","剑尊归来"],"title":{"english":"Return of the Blossoming Blade","native":"화산귀환","romaji":"Hwasangwihwan","userPreferred":"Hwasangwihwan"},"type":"MANGA"}}},{"node":{"mediaRecommendation":{"bannerImage":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/manga/banner/183285-WDUO6vLjpwAp.jpg","countryOfOrigin":"KR","coverImage":{"color":"#f15d50","extraLarge":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/manga/cover/large/bx183285-ZfemXvC1AHGk.jpg","large":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/manga/cover/medium/bx183285-ZfemXvC1AHGk.jpg","medium":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/manga/cover/small/bx183285-ZfemXvC1AHGk.jpg"},"description":"Twenty years have passed since the Great War, but petty theft and exploitation have taken root during times of peace. The once dazzling world of Murim is a mere shadow of its former self, but one young enigmatic swordsman has sworn to restore Jianghu to its former glory. Will the noble principles of justice and loyalty prevail over corruption and greed?\u003cbr\u003e\u003cbr\u003e(Source: WEBTOON)","endDate":{},"format":"MANGA","id":183285,"idMal":174691,"isAdult":false,"meanScore":76,"siteUrl":"https://anilist.co/manga/183285","startDate":{"day":27,"month":9,"year":2024},"status":"RELEASING","synonyms":["Absolute Dominion","绝代君临","絕代君臨","天下君臨～江湖を覇せし者～","เซียนพิชิตหล้า"],"title":{"english":"Absolute Reign","native":"절대군림","romaji":"Jeoldaegullim","userPreferred":"Jeoldaegullim"},"type":"MANGA"}}},{"node":{"mediaRecommendation":{"bannerImage":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/manga/banner/119521-CPhjvDuMReVg.jpg","chapters":202,"countryOfOrigin":"KR","coverImage":{"extraLarge":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/manga/cover/large/bx119521-qYqxFvn0NnXo.png","large":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/manga/cover/medium/bx119521-qYqxFvn0NnXo.png","medium":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/manga/cover/small/bx119521-qYqxFvn0NnXo.png"},"description":"For decades, the brave warriors of the Northern Heavenly Sect fought to keep the world safe from the evil Silent Night. But when the fourth generation leader is accused of colluding with the enemy, he is forced to disband the sect and commit suicide to protect his son, Moo-Won. With no family and allies left, Moo-Won leads a dreary life under close surveillance... until a surprise attack from the Silent Night gives him a chance to escape to the mountains. There, the young warrior trains to master the fighting techniques of his predecessors, before the mysterious disappearance of a loved one brings him back to the mainland. Follow Moo-Won as he embarks on a journey to avenge his father’s death and take down the villains who threaten to plunge the world into darkness! \u003cbr\u003e\n\u003cbr\u003e\n(Source: Tappytoon)\n","endDate":{"day":19,"month":11,"year":2024},"format":"MANGA","id":119521,"idMal":134744,"isAdult":false,"meanScore":85,"siteUrl":"https://anilist.co/manga/119521","startDate":{"day":31,"month":12,"year":2019},"status":"FINISHED","synonyms":["北剑江湖"],"title":{"english":"The Legend of the Northern Blade","native":"북검전기","romaji":"Bukgeom Jeongi","userPreferred":"Bukgeom Jeongi"},"type":"MANGA"}}},{"node":{"mediaRecommendation":{"countryOfOrigin":"KR","coverImage":{"color":"#f1bb5d","extraLarge":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/manga/cover/large/bx183376-Cw3VnZAItw2a.jpg","large":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/manga/cover/medium/bx183376-Cw3VnZAItw2a.jpg","medium":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/manga/cover/small/bx183376-Cw3VnZAItw2a.jpg"},"description":"Gifted by the heavens yet cursed by fate, Yeonshin was born with unimaginable talent in martial arts. But this very gift condemned him to a life that would end before adulthood. With the right opportunities, he had the potential to become a legendary hero, or the reincarnation of the Heavenly Demon. Yet fate cast him into the third-rate Jeong Clan, a family of no particular renown. Now, with time slipping through his fingers, Yeonshin must find a way to defy his doomed destiny.\u003cbr\u003e\u003cbr\u003e(Source: WEBTOON)","endDate":{},"format":"MANGA","id":183376,"idMal":174692,"isAdult":false,"meanScore":77,"siteUrl":"https://anilist.co/manga/183376","startDate":{"day":29,"month":9,"year":2024},"status":"HIATUS","synonyms":["How a Terminally Ill Genius Survives","Surviving as a Genius on Borrowed Time"],"title":{"english":"Chronicles of a Doomed Prodigy","native":"시한부 천재가 살아남는 법","romaji":"Sihanbu Cheonjaega Saranamneun Beop","userPreferred":"Sihanbu Cheonjaega Saranamneun Beop"},"type":"MANGA"}}},{"node":{"mediaRecommendation":{"bannerImage":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/manga/banner/120980-7ak3NnHP5f2X.jpg","countryOfOrigin":"KR","coverImage":{"color":"#e4506b","extraLarge":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/manga/cover/large/bx120980-RZ9WLd0o9hyo.jpg","large":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/manga/cover/medium/bx120980-RZ9WLd0o9hyo.jpg","medium":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/manga/cover/small/bx120980-RZ9WLd0o9hyo.jpg"},"description":"Nanotechnology meets martial arts at the Mashin Academy. Yeo-Un’s mother may not be one of the High Priest’s six official wives, but his father’s blood still qualifies him for a chance at the position of Minor Priest. Will a mysterious nanomachine injection from a future descendent help Yeo-un in this fierce competition against his powerful half-siblings?\n\u003cbr\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\n(Source: WEBTOON)\n","endDate":{},"format":"MANGA","id":120980,"idMal":147863,"isAdult":false,"meanScore":81,"siteUrl":"https://anilist.co/manga/120980","startDate":{"day":10,"month":6,"year":2020},"status":"RELEASING","synonyms":["Nano Mashin","某天成为魔神","奈米魔神","ナノ魔神","นาโนมาชิน"],"title":{"english":"Nano Machine","native":"나노마신","romaji":"Nano Machine","userPreferred":"Nano Machine"},"type":"MANGA"}}}]},"relations":{},"siteUrl":"https://anilist.co/manga/180891"}},"updated_at":"2026-03-07T00:44:13.738665+03:00"},"187427":{"value":{"Media":{"characters":{"edges":[{"id":526274,"node":{"dateOfBirth":{},"description":"U-Jin Kim is a game developer, who possesses the body of Deculein, an in-game villain.","gender":"Male","id":360328,"image":{"large":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/character/large/b360328-XENdy0EjI9DF.jpg"},"isFavourite":false,"name":{"alternative":["U-Jin Kim (김우진)"],"full":"Deculein von Grahan Yukline","native":"데큘레인 폰 그라한 유크라인"},"siteUrl":"https://anilist.co/character/360328"},"role":"MAIN"},{"id":526273,"node":{"dateOfBirth":{},"description":"Deculein's fiancée.\n\nHer relationship with Deculein is not very good. From the day of their first engagement, she was disappointed by his actions as if he was trying to buy her with his wealth. After that, she learned of all the corruption and evil deeds that Deculein committed to get in her way or gain power in the Magic Tower, and she came to hate him even more.","gender":"Female","id":360327,"image":{"large":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/character/large/b360327-ZCjbelmTVPnM.jpg"},"isFavourite":false,"name":{"full":"Yulie von Deya Freyden","native":"율리 폰 데이아 프하이르덴"},"siteUrl":"https://anilist.co/character/360327"},"role":"SUPPORTING"},{"id":526275,"node":{"dateOfBirth":{},"description":"She is a named character who can kill anyone with just a single strand of her hair. A true warrior and adventurer who has reached the pinnacle of physical strength.","gender":"Female","id":360329,"image":{"large":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/character/large/b360329-4c55MBw6PTpw.jpg"},"isFavourite":false,"name":{"full":"Ganesha","native":"가네샤"},"siteUrl":"https://anilist.co/character/360329"},"role":"SUPPORTING"},{"id":526276,"node":{"dateOfBirth":{},"gender":"Female","id":360330,"image":{"large":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/character/large/b360330-FqpBpvT4RQ3R.jpg"},"isFavourite":false,"name":{"full":"Sylvia von Yossepin Iliade","native":"실비아 폰 유세핀 일레이드"},"siteUrl":"https://anilist.co/character/360330"},"role":"SUPPORTING"},{"id":526277,"node":{"dateOfBirth":{},"description":"She is the daughter of the former head of the Yukline family and his second wife, and is Deculein's half-sister.","gender":"Female","id":360331,"image":{"large":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/character/large/b360331-mZt5i9WIYWuL.jpg"},"isFavourite":false,"name":{"full":"Yeriel von Dellun Yukline","native":"예리엘 폰 델룬 유크라인"},"siteUrl":"https://anilist.co/character/360331"},"role":"SUPPORTING"},{"id":526278,"node":{"dateOfBirth":{},"gender":"Female","id":360332,"image":{"large":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/character/large/b360332-954qIv1OpjV3.jpg"},"isFavourite":false,"name":{"alternative":["Epherene Luna"],"full":"Ifrin Luna","native":"이프린 루나"},"siteUrl":"https://anilist.co/character/360332"},"role":"SUPPORTING"},{"id":532954,"node":{"dateOfBirth":{},"description":"Yuria is an in-game character who got possessed  by Kim U-Jin's ex-girlfriend, Yuara.","gender":"Female","id":365694,"image":{"large":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/character/large/b365694-U4m7wBCAyv4Q.jpg"},"isFavourite":false,"name":{"alternative":["Lia","Yuara"],"full":"Yuria","native":"유리아"},"siteUrl":"https://anilist.co/character/365694"},"role":"SUPPORTING"},{"id":532955,"node":{"dateOfBirth":{},"description":"She is the chairman of the Imperial University and a wizard who rose to the rank of Ether at a young age.","gender":"Female","id":365697,"image":{"large":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/character/large/b365697-H7dk5WB1WRPK.jpg"},"isFavourite":false,"name":{"full":"Adeline Sezelian","native":"아드린느 세젤리안"},"siteUrl":"https://anilist.co/character/365697"},"role":"SUPPORTING"}]},"genres":["Drama","Fantasy"],"id":187427,"rankings":[{"allTime":false,"context":"highest rated","format":"MANGA","rank":2,"type":"RATED","year":2025},{"allTime":false,"context":"most popular","format":"MANGA","rank":2,"type":"POPULAR","year":2025}],"recommendations":{"edges":[{"node":{"mediaRecommendation":{"countryOfOrigin":"KR","coverImage":{"color":"#5da1e4","extraLarge":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/manga/cover/large/bx150836-vWf0Hgyey7Mj.jpg","large":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/manga/cover/medium/bx150836-vWf0Hgyey7Mj.jpg","medium":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/manga/cover/small/bx150836-vWf0Hgyey7Mj.jpg"},"description":"Machiavelli and Gerrard are just one of the many names the new professor of Ceoren Academy uses to disguise his identity, and now he can add one more to his list, Professor Ludger Cherish. The real Ludger Cherish dies on board a train during a terrorist attack, making him the perfect target for a new identity. Little does the new professor know, Ludger Cherish was involved in something deep and secret. The new Professor Ludger has to be careful to not get caught by the school and the dangerous secret society.\n\u003cbr\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\n(Source: WEBTOON)","endDate":{},"format":"MANGA","id":150836,"idMal":149801,"isAdult":false,"meanScore":77,"siteUrl":"https://anilist.co/manga/150836","startDate":{"day":4,"month":6,"year":2022},"status":"RELEASING","synonyms":["Academy's Undercover Professor","I Got a Fake Job at the Academy","魔法学院的伪装教师"],"title":{"english":"The Academy's Undercover Professor","native":"아카데미에 위장취업당했다","romaji":"Academy Wijangchwieopdanghaetda","userPreferred":"Academy Wijangchwieopdanghaetda"},"type":"MANGA"}}},{"node":{"mediaRecommendation":{"bannerImage":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/manga/banner/118408-FT9bkwTdii7D.jpg","countryOfOrigin":"KR","coverImage":{"color":"#e45d93","extraLarge":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/manga/cover/large/bx118408-zZuOINqjBZYn.jpg","large":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/manga/cover/medium/bx118408-zZuOINqjBZYn.jpg","medium":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/manga/cover/small/bx118408-zZuOINqjBZYn.jpg"},"description":"This game’s got me obsessed! It’s like it’s taken over my life... wait—HARD MODE ACTIVATED. No-no-no-no-no! It has literally taken me and thrown me into the part of Penelope Eckhart. Love is easy as the heroine, but as the hated villainess, I’m trying very hard not to die… at the hands of my brothers… the prince… a fork… every possible ending is death! This world is stacked against me, but can my wits and insider game knowledge score the affection of these male characters? Or the reset button???\u003cbr\u003e\u003cbr\u003e(Source: Tapas)","endDate":{},"format":"MANGA","id":118408,"idMal":133641,"isAdult":false,"meanScore":84,"siteUrl":"https://anilist.co/manga/118408","startDate":{"day":1,"month":5,"year":2020},"status":"RELEASING","synonyms":["Death Is The Only Ending For The Villainess ","The Villain's Ending Is Death ","Seule la mort attend la Vilaine","Penelope – Das Böse ist dem Tod geweiht","O Único Destino da Vilã é a Morte","O Único Destino dos Vilões é a Morte","Единственный конец злодейки - смерть","Єдиний фінал лиходіїв – смерть","Kötülerin Kaderi Yok Olmaktır","Kematian adalah Akhir Sang Antagonis","悪役のエンディングは死のみ","反派角色只有死亡結局","恋爱手游的男主都很危险","恶役只有死亡结局","เป็นตัวร้ายก็ต้องตายเท่านั้น","Przeznaczeniem Złoczyńców jest śmierć"],"title":{"english":"Villains Are Destined to Die","native":"악역의 엔딩은 죽음뿐","romaji":"Agyeogui Ending Jugeumppun","userPreferred":"Agyeogui Ending Jugeumppun"},"type":"MANGA"}}},{"node":{"mediaRecommendation":{"bannerImage":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/manga/banner/123573-mUJqgpAkIWrX.jpg","countryOfOrigin":"KR","coverImage":{"color":"#e45d50","extraLarge":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/manga/cover/large/bx123573-LKoCKwRouEMW.png","large":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/manga/cover/medium/bx123573-LKoCKwRouEMW.png","medium":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/manga/cover/small/bx123573-LKoCKwRouEMW.png"},"description":"Kim Rok-Su has one life motto: “Let’s not get beat up.” But after dozing off somewhere midway through the novel “Birth of a Hero,” he wakes up as Cale Henituse - one of the minor villains in the novel who gets the beating of a lifetime from soon-to-be hero Choi Han. Only time will tell how much longer he has before that dreadful encounter. Can Kim Rok-Su change the course of this story so he can enjoy a long and lavish life free of the soon-to-be hero?\n\u003cbr\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\n(Source: Tappytoon)","endDate":{},"format":"MANGA","id":123573,"idMal":147317,"isAdult":false,"meanScore":78,"siteUrl":"https://anilist.co/manga/123573","startDate":{"day":31,"month":8,"year":2020},"status":"HIATUS","synonyms":["TCF","Trash Count","Trash of the Count's Family","La Basura De La Familia Del Conde","伯爵家の暴れん坊になった","成为伯爵家的废物","變成伯爵家的混混","อันธพาลแห่งตระกูลเคานต์","Pembuat Onar di Keluarga Count","Je suis devenu le voyou de la famille du comte "],"title":{"english":"Lout of Count’s Family","native":"백작가의 망나니가 되었다","romaji":"Baekjakgaui Mangnaniga Doeeotda","userPreferred":"Baekjakgaui Mangnaniga Doeeotda"},"type":"MANGA"}}},{"node":{"mediaRecommendation":{"countryOfOrigin":"KR","coverImage":{"color":"#0daee4","extraLarge":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/manga/cover/large/bx188902-LlmzxcoT36Fd.jpg","large":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/manga/cover/medium/bx188902-LlmzxcoT36Fd.jpg","medium":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/manga/cover/small/bx188902-LlmzxcoT36Fd.jpg"},"description":"Shi-Hu Lee has logged 20,000 hours playing Let's Kill the Demon Lord! for the past 5 years. But when the game takes a turn he doesn't like, Shi-Hu cancels his pre-order of the DLC in anger, only to find himself sucked into the game! Now in the body of Julian Kreipart Prason, the villain, he has to play the part perfectly to survive the many enemies around him while unable to use the moonlight blade, Julian's signature ability. Under the watchful eye of Eileen, the genius gold mage, and his family members who want him gone, can Julian make it?\u003cBr\u003e\u003cbr\u003e(Source: WEBTOON)","endDate":{},"format":"MANGA","id":188902,"idMal":180394,"isAdult":false,"meanScore":63,"siteUrl":"https://anilist.co/manga/188902","startDate":{"day":24,"month":3,"year":2025},"status":"RELEASING","title":{"english":"Playing the Perfect Fox-Eyed Villain","native":"완벽한 실눈 악역을 연기하다","romaji":"Wanbyeokhan Silnun Agyeogeul Yeongihada","userPreferred":"Wanbyeokhan Silnun Agyeogeul Yeongihada"},"type":"MANGA"}}},{"node":{"mediaRecommendation":{"countryOfOrigin":"KR","coverImage":{"color":"#5d86f1","extraLarge":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/manga/cover/large/bx152128-hk1Dq8zlEPVn.png","large":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/manga/cover/medium/bx152128-hk1Dq8zlEPVn.png","medium":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/manga/cover/small/bx152128-hk1Dq8zlEPVn.png"},"description":"Wouldn’t it be a dream to wake up in a world of your own creation? For Kim Hajin, it’s nothing short of a nightmare. With no clue how or why he’s been transported into his web novel — as a mere extra, no less! — Hajin has little choice but to see his story through until the end. Lucky for him, as the author, he knows this perilous world like the back of his hand. But when discrepancies in the plot begin popping up left and right, Hajin soon realizes that things aren’t quite so simple, after all…\u003cbr\u003e\u003cbr\u003e(Source: Tapas)","endDate":{},"format":"MANGA","id":152128,"idMal":148985,"isAdult":false,"meanScore":78,"siteUrl":"https://anilist.co/manga/152128","startDate":{"day":30,"month":6,"year":2022},"status":"RELEASING","synonyms":["The Novel's Extra (2022)","The Novel's Extra (Remake)","The Ghost Writing Hero","小説の中のエキストラ","ผมก็แค่ตัวประกอบในนิยาย","成為我筆下小說的路人甲"],"title":{"english":"The Novel's Extra","native":"소설 속 엑스트라","romaji":"Soseol Sok Extra","userPreferred":"Soseol Sok Extra"},"type":"MANGA"}}},{"node":{"mediaRecommendation":{"countryOfOrigin":"JP","coverImage":{"color":"#aed6ff","extraLarge":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/manga/cover/medium/b199682-ynDb5lYtloMc.jpg","large":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/manga/cover/medium/b199682-ynDb5lYtloMc.jpg","medium":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/manga/cover/small/b199682-ynDb5lYtloMc.jpg"},"description":"Waking up in a fantasy novel where the universe bans her from using magic is just the first of many trials for Chris Dotten, a new professor at the prestigious Bedallua Academy of Magic. Bombarded with quests that each threaten to penalize her with death if she fails, Chris must survive her tenure as the teacher of the novel’s protagonist using whatever means necessary. However, with no magical solution at hand, her sole strategy is to roleplay as the teacher who is so powerful that using magic is unnecessary. Will Chris and her act survive until graduation day?\u003cbr\u003e\u003cbr\u003e(Source: Tappytoon)","endDate":{},"format":"MANGA","id":199682,"isAdult":false,"meanScore":59,"siteUrl":"https://anilist.co/manga/199682","startDate":{"day":29,"month":4,"year":2025},"status":"RELEASING","synonyms":["The Fake Master Who Accidentally Became the Strongest","컨셉러가 최강 스승임"],"title":{"english":"The Mighty Teacher is a Roleplayer","native":"欠陥転生者、最強教師になりきります","romaji":"Kekkan Tenseisha, Saikyou Kyoushi ni Narimakirimasu","userPreferred":"Kekkan Tenseisha, Saikyou Kyoushi ni Narimakirimasu"},"type":"MANGA"}}},{"node":{"mediaRecommendation":{"countryOfOrigin":"KR","coverImage":{"color":"#aec9e4","extraLarge":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/manga/cover/large/bx187169-KwlSwFdW7gOa.png","large":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/manga/cover/medium/bx187169-KwlSwFdW7gOa.png","medium":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/manga/cover/small/bx187169-KwlSwFdW7gOa.png"},"description":"Long ago, a \"door\" connecting to another world opened, and those who gained special abilities along with a \"mark\" began to be called \"wizards.\" After the incident of \"that day,\" Ophion's first-class wizard \"Blow\" became very famous. One day, he receives a very special request. It is to protect the second son of the Artian Duke family, who is being called a \"monster\" and suffering at the \"Magic School Helios\"! Thus, Blow enters Helios as a student under the name \"Rood Krisch\" while hiding his identity... Will Blow be able to successfully complete the request amidst the whirlwind of unexpected events?\u003cbr\u003e\u003cbr\u003e(Source: KakaoPage, translated)","endDate":{},"format":"MANGA","id":187169,"idMal":178334,"isAdult":false,"meanScore":65,"siteUrl":"https://anilist.co/manga/187169","startDate":{"day":28,"month":1,"year":2025},"status":"RELEASING","synonyms":["Black Haze (2025)"],"title":{"native":"블랙 헤이즈","romaji":"Black Haze","userPreferred":"Black Haze"},"type":"MANGA"}}},{"node":{"mediaRecommendation":{"countryOfOrigin":"KR","coverImage":{"color":"#c9c9f1","extraLarge":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/manga/cover/large/bx165182-k4Jfk2XMkylP.jpg","large":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/manga/cover/medium/bx165182-k4Jfk2XMkylP.jpg","medium":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/manga/cover/small/bx165182-k4Jfk2XMkylP.jpg"},"description":"When there is no way out, the way is in. Doomed to die next month, our terminally ill protagonist Chan is too frail and defeated to try anything at all. No wonder he chooses to plunge himself into an RPG world he is only too familiar with. Why should this run be any different? Well, other than the fact that he will wake up inside the game and get struck with an existential epiphany that will make him fight tooth and nail to give Nox, his equally ill-fated RPG persona, a better chance? Maybe, it’s not over until it’s over.\n\u003cbr\u003e\u003cbr\u003e(Source: WEBTOON)","endDate":{},"format":"MANGA","id":165182,"idMal":159015,"isAdult":false,"meanScore":72,"siteUrl":"https://anilist.co/manga/165182","startDate":{"day":17,"month":5,"year":2023},"status":"RELEASING","synonyms":["Terminally-Ill Genius Dark Knight","Terminally ill Dark Knight","อัศวินดำล่าท้าเวลา","身患绝症的天才黑暗骑士"],"title":{"english":"Time-Limited Genius Dark Knight","native":"시한부 천재 암흑기사","romaji":"Sihanbu Cheonjae Amheukgisa","userPreferred":"Sihanbu Cheonjae Amheukgisa"},"type":"MANGA"}}}]},"relations":{},"siteUrl":"https://anilist.co/manga/187427"}},"updated_at":"2026-03-07T01:04:12.826288+03:00"},"199351":{"value":{"Media":{"characters":{"edges":[{"id":543941,"node":{"dateOfBirth":{},"gender":"Male","id":375933,"image":{"large":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/character/large/b375933-e0nDAEGpJSPz.png"},"isFavourite":false,"name":{"full":"Su Yu","native":"溯渔"},"siteUrl":"https://anilist.co/character/375933"},"role":"MAIN"},{"id":543942,"node":{"dateOfBirth":{},"gender":"Male","id":375934,"image":{"large":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/character/large/b375934-jiihiZsDkDTW.png"},"isFavourite":false,"name":{"full":"Hui Yang","native":"洄洋"},"siteUrl":"https://anilist.co/character/375934"},"role":"MAIN"}]},"genres":["Drama","Romance","Thriller"],"id":199351,"recommendations":{},"relations":{},"siteUrl":"https://anilist.co/manga/199351"}},"updated_at":"2026-02-26T19:15:02.345504+03:00"},"84505":{"value":{"Media":{"characters":{"edges":[{"id":412122,"node":{"dateOfBirth":{},"description":"__Height:__ 163cm\n__Weight:__ 56kg","gender":"Female","id":298314,"image":{"large":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/character/large/b298314-oa5DDTbGZRuA.jpg"},"isFavourite":false,"name":{"full":"Yuri Momoi","native":"桃井由梨"},"siteUrl":"https://anilist.co/character/298314"},"role":"MAIN"},{"id":412123,"node":{"dateOfBirth":{},"description":"__Height:__ 171cm","gender":"Female","id":298315,"image":{"large":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/character/large/b298315-Qqiavgd4anaO.jpg"},"isFavourite":false,"name":{"full":"Kumiko Aoyama","native":"青山久美子"},"siteUrl":"https://anilist.co/character/298315"},"role":"MAIN"},{"id":412124,"node":{"dateOfBirth":{},"description":"__Height:__ 161cm\n__Weight:__ 50kg","gender":"Female","id":298316,"image":{"large":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/character/large/b298316-41ZNpuyy9yJu.jpg"},"isFavourite":false,"name":{"full":"Sakura Shirogane","native":"白銀さくら"},"siteUrl":"https://anilist.co/character/298316"},"role":"MAIN"},{"id":412125,"node":{"dateOfBirth":{},"gender":"Male","id":298312,"image":{"large":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/character/large/b298312-QQ4l9xzSNCJG.jpg"},"isFavourite":false,"name":{"full":"Koutarou Kuroda","native":"黒田幸太郎"},"siteUrl":"https://anilist.co/character/298312"},"role":"MAIN"},{"id":412126,"node":{"dateOfBirth":{},"description":"__Height:__ 145cm\n__Weight:__ 42kg","gender":"Female","id":298313,"image":{"large":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/character/large/b298313-tS9OGeXxhwk3.jpg"},"isFavourite":false,"name":{"full":"Matori Kise","native":"黄瀬真鳥"},"siteUrl":"https://anilist.co/character/298313"},"role":"MAIN"},{"id":412127,"node":{"dateOfBirth":{},"description":"__Height:__ 167 cm","gender":"Female","id":298317,"image":{"large":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/character/large/b298317-WMqYAHstzqCy.jpg"},"isFavourite":false,"name":{"full":"Aya Akagi","native":"赤城綾"},"siteUrl":"https://anilist.co/character/298317"},"role":"MAIN"}]},"genres":["Hentai","Romance","Sports"],"id":84505,"recommendations":{"edges":[{"node":{"mediaRecommendation":{"bannerImage":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/manga/banner/123760-KhoXSLHmJLpu.jpg","countryOfOrigin":"JP","coverImage":{"color":"#f1ae28","extraLarge":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/manga/cover/medium/b123760-BQT1K7Z7k6ZB.jpg","large":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/manga/cover/medium/b123760-BQT1K7Z7k6ZB.jpg","medium":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/manga/cover/small/b123760-BQT1K7Z7k6ZB.jpg"},"description":"Some gyarus have decided to use Imaizumi's house as a gathering spot to play video games and eat snacks. When Reina gets bored with video games, she sets her sights on another toy in the house: Imaizumi himself...\u003cbr\u003e\n\u003cbr\u003e\n(Source: Fakku!)\u003cbr\u003e","endDate":{},"format":"MANGA","id":123760,"idMal":124483,"isAdult":true,"meanScore":80,"siteUrl":"https://anilist.co/manga/123760","startDate":{"day":8,"month":4,"year":2019},"status":"RELEASING","synonyms":["Imaizumi's house is a place for gals to gather","이마이즈미네, 어느새 갸루 아지트가 되어버렸다"],"title":{"english":"Imaizumi Brings All The Gyarus To His House","native":"今泉ん家はどうやらギャルの溜まり場になってるらしい","romaji":"Imaizumin-chi wa Douyara Gal no Tamariba ni Natteru Rashii","userPreferred":"Imaizumin-chi wa Douyara Gal no Tamariba ni Natteru Rashii"},"type":"MANGA"}}},{"node":{"mediaRecommendation":{"bannerImage":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/manga/banner/88701-sYURNHdGNIHS.jpg","chapters":6,"countryOfOrigin":"JP","coverImage":{"color":"#f1e41a","extraLarge":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/manga/cover/large/bx88701-WchZVvYW0E00.jpg","large":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/manga/cover/medium/bx88701-WchZVvYW0E00.jpg","medium":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/manga/cover/small/bx88701-WchZVvYW0E00.jpg"},"description":"1-6. \u003cb\u003eZannen na Heroine-tachi\u003c/b\u003e (残念なヒロインたち); Comic Mujin 2013-09, 10, 12, 2014-03, 05, 07","endDate":{"day":6,"month":6,"year":2014},"format":"MANGA","id":88701,"idMal":58851,"isAdult":true,"meanScore":74,"siteUrl":"https://anilist.co/manga/88701","startDate":{"day":5,"month":8,"year":2013},"status":"FINISHED","synonyms":["Zannen na Heroine-tachi","Regrettable Heroines"],"title":{"native":"いきなり！ハーレムライフ","romaji":"Ikinari! Harem Life","userPreferred":"Ikinari! Harem Life"},"type":"MANGA","volumes":1}}},{"node":{"mediaRecommendation":{"bannerImage":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/manga/banner/92798-weBJg9FjKcJ3.jpg","chapters":9,"countryOfOrigin":"JP","coverImage":{"color":"#f15093","extraLarge":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/manga/cover/large/bx92798-Fm0EvZlfcf49.jpg","large":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/manga/cover/medium/bx92798-Fm0EvZlfcf49.jpg","medium":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/manga/cover/small/bx92798-Fm0EvZlfcf49.jpg"},"description":"Oh, to be on a nude beach with a harem of all your classmates! Another legendary story from Shiwasu no Okina, this title tells you exactly what you’re going to get!","endDate":{"day":27,"month":6,"year":2015},"format":"MANGA","id":92798,"idMal":79253,"isAdult":true,"meanScore":75,"siteUrl":"https://anilist.co/manga/92798","startDate":{"day":28,"month":4,"year":2014},"status":"FINISHED","synonyms":["Class Trip to the Nudist Beach!!","Nudist Beach ni Shuugakuryokou de!!","Yarimoku Beach ni Shuugaku Ryokou de!!","In school trip to the nudist beach!!","The Nude Beach Field Trip!!"],"title":{"english":"The Nude Beach Field Trip!!","native":"ヌーディストビーチに修学旅行で!!","romaji":"Nudist Beach ni Shuugaku Ryokou de!!","userPreferred":"Nudist Beach ni Shuugaku Ryokou de!!"},"type":"MANGA","volumes":1}}},{"node":{"mediaRecommendation":{"bannerImage":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/manga/banner/104449-9f8yf3xrUTgh.jpg","countryOfOrigin":"JP","coverImage":{"extraLarge":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/manga/cover/large/bx104449-HupiskHd11wG.jpg","large":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/manga/cover/medium/bx104449-HupiskHd11wG.jpg","medium":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/manga/cover/small/bx104449-HupiskHd11wG.jpg"},"description":"1. \u003cb\u003eSaimin Seishidou 1 Obata Yui to Tachibana Daiki no Baai\u003c/b\u003e (催眠性指導1 小幡優衣と橘大貴の場合), Comic Market 90\u003cbr\u003e\nUsing hypnosis, Tanaka appoints himself the school's Sexual Counselor, in charge of training the girls of his school how to have sex, all while their boyfriends are watching!\u003cbr\u003e\n\u003cbr\u003e\n2. \u003cb\u003eSaimin Seishidou 2 Kurashiki Reina no Baai\u003c/b\u003e (催眠性指導2 倉敷玲奈の場合), Comic Market 91\u003cbr\u003e\nTanaka's adventures continue as he uses his talents to bring Reina, one of the most popular girls at his school, down a peg or two!\u003cbr\u003e\n\u003cbr\u003e\n3. \u003cb\u003eSaimin Seishidou 2.5 Keika Kansatu\u003c/b\u003e (催眠性指導 2・5 経過観察), COMIC1☆11\u003cbr\u003e\nThis busty blonde is looking to get better at sex for her boyfriend, and what better way then to engage in some \"sexual counseling\" in the men's bathroom for a crowd. Wait, isn't this just sex? N-No, that can't be...\u003cbr\u003e\n\u003cbr\u003e\n4. \u003cb\u003eSaimin Seishidou 2.75 Taiken Shidou\u003c/b\u003e (催眠性指導 2.75 体験指導), Comic Market 92\u003cbr\u003e\nTanaka generously offers to train even the girls who lack boyfriends, indulging in a variety of girls and teaching them about sex.\u003cbr\u003e\n\u003cbr\u003e\n5. \u003cb\u003eSaimin Seishidou 3 Miyajima Sakura to Kase Masafumi no Baai\u003c/b\u003e (催眠性指導 3 宮島桜と加瀬正文の場合), Comic Market 93\u003cbr\u003e\nTanaka's attentions turn to Sakura Miyajima, president of the kendo club, who begs him to teach her how to get pregnant!\u003cbr\u003e\n\u003cbr\u003e\n6. \u003cb\u003eSaimin Seishidou 4 Ninshin Taiken Shidou (Shi)\u003c/b\u003e (催眠性指導 4 妊娠体験指導(試)), Comic Market 94\u003cbr\u003e\nContinuing from the events of Hypnotic Sexual Counseling 3, self-elected school sexual counselor Hajime continues his pursuit of Sakura by persuading her to prepare herself for a future of childbearing. When it comes to the point that he is even brought to Sakura's house in order to update her parents on their daughter's progress, Hajime begins to get ideas on his next target after seeing an all-but-alluring Mrs. Miyajima.\u003cbr\u003e\n\u003ci\u003eNOTE: This is the first part of two in the fourth installment to the mainline stories of the Hypnotic Sexual Counseling series.\u003c/i\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\n\u003cbr\u003e\n7. \u003cb\u003eSaimin Seishidou Kurashiki Reika no Baai\u003c/b\u003e (催眠性指導 倉敷麗華の場合), Comic Market 95\u003cbr\u003e\nReina's mother, Reika, is displeased to fine her daughter fraternizing with the self-proclaimed sexual guidance counselor, Hajime. More than simply unimpressed with his general appearance, Reika doubts his capabilities in sex in general, and so decides to test him through a physical show of prowess. Needless to say, Hajime is more than up for the challenge, but will he be able to meet Reika's strict expectations?\u003cbr\u003e\n\u003cbr\u003e\n8. \u003cb\u003eSaimin Seishidou Nozaki Yuu no Baai\u003c/b\u003e (催眠性指導 野崎悠の場合), COMIC1☆15\u003cbr\u003e\nHer name is Yuu Nozaki, the so-called \"Sleeping Beauty\" of the academy. Her nonchalance and grace belie her sloth-like attitude towards life. With this in mind, self-proclaimed school sexual counsellor Hajime Tanaka takes it upon himself to instruct the unassuming Yuu regarding the pleasures of sexual intercourse and what makes sexual relationships so great.\u003cbr\u003e\n\u003cbr\u003e\n9. \u003cb\u003eSaimin Seishidou 4: Ninshin Taiken Shidou\u003c/b\u003e (催眠性指導4 妊娠体験指導); Comic Market 96\u003cbr\u003e\nHajime Tanaka isn't done with the women of the Miyajima household, this time hypnotizing both mother and daughter to take part in his twisted scheme of teaching Sakura what it means to become pregnant. Using her own mother, Tsubaki, as a visual aid, Tanaka proceeds to inseminate both mother and daughter in the awesome conclusion of the fourth chapter of the Hypnotic Sexual Counseling series.\u003cbr\u003e\n\u003cbr\u003e\n10. \u003cb\u003eSaimin Seishidou Obata Natsumi no Baai\u003c/b\u003e (催眠性指導 小幡夏美の場合); Comic Market 97\u003cbr\u003e\nHajime Tanaka visits the house of Yui Obata, only to be informed by her mother, Natsumi Obata, that she is out for the day. Good thing Tanaka's real purpose for visiting was to supplement his Sexual Counseling services for Yui by \"examining\" her own mother. It's all-in-a-day's work for our resident hypnotic sexual counseling expert as he adds yet another mother to his growing collection of women.\u003cbr\u003e\n\u003cbr\u003e\n11. \u003cb\u003eSaimin Seishidou 5 Hiiragi Suzuka\u003c/b\u003e (催眠性指導5 柊鈴香)\u003cbr\u003e\n\u003cbr\u003e\n(Source: fakku)","endDate":{},"format":"MANGA","id":104449,"idMal":104219,"isAdult":true,"meanScore":77,"siteUrl":"https://anilist.co/manga/104449","startDate":{"day":14,"month":8,"year":2016},"status":"RELEASING","synonyms":["Hypnosis Sex Guidance","Training Session One: Yui Obata And Daiki Tachibana","Training Session Two: Reina Kurashiki","Personal Guidance","Pregnancy Guidance Experience","Reika Kurashiki's Case","Yuu Nozaki","Natsumi Obata"],"title":{"english":"Hypnotic Sexual Counseling","native":"催眠性指導","romaji":"Saimin Seishidou","userPreferred":"Saimin Seishidou"},"type":"MANGA"}}},{"node":{"mediaRecommendation":{"bannerImage":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/manga/banner/n105605-VbKYWF4Lx4X7.jpg","chapters":8,"countryOfOrigin":"JP","coverImage":{"color":"#e4bb50","extraLarge":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/manga/cover/large/nx105605-DxWIFwiaX1s3.jpg","large":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/manga/cover/medium/nx105605-DxWIFwiaX1s3.jpg","medium":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/manga/cover/small/nx105605-DxWIFwiaX1s3.jpg"},"description":"1. \u003cb\u003eShishunki Sex\u003c/b\u003e (思春期セックス); Comic Shingeki 2018-04\u003cbr\u003e\n2-4. \u003cb\u003eKyou, Watashinchi Shuugou ne!\u003c/b\u003e (今日、私ん家集合ね!); Comic Shingeki 2017-07, 09, 2018-02\u003cbr\u003e\n5. \u003cb\u003eNurunuru DeliHeal\u003c/b\u003e (ぬるぬるデリヘル); Comic Shingeki 2017-04\u003cbr\u003e\n6. \u003cb\u003eSaiminjutsu ni Kakerarete\u003c/b\u003e (催眠術にかけられて); Comic Shingeki 2016-08\u003cbr\u003e\n7. \u003cb\u003eNantai Shoujo\u003c/b\u003e (軟体少女); Comic Shingeki 2016-12\u003cbr\u003e\n8. \u003cb\u003eAfter Nantai Shoujo\u003c/b\u003e (after軟体少女); kakioroshi","endDate":{"day":6,"month":4,"year":2018},"format":"MANGA","id":105605,"idMal":116833,"isAdult":true,"meanScore":75,"siteUrl":"https://anilist.co/manga/105605","startDate":{"day":6,"month":4,"year":2018},"status":"FINISHED","synonyms":["Kyou, Watashi ie Shuugou ne!","Nurunuru Deriheru","Saimin Jutsu ni Kakerarete","Nantai Shoujo"],"title":{"native":"思春期セックス","romaji":"Shishunki Sex","userPreferred":"Shishunki Sex"},"type":"MANGA","volumes":1}}},{"node":{"mediaRecommend